\id LUK
\h Luka
\toc1 Luka
\toc2 Luka
\toc3 Lk.
\mt1 Luka
\c 1
\s1 Tamezwarut
\m 
\v 1 Umi aṭṭas idsen tuɣa nwan ad arin imezruyen x tmesřayin i zi nettwasseqneɛ
\v 2 - am mammec tent i d aneɣ xebbaren nitni, inni iẓrin Awař zeg umezwaru u tuɣa aten d imsexxaren nnes -
\v 3 iban ayi-dd uřa i necc, minzi ḍfareɣ marra timesřayin mliḥ zeg umezwaru, ḥima ad ac dd-ariɣ kuřci s usettef, \add a\add* Tiyufilis iɛizzen,
\v 4 ḥima ad tessned \add mliḥ\add* tidett n wawařen nni zi tᵉttwassřemded.
\b
\s1 Zakariyya d Iliṣabit
\m 
\v 5 Tuɣa din deg wussan n Hirudus, ajeǧid n Yahudiyya, ijj n ukehhan, qqaren as Zakariyya. Netta zi terbiɛt \add n ikehhanen\add* n taddart n Abiya uca tamɣart nnes tuɣa-tt zi tarrawt n Harun, qqaren as Iliṣabit. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Im. 24:10. \x*
\v 6 Tuɣa s tnayen idsen d imseggaden ɣar AREBBI, ḍfaren marra tiweṣṣa u uyuren \add di řatarat n\add* tsegda n SIDI břa řɛib.
\v 7 War tuɣi ɣarsen bu uḥenjir minzi Iliṣabit tuɣa war dd-tᵉttiruw ca u tuɣa s tnayen idsen mɣaren deg wussan.
\m 
\v 8 Aqa imsar, řami tuɣa \add Zakariyya\add* ittegg řxedmet n ukehhan qibač i AREBBI x nnubet n terbiɛt nnes \add n ikehhanen\add*, \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt 1 Im. 24\x*
\v 9 aqa yusa-dd dayes ukeccuḍ ɛlaḥsab lqaɛida n tukehhant, ḥima ad iqeddem tawhibt n řebxur, uca yudef netta ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Uf. 30:7; Lawi 16:17. \x*
\v 10 Tuɣa qaɛ abarru n řgens ittẓaǧa barra di tsaɛɛet n tewhibt n řebxur.
\v 11 \add Řexdenni\add* iḍḥar as-dd lmalak n SIDI i Zakariyya nni tuɣa ibedden x ufusi n uɛalṭar n řebxur.
\v 12 Umi t iẓra Zakariyya, innexřeɛ uca iggʷed.
\v 13 Inna as lmalak: “War tteggʷed ca, \add a\add* Zakariyya, minzi tᵉttwaqbeř tẓaǧit nnec. Aqa Iliṣabit, tameṭṭut nnec, ad ac dd-taruw aḥenjir, ad t tsemmid Yuḥanna. \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt Lk. 1:60. \x*
\v 14 Ad tfarḥed u ad tesřiwřewed uca aṭṭas n iwdan ad farḥen i wexřaq nnes, \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Lk. 1:58. \x*
\v 15 minzi ad yiři d ameqqran ɣar SIDI, war isess binu uřa d ccrab. Ad ittwaccur s Arruḥ Iqeddsen deg uɛeddis n yemmas, \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Řqḍ. 13:4. \x*
\v 16 uca ad dd-yarr aṭṭas n iḥenjiren n Israil ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Mal. 3:24; Mt. 11:14. \x*
\v 17 Netta ad yuyur zzates s arruḥ d jjehd n unabi Iliya, ḥima ad dd-yarr uřawen n ibabaten ɣar tarrawt nsen u inni war yuminen ɣar tussna n Umsegged, ḥima ad issewjed ijj n řgens ikmeř i SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Mal. 3:23-24; Mt. 3:2; Mk. 9:12. \x*
\v 18 Yarra-dd Zakariyya x lmalak: “Mammec i ɣa ggeɣ ad fehmeɣ aya, minzi necc d awessar uřa d tamɣart inu temɣar aṭṭas!” \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Amz. 17:17. \x*
\v 19 Yarra-dd lmalak, inna as: “Necc d \bd Jibril\bd*, wenni ibedden zzat i AREBBI, ttwassekkeɣ-dd ḥima ad kik ssiwřeɣ, ad cek xebbareɣ řexbar-a wanita aṣebḥan.
\v 20 Zi řexxu ad tegnud u war tzemmared ad tessiwřed ař ass min di i ɣa imsar uya, minzi war tumined ca s wawařen inu nni i ɣa ittwakemmřen di řweqt nsen.”
\v 21 Tuɣa řgens \add di barra\add* ittraja Zakariyya uca \add iwdan\add* ttbehten umi iɛeṭṭař daxeř di Zzawect Tameqqrant.
\v 22 Umi dd-iffeɣ Zakariyya, tuɣa war izemmar ad kisen issiweř. Xenni fehmen belli iban as-dd ca n řewḥiy di Zzawect Tameqqrant. Tuɣa ittceyyar asen, \add maca\add* iqqim ignu.
\v 23 Umi kemmřen wussan n řxedmet \add n tukehhant\add* nnes, iɛqeb-dd ɣar taddart nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 24 Awarni ussan nni teksi tamɣart nnes Iliṣabit s ddeyset. Teffar ixef nnes xemsa n iyuren, uca tebda teqqar:
\v 25 “Ammu i zzayi igga SIDI deg wussan nni umi ɣari dd-ixzar, ḥima ad xafi ikkes aseḥqar n iwdan.” \x ◘ \xo 1:25 \xt Amz. 30:23; Ica. 4:1. \x*
\b
\s1 Aḍhar n lmalak i Maryam
\m 
\v 26 Deg uyur wiss setta issekk-dd AREBBI lmalak Jibril ɣar ict n tendint di Ljalil, qqaren as Nnaṣira,
\v 27 ɣar ict n teɛzarect d tanexḍabt ɣar weryaz zi taddart n \add ujeǧid\add* Dawud, qqaren as Yusuf. Tuɣa isem n teɛzarect nni Maryam. \x ◘ \xo 1:27 \xt Mt. 1:18. \x*
\v 28 Yudef-dd ɣares lmalak, inna as: “Sřam xam, \add a\add* tamimunt! Siditneɣ akidem! Cem aqa tᵉttwabarked jar temɣarin!”
\v 29 Umi t teẓra, tennexřeɛ zeg wawař nnes uca txarreṣ min ixs ad yini sřam-a.
\v 30 Inna as lmalak: “War tteggʷed ca, \add a\add* Maryam, minzi tufid arḍa ɣar AREBBI.
\v 31 Ad teksid ddeyset uca ad tarwed Aḥenjir, ad t tsemmid ‘Yeccu’. \x ◘ \xo 1:31 \xt Ica. 7:14. \x*
\v 32 Wanita ad yiři d ameqqran, ad xas ttřaɣan Mmis n Umɛuǧi x kuřci, u ad as iwc SIDI AREBBI řɛarc n jeddis Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 1:32 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 9:6; 54:5. \x*
\v 33 Netta ad iḥkem x taddart n Yaɛqub i řebda, war ittiři uneggar i Tgeldit nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 1:33 \xt 1 Im. 22:10; Izhd. 45:7; 89:37; Irm. 23:5; Dan. 7:14, 27; Mixa 4:7; Ɛbr. 1:8. \x*
\v 34 Tenna Maryam i lmalak: “Mammec i ɣa yiři uya am war mřiceɣ ca ak-d weryaz?”
\v 35 Yarra-dd lmalak, inna as: “Arruḥ Iqeddsen ad dd-yas uca jjehd n Umɛuǧi x kuřci ad xam yarsa. S uyenni ad yiři wenni i dd ɣa ixeřqen zzayem d amqeddas u ad t semman Mmis n AREBBI.
\v 36 Xzar, Iliṣabit, řaǧ nnem, nettat ɛawed aqa-tt s ddeyset di tewsar nnes. Aqa d ayur wiss setta i nettat umi qqaren ‘war tᵉttiruw!’
\v 37 Minzi war din min yewɛaren i AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 1:37 \xt Ayub 42:2; Irm. 32:17; Zak. 8:6; Mt. 19:26; Lk. 18:27. \x*
\v 38 Tenna Maryam: “Xzar, necc d tayya n SIDI, ad ayi imsar ɛlaḥsab awař nnec.” \add Xas uca\add* yuyur xas lmalak.
\b
\s1 Maryam truḥ ad tarzef Iliṣabit
\m 
\v 39 Deg wussan nni tekkar Maryam, truḥ deɣya ɣar idurar, ɣar ict n tendint n Yahudiyya.
\v 40 Tudef ɣar taddart n Zakariyya, tseǧem x Iliṣabit.
\v 41 Umi tesřa Iliṣabit i sřam n Maryam, imsar aqa inhezz useymi deg uɛeddis nnes, uca tedweř Iliṣabit teccur s Arruḥ Iqeddsen.
\v 42 Nettat tesɣuy s jjehd, tenna i Maryam: “Cem aqa tᵉttwabarked jar temɣarin, tᵉttwabarek řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnem!
\v 43 Zi manis ɣari aya, ḥima ad ɣari dd-tas yemmas n Sidi inu?
\v 44 Maɣar řami dd-tiweḍ tmijja n sřam nnem ɣar umezzuɣ inu, inhezz useymi deg uɛeddis inu s řefraḥet tameqqrant.
\v 45 Sseɛd n tenni yumnen aqa ad ittwakemmeř min d as ittwanna zi SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 1:45 \xt Lk. 11:28. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 46 Tenna Maryam:
\b
\m \qt “Řeɛmar inu issemɣara di SIDI,\qt*
\m 
\v 47 \qt ifarḥ buḥbeř inu s AREBBI,\qt*
\m \qt wenni d ayi itticen Tudart,\qt*
\m 
\v 48 \qt s minzi ixzar\qt*
\m \qt ɣar umeddur awaḍeɛ n tayya nnes.\qt*
\m \qt Xzar, zi řexxu marra arrawen\qt*
\m \qt ad ayi semman ‘D tamimunt!’\qt*
\m 
\v 49 \qt Minzi wenni d Amzemmar igga dayi\qt*
\m \qt timesřayin mɣarent,\qt*
\m \qt aqa Isem nnes iqeddes.\qt*
\m 
\v 50 \qt Arreḥmet nnes x tarwa d jjiřat,\qt*
\m \qt x yinni t ittweqqaren.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:50 \xt Uf. 20:6. \x*
\m 
\v 51 \qt S uɣiř nnes aqa yiwi-dd řeɣřeb.\qt*
\m \qt Ifartek inni iɛeffaren\qt*
\m \qt deg ixarriṣen n wuřawen nsen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:51 \xt Izhd. 33:10; Ica. 51:9; 52:10; 1 Bṭ. 5:5. \x*
\m 
\v 52 \qt Inni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa iɣḍeř i-ten\qt*
\m \qt zi řekrasi nsen,\qt*
\m \qt imwaḍɛen issgeɛɛed i-ten.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:52 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:8; Izhd. 113:6. \x*
\m 
\v 53 \qt Issjiwen s řxar inni iǧuẓen,\qt*
\m \qt isqad aytbab n wagřa s ifassen xwan.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:53 \xt Izhd. 34:11. \x*
\m 
\v 54 \qt Amsexxar nnes Israil, iɛawen i-t,\qt*
\m \qt aqa iɛqeř x arreḥmet nnes,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:54 \xt Ica. 30:18; 41:9; 54:5; Irm. 31:2, 20. \x*
\m 
\v 55 \qt am mammec issiweř ak-d řejdud nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ak-d Ibrahim d zzariɛet nnes,\qt*
\m \qt i řebda.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:55 \xt Amz. 17:19; 22:18; Izhd. 132:11. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 56 Tekka Maryam ɛřaḥař třata n iyuren ɣar Iliṣabit, \add xenni\add* teɛqeb ɣar taddart nnes.
\b
\s1 Axřaq n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ
\m 
\v 57 Řami dd-tiweḍ řweqt n Iliṣabit, ḥima ad dd-taruw, tejj-dd aḥenjir.
\v 58 Sřin jjiran d řaǧ nnes belli AREBBI isscen as arreḥmet nnes aṭṭas, farḥen nitni akides. \x ◘ \xo 1:58 \xt Lk. 1:14. \x*
\m 
\v 59 Deg wass wiss tmenya usin-dd, ḥima ad xetnen i uḥenjir uca semman t s yisem n babas Zakariyya. \x ◘ \xo 1:59 \xt Amz. 17:12; Lawi 12:3. \x*
\v 60 \add Maca\add* tᵉṭṭef yemmas deg wawař, tenna: “Lla. war ittwasemma ammu, maca ad ittwasemma Yuḥanna.” \x ◘ \xo 1:60 \xt Lk. 1:13. \x*
\v 61 Nnan as: “War iǧi ḥed zi řaǧ nnem ttřaɣan as-dd s yisem-a.”
\v 62 \add Xenni\add* ciyyaren ɣar babas, mammec ixs ad t isemma.
\v 63 Ittar tařwiḥt uca yura xas, inna: “Isem nnes Yuḥanna.” Uca tbehten iwdan marra.
\v 64 Řexdenni yarzem aqemmum nnes uca \add ittwaḍřeq\add* yiřes nnes uca issiweř \add ɛawed\add*, ibarek AREBBI.
\m 
\v 65 Tehwa-dd tiggʷudi x marra jjiran nsen, ssiwřen aṭṭas x marra man aya di kuř idurar n Yahudiyya.
\v 66 Marra inni isřin i man aya, xemmřen t deg wuřawen nsen, nnan: “Aqa min ɣa yiři uḥenjir-a?” Tuɣa afus n SIDI akides.
\b
\m 
\v 67 Ittwaccur Babas Zakariyya s Arruḥ Iqeddsen, inebba, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 68 \qt “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Israil,\qt*
\m \qt minzi ifekkar di řgens nnes\qt*
\m \qt uca yiwi asen-dd asenjem.\qt*
\m 
\v 69 \qt Issgeɛɛed aneɣ-dd ijj n yicc n usenjem\qt*
\m \qt di taddart n Dawud, amsexxar nnes,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:69 \xt Izhd. 132:17. \x*
\m 
\v 70 \qt - am mammec tuɣa d aneɣ inna\qt*
\m \qt s uqemmum n inabiyyen iqeddsen nnes,\qt*
\m \qt inni din tuɣa zeg wecḥař uya -\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:70 \xt Izhd. 72:12; Ica. 40:10; Irm. 23:6; 30:10; Dan. 9:27. \x*
\m 
\v 71 \qt ḥima ad aneɣ ifekk zi řɛedyan nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt zeg ifassen n yinni i d aneɣ icarrhen.\qt*
\m 
\v 72 \qt Netta igga arreḥmet nnes i řejdud nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt aqa iɛqeř x řɛuhud nnes iqeddsen,\qt*
\m 
\v 73 \qt x tajaǧit tenni ijjuǧ i Ibrahim, jedditneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad d aneɣ iwc,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:73 \xt Amz. 22:16; Izhd. 105:9; Irm. 31:33; Ɛbr. 6:13, 17. \x*
\m 
\v 74 \qt maḥend ad nettwafekk\qt*
\m \qt zeg ifassen n řɛedyan nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ad as nsexxar břa tiggʷudi,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:74 \xt Ɛbr. 9:14\x*
\m 
\v 75 \qt s tqeddast d tsegda,\qt*
\m \qt marra ussan \tl n tudart\tl* nneɣ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:75 \xt 1 Bṭ. 1:15. \x*
\m 
\v 76 \qt I cek, a aḥenjir, ad ac ttřaɣan\qt*
\m \qt anabi n Umɛuǧi x kuřci,\qt*
\m \qt minzi ad traḥed zzat i uɣembub n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad tesswejded abrid nnes,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:76 \xt Lk. 1:17; Mal. 3:23. \x*
\m 
\v 77 \qt ḥima ad iwc i řgens nnes tussna n Tudart,\qt*
\m \qt \tl i iǧan\tl* s weɣfar n ddnub nsen,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:77 \xt Lk. 3:3. \x*
\m 
\v 78 \qt s řaǧaɣ n arreḥmet n AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt i zi xaneɣ i ɣa iḥinn řefjar zi řuɛřa,\qt*
\m 
\v 79 \qt ḥima ad issirɣ tfawt i yinni iqqimen\qt*
\m \qt di taǧest d tiři n řmewt,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad igewwed iḍaren nneɣ\qt*
\m \qt deg webrid n řehna.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:79 \xt Ica. 9:1; 42:7; 43:8; 49:9; 60:1. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 80 Am iggam uḥenjir, yarenni dayes Arruḥ u tuɣa-t di řexřa ař ass i di dd-iḍhar i Israil. \x ◘ \xo 1:80 \xt Lk. 2:40. \x*
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Axřaq n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni iffeɣ-dd ijj n řumur zi qayṣar Uɣustus ḥima ad ttwazemmemen marra imezdaɣ n řeḥkamet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt [Mt. 1:18-25] \x*
\v 2 Azemmem-a tuɣa-t d amezwaru umi tuɣa Qiriniyus iḥekkem di Suriya.
\v 3 Kuř ijjen iřuḥ ɣar tendint nnes, ḥima ad ittwazemmem dinni.
\v 4 Igeɛɛed ɛawed Yusuf zi Nnaṣira, ict n tendint di Ljalil, ɣar Yahudiyya, ɣar tendint n Dawud tenni umi qqaren Bayt-Laḥm umi t tuɣa zi taddart u zi jjiř n Dawud, \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16; Mixa 5:1; Mt. 1:1; Yḥ. 7:42. \x*
\v 5 ak-d Maryam, tanexḍabt nnes, tenni tuɣa s ddeyset, ḥima ad ittwazemmem dinni.
\m 
\v 6 Uca imsar, ařami ten tuɣa dinni, qefřen wussan nnes ḥima ad taru.
\v 7 Turuw-dd Mmis amenzu, tessenneḍ i-t di teḥřucin uca tessars i-t di řkuri, minzi war ɣarsen bu wemcan mani \add zemmaren\add* ad qqimen. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Mt. 1:25. \x*
\b
\s1 Imeksawen deg iyyaren n Bayt-Laḥm
\m 
\v 8 Di jjwayeh nni tuɣa din ca n imeksawen, ḥeṭṭan tiḥimriwin nsen di ǧiřet.
\v 9 U xzar, lmalak n AREBBI ibedd-dd ɣarsen uca aɛuǧi n SIDI issarɣ xasen, inneḍ asen, uca třeḥḥef asen ict n tiggʷudi temɣar.
\v 10 Inna asen lmalak nni: “War tteggʷedem ca, ad awem barrḥeɣ řexbar aṣebḥan, ad tiři řefraḥet temɣar i ddunect marra.
\v 11 Aqa ittwaxřeq awem-dd ass-a Umsenjem, SIDI, Lmasiḥ, di tendint n Dawud.
\v 12 D wa d awem i ɣa yiřin d řeɛřamet: Ad tafem Aseymi ittwanneḍ di teḥřucin, immars di řkuri.”
\v 13 Řexdenni iban-dd ak-d lmalak ijj n řɣaci ameqqran n řɛeskarat n ujenna ttṣebbaḥen AREBBI, qqaren: \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt Dan. 7:10; Asa. 5:11. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 \qt “Aɛuǧi i AREBBI di řuɛřa,\qt*
\m \qt řehna x temmurt,\qt*
\m \qt u asitem d aṣebḥan i yewdan.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Ica. 57:19; Afa. 2:17. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 15 Umi xasen uyurent lmalakat ɣar ujenna, ssiwřen imeksawen ak-d wayawya, nnan: “Ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ ɣar Bayt-Laḥm, ḥima ad nẓar min imsaren min xef d aneɣ issargeb SIDI.”
\v 16 Usin-dd s tazřa, ufin Maryam d Yusuf d Useymi immars di řmedwed.
\v 17 Umi t ẓrin, ɛawden awař i d asen ittwannan x Uḥenjir.
\v 18 Marra inni isřin, tbehten s min d asen nnan imeksawen.
\v 19 Maca Maryam tuɣa txemmeř marra awařen-a, tᵉttxarraṣ daysen deg wuř nnes.
\v 20 Xenni ɛeqben-dd imeksawen, ttṣebbaḥen u ssemɣaran di AREBBI x marra min sřin d marra min ẓrin, \add nican\add* am mammec d asen tuɣa ittwanna.
\b
\s1 Axtan n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 21 Umi kemmřen tmenya n wussan, ḥima ad ittwaxten Useymi, semman t ‘Yeccu’, am mammec tuɣa t isemma lmalak qbeř i ɣa ittwaksi deg uɛeddis. \x ◘ \xo 2:21 \xt Amz. 17:12; Lawi 12:3; Mt. 1:21; Lk. 1:31; Yḥ. 7:22. \x*
\v 22 Umi kemmřen wussan n usizdeg nsen ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n Musa, iwyen t ɣar Urcalim, ḥima ad t qeddmen zzat i SIDI \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Lawi 12:6. \x*
\v 23 - am mammec tura di Ccariɛa n SIDI: ‘Aqa kuř \add mmis\add* amenzu i dd-ittwaxeřqen zeg uɛeddis n yemmas ad ittwasemma d amqeddas i SIDI!’ - \x ◘ \xo 2:23 \xt Uf. 13:2, 12; Řxř. 3:13; 8:16, 17. \x*
\v 24 u ḥima ad ḥḍaren taɣarṣt am mammec tᵉttwanna di Ccariɛa n SIDI: tnayen n idbiren niɣ tyuya n iwarruḍen n idbiren. \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Lawi 12:8. \x*
\b
\s1 Řefraḥet n Cimɛun d Ḥanna
\m 
\v 25 Tuɣa di Urcalim ijj n weryaz qqaren as Cimɛun. Tuɣa aryaz-a nican d amsegged, ittraja afewwej n Israil uca tuɣa Arruḥ Iqeddsen xas.
\v 26 Tuɣa Arruḥ Iqeddsen iweḥḥa as-dd aqa war ittmetti ca qbeř i ɣa iẓar Lmasiḥ n SIDI.
\v 27 Yusa-dd ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant \add am t iɛarren\add* Arruḥ Iqeddsen, umi dd-udfen lwalidin s Uḥenjir Yasuɛ, ḥima ad as ggen ɛlaḥsab lqaɛida n Ccariɛa.
\v 28 Iksi t deg iɣaǧen nnes uca ibarek AREBBI, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 29 \qt “\tl A\tl* Sidi inu,\qt* \qt ejj amsexxar nnec\qt*
\m \qt ad iraḥ di řehna řexxu,\qt*
\m \qt ɛlaḥsab awař nnec,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:29 \xt Amz. 46:30. \x*
\m 
\v 30 \qt minzi tiṭṭawin inu ẓrint arreḥmet nnec,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:30 \xt Izhd. 98:2; Ica. 52:10. \x*
\m 
\v 31 \qt i tesswejded zzat i wudem n marra řegnus:\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:31 \xt Řex. 28:28. \x*
\m 
\v 32 \qt Tafawt i ɣa tᵉttwasargeb i řegnus\qt*
\m \qt d uɛuǧi i řgens nnec Israil!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:32 \xt Ica. 42:6; 49:6; Řex. 13:47. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 33 Itebhet Yusuf d yemmas s min xas ittwannan.
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* ibark i-ten Cimɛun, inna i Maryam yemmas:
\b
\m \qt “Aqa Wa immars i uweṭṭu d tnukra\qt*
\m \qt n waṭṭas di Israil\qt*
\m \qt u i řeɛřamet i ɣa ittwaɛekksen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:34 \xt Ica. 8:14; Rum. 9:32; 1 Bṭ. 2:8. \x*
\m 
\v 35 \qt Ad icuq ssif di řeɛmar nnem,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad dd-ttwasseḍharen ixarriṣen\qt*
\m \qt zeg waṭṭas n wuřawen.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 36 Ict n tnabit, \add qqaren as\add* Ḥanna, yeǧis n Fanwil, zi teqbič n Acir, tuɣa-tt uřa d nettat tewsar aṭṭas. Teddar ak-d weryaz nnes sebɛa n iseggʷusa zeg wami tt tuɣa \add ɛad\add* d taɛzarect.
\v 37 Tuɣa-tt d tajjač i yijj n řmijař n arebɛa u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa, war tᵉttbeɛɛid ca x Zzawect Tameqqrant. Tuɣa tɛebbed \add AREBBI\add* s uẓummi d tẓaǧit ǧiřet d wass. \x ◘ \xo 2:37 \xt 1 Ṣm. 1:22. \x*
\v 38 Ɣar tsaɛɛet nni tbedd nettat ɛawed, tᵉttṣebbaḥ i SIDI, tessawař xas ak-d marra inni ittrajan asenjem n Urcalim. \f ◼ \fr 2:38 \fk asenjem\ft - niɣ ‘asellak’.\f*
\m 
\v 39 Umi kemmřen nitni kuřci ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n SIDI, ɛeqben ɣar tendint nsen Nnaṣira di Ljalil.
\v 40 Tuɣa Aḥenjir iggam, yarenni dayes Arruḥ, idweř iccur s tiɣit, u arḍa n AREBBI aqa-t xas. \x ◘ \xo 2:40 \xt Lk. 1:80. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ di Zzawect Tameqqrant řami igga tenɛac n isseggʷusa
\m 
\v 41 Tuɣa řaǧ nnes ttraḥen kuř aseggʷas ɣar Urcalim di Řɛid n \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 2:41 \xt Uf. 23:15, 17; Lawi 23:5; Aɛwd. 16:1. \x*
\v 42 Umi ɣares yiweḍ tenɛac n iseggʷusa, geɛɛden ɣar Řɛid am mammec nnumen nitni.
\v 43 Awarni řami ɛdun wussan \add n Řɛid\add*, ɛeqben-dd, maca Aḥenjir, Yasuɛ, iqqim awarni asen di Urcalim, umi Yusuf d yemmas war argiben ca x man aya.
\v 44 Ittɣiř asen aqa-t jar imsebriden. Awarni řami uyuren ict n ticři n wass, arezzun xas jar řaǧ nsen d yinni ten issnen.
\v 45 Umi war t ufin, ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim, arezzun xas.
\v 46 Awarni třata n wussan ufin t di Zzawect Tameqqrant, tuɣa iqqim di řwesṭ n imesɣaren \add n Ccariɛa\add*, ittesřa ɣarsen, ittseqsa ten.
\v 47 Marra inni d as isřin tbehten di řefhamet d wawař i dd-ittarra. \x ◘ \xo 2:47 \xt Mt. 7:28; Mk. 1:22; Lk. 4:22, 32; Yḥ. 7:15. \x*
\v 48 Řami t ẓrin, tbehten. Tenna as yemmas: “\add A\add* Mmi, mayemmi d aneɣ teggid ammu? Aqa, babac d necc nedɛeq s tarezzut xak.”
\v 49 Inna asen: “Mayemmi xafi tarzum? Ma war targibem ca belli \add ittxeṣṣa ayi\add* ad iřiɣ di Taddart n Baba?”
\v 50 Maca war fhimen awař i d asen inna. \x ◘ \xo 2:50 \xt Lk. 9:45; 18:34. \x*
\v 51 Uca ihwa-dd akidsen ɣar Nnaṣira, tuɣa ittegg asen array. Maca yemmas txemmeř marra awařen-a deg wuř nnes.
\m 
\v 52 Uca tuɣa Yasuɛ yarenni di tiddi nnes d tiɣit nnes u di arḍa ɣar AREBBI d yewdan. \x ◘ \xo 2:52 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:26; Lk. 1:80. \x*
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss xemmesṭac zi řeḥkamet n qayṣar Tibaryus, řami tuɣa Punṭiyus Pilaṭus d řḥakem x Yahudiyya, u Hirudus d řḥakem x Ljalil, ijj n arbeɛ n temmurt, u Filippus, umas, d řḥakem x Ituriya d jjihet n Traxunitis, ijj n arbeɛ nneɣni n temmurt, u Lisanyus d řḥakem x jjihet n Abilini, \add tenni ɛawed\add* d ijj n arbeɛ nneɣni n temmurt, \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt [Mt. 3:1-12; Mk. 1:1-8; Yḥ. 1:19-28] \x*  *
\b
\m 
\v 2 umi tuɣa Ḥannan d Qayafa d arruyas n ikehhanen, aqa yusa-dd wawař n AREBBI x Yuḥanna, mmis n Zakariyya, di řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Řex. 4:6. \x*
\v 3 Yiweḍ-dd ɣar marra jjwayeh i d as dd-innḍen i L’Urdun, ittbarreḥ s useɣḍeṣ n ttubet i weɣfar n ddnub, \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Mt. 3:1; Mk. 1:4. \x*
\v 4 am mammec tura deg wedlis n wawařen n unabi Icaɛya i innan:
\b
\m \qt “Tmijja n wenni isɣuyyun di řexřa:\qt*
\m \qt Swejdem abrid n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt seggmem amesraq i AREBBI nneɣ di řewḍa.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Ica. 40:3-5; Mt. 3:3; Mk. 1:3; Yḥ. 1:23. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 \qt Marra tiddaɣin ad ttwaccurent,\qt*
\m \qt marra idurar d tewririn\qt*
\m \qt ad dd-ttwassehwan,\qt*
\m \qt ddmani ad ttwaseggment,\qt*
\m \qt u imucan iwɛaren ad dewřen d řewḍa.\qt*
\m 
\v 6 \qt Kuř ddat \tl s idammen d weysum\tl*\qt*
\m \qt ad tẓar Tudart n AREBBI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Izhd. 98:2; Ica. 40:3-5; 52:10. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 Tuɣa iqqar i řɣaci i dd-itteffɣen ḥima ad ttwassɣeḍṣen: “\add A\add* tarwa n iřefsawen, wi d awem imřen maḥend \add ad tarzum\add* ad tarewřem zeg weɣḍab i dd ɣa yasen? \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Mt. 3:7; 23:33. \x*
\v 8 S uya ggem řɣiǧet i ɣa iřiqqen i ttubet. War ttbeddam ad tinim deg ixef nwem: ‘Aqa ɣarneɣ Ibrahim d jedditneɣ!’, minzi Necc ad awem iniɣ, belli AREBBI izemmar ad issnekkar zeg iẓra-ya tarwa i Ibrahim. \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Mt. 3:9; Yḥ. 8:39; Řex. 13:26. \x*
\v 9 Xzar, aqa tᵉttwassars tcaqurt ɣar iẓewran n tcejjura. S uya kuř tacejjart i war itticen řɣiǧet tecna ad tᵉttwaqess uca ad tewḍa di tmessi.” \f ◼ \fr 3:9 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Mt. 3:10; 7:19. \x*
\m 
\v 10 Isseqsa t řɣaci, inna: “Min ɣa negg?” \x ◘ \xo 3:10 \xt Řex. 2:37. \x*
\v 11 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Ejj wenni ɣar iǧa tyuya n tcamirat, ad iwc i wenni war ɣar iǧi ca, u ejj wenni ɣar iǧa macca, ad igg amenni.” \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Yaɛ. 2:13, 15; 1 Yḥ. 3:17. \x*
\v 12 Usin-dd ɛawed ayt n ḍḍariba, ḥima ad ttwassɣeḍṣen, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, min ɣa negg?”
\v 13 Inna asen: “War ttᵉṭṭfem ḍḍariba ktar zi min d awem weṣṣan maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfem.”
\v 14 Sseqsan t ɛawed iɛeskariyyen, nnan as: “Min ɣa negg neccin?” Inna asen: “War tteggem řɣar uřa deg ijj, war deǧmem ḥed, qennɛem s řmunet nwem.”
\m 
\v 15 Am ibda řgens ad ittceř x Yuḥanna, u xarrṣen deg wuřawen nsen ma Yuḥanna netta d Lmasiḥ,
\v 16 xenni iṭṭef Yuḥanna deg wawař, inna asen: “Necc sseɣḍaṣeɣ kenniw deg waman, maca awarni ayi ad dd-yas wi ijehden xafi, wenni umi necc war sdihiǧeɣ uřa ad as fesyeɣ ifiřan n sandaliyat nnes. Aqa Netta ad kenniw isseɣḍeṣ di Arruḥ Iqeddsen u di tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt Ica. 44:3; Yuw. 3:1; Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:8; Yḥ. 1:26; Řex. 1:5; 11:16; 2:4; 11:15; 19:4. \x*
\v 17 Netta ɣares tazzart deg ufus nnes uca ad issizdeg andrar nnes. Ad issmun irden ɣar řmarsi nnes, maca icarfa ad ten issecmeḍ s tmessi war ixsin ɛemmarṣ.” \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt Mt. 3:12. \x*
\m 
\v 18 S tmesřayin nneɣni ɛad aṭṭas tuɣa isseřmad \add iwdan\add* uca ittbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan i řgens.
\v 19 Maca umi iɛayar Yuḥanna Hirudus, řḥakem x ijj n arbeɛ n temmurt, zi ssibbet n Hirudiyya tamɣart n Filippus umas, u zi ssibbet n marra tuɛeffna i igga, \x ◘ \xo 3:19 \xt Mt. 14:3; Mk. 6:18. \x*
\v 20 aqa yarni \add Hirudus\add* ɛawed di man aya marra, řami tuɣa iḥebbes Yuḥanna \add Amseɣḍaṣ\add*.
\b
\s1 Aseɣḍeṣ n Yasuɛ s ufus n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ
\m 
\v 21 Awarni řami isseɣḍeṣ \add Yuḥanna\add* marra řgens, isseɣḍeṣ ɛawed Yasuɛ, uca am tuɣa Wanita ittẓaǧa, innurzem ujenna, \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt [Mt. 3:13-17; Mk. 1:9-11] — Mt. 3:13; Mk. 1:9; Yḥ. 1:32. \x*
\v 22 uca ihwa-dd xas Arruḥ Iqeddsen s ṣṣifet n ddat n tedbirt. Uca ict n tmijja zeg ujenna tuɣa teqqar: “Cek d Mmi iɛizzen, dayek ufiɣ arḍa inu.” \x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Ica. 42:1; Mt. 17:5; Mk. 9:7; Lk. 9:35; Kul. 1:13; 2 Bṭ. 1:17. \x*
\b
\s1 Taṣiřet n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ
\m 
\v 23 Tuɣa Yasuɛ ɣares ɛřaḥař třatin n iseggʷusa u ittɣiř asen aqa Netta d mmis n Yusuf, mmis n Hayli, \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt [Mt. 1:1-17] — Mt. 13:55; Yḥ. 6:42. \x*
\v 24 mmis n Mattat, mmis n Lawi, mmis n Malki, mmis n Yanna, mmis n Yusuf,
\v 25 mmis n Mattata, mmis n Ɛamus, mmis n Naḥum, mmis n Ḥasli, mmis n Najjay,
\v 26 mmis n Maɛat, mmis n Mattat, mmis n Cimɛi, mmis n Yusuf, mmis n Yahuda,
\v 27 mmis n Yuḥanna, mmis n Risa, mmis n Zarubbabil, mmis n Caɛaltiyil, mmis n Niri,
\v 28 mmis n Malki, mmis n Addi, mmis n Quṣam, mmis n Almudam, mmis n Ɛir,
\v 29 mmis n Yusi, mmis n Aliɛazar, mmis n Yuram, mmis n Matita, mmis n Lawi,
\v 30 mmis n Cimɛun, mmis n Yahuda, mmis n Yusuf, mmis n Yunam, mmis n Alyaqim,
\v 31 mmis n Maliya, mmis n Miynan, mmis n Mattata, mmis n Natan, mmis n Dawud,
\v 32 mmis n Yassa, mmis n Ɛubid, mmis n Buɛaz, mmis n Salmun, mmis n Naḥcun,
\v 33 mmis n Ɛamminadab, mmis n Aram, mmis n Ḥaṣrun, mmis n Fariṣ, mmis n Yahuda,
\v 34 mmis n Yaɛqub, mmis n Isḥaq, mmis n Ibrahim, mmis n Taraḥ, mmis n Naḥur, \x ◘ \xo 3:34 \xt Amz. 11:10. \x*
\v 35 mmis n Saruj, mmis n Raɛuw, mmis n Falaj, mmis n Ɛabir, mmis n Calaḥ,
\v 36 mmis n Qinan, mmis n Arfakcad, mmis n Cam, mmis n Nuḥ, mmis n Lamak,
\v 37 mmis n Matucalaḥ, mmis n Ḥanux, mmis n Yarad, mmis n Mahalal-Il, mmis n Qinan,
\v 38 mmis n Anuc, mmis n Cit, mmis n Adam, mmis n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:38 \xt Amz. 5:3. \x*
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Ajarreb n Yasuɛ di řexřa
\m 
\v 1 Yasuɛ iɛqeb-dd zi L’Urdun am tuɣa iccur s Arruḥ Iqeddsen uca Arruḥ indeh i-t ɣar řexřa, \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt [Mt. 4:1-11; Mk. 1:12-13] — Mt. 4:1; Mk. 1:12. \x*
\v 2 ḥima ad ittwajarreb zeg ibřis arebɛin n wussan. War icci walu deg wussan nni uca awarni řami ɛdun \add wussan nni\add*, iṭṭef i-t řaẓ ɣar uneggar. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt Uf. 34:28; 1 Ij. 19:8. \x*
\m 
\v 3 Inna as ibřis: “Mařa Cek d mmis n AREBBI, ini i weẓru-ya ad idweř d aɣrum.”
\v 4 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ, inna: “Aqa tura: ‘Bnadem war iddar s weɣrum waha, maca s kuř awař n AREBBI.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt Aɛwd. 8:3; Mt. 4:4. \x*
\m 
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed i-t cciṭan ɣar ijj n wedrar yuɛřan, isscen as marra tigeldiwin n ddunect deg ijjen wermac.
\v 6 Inna as ibřis: “Ad ac wceɣ ṣṣulṭa-ya marra d uɛuǧi nnes, minzi i necc umi temmewc u tticeɣ \add tt\add* i umi xseɣ.
\v 7 Mařa tɛebded ayi, ad ɣarek yiři marra aya.”
\v 8 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ, inna as: “Aqa tura: ‘SIDI, AREBBI nnec, umi ɣa tsejded u i Netta weḥḥdes umi ɣa tsexxared.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Aɛwd. 6:13; 10:20; 1 Ṣm. 7:3. \x*
\m 
\v 9 Yiwyi t ɣar Urcalim uca issbedd i-t ɣar ṭṭarf n tzeqqa n Zzawect Tameqqrant, inna as: “Mařa Cek d Mmis n AREBBI, nḍar Ixef nnec ssa ɣar wadday,
\v 10 minzi tura: ‘Ad yumur lmalakat nnes xak maḥend ad Cek ḥḍant,
\v 11 aqa x ifassen nsent ad Cek ksint, ḥima aḍar nnec war ineggeḥ ca aẓru.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Izhd. 91:11, 12. \x*
\v 12 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ inna as: “Aqa ittwanna: ‘War ttjarrab SIDI, AREBBI nnec.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Aɛwd. 6:16. \x*
\m 
\v 13 Umi ikemmeř ibřis marra ajarreb nnes, yuyur xas ca n řweqt.
\b
\s1 Anabi war iǧi d ameqbuř di tendint nnes
\m 
\v 14 Iɛqeb-dd Yasuɛ s jjehd n Arruḥ ɣar Ljalil, uca iffeɣ řexbar xas di marra jjwayeh i d asen dd-innḍen. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt [Mt. 4:12-17; 13:53-58; Mk. 1:14-15; 6:1-6] — Mt. 4:12; Mk. 1:14; Yḥ. 4:43; Řex. 10:37. \x*
\v 15 Tuɣa isseřmad di temzidawin nsen, ssɛuǧan t \add iwdan\add* marra.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Yusa-dd ɣar Nnaṣira mani tuɣa ittwarebba, uca yudef ɣar temzida \add n Wudayen\add* deg wass n ssebt ɛlaḥsab tanamit nnes, uca ikkar, ḥima ad issɣar. \x ◘ \xo 4:16 \xt [Naḥ. 8:4, 5; Mt. 13:54; Mk. 6:1; Yḥ. 4:43] \x*
\v 17 Immewc as adlis ittwannḍen n unabi Icaɛya, uca yarzem Yasuɛ adlis ittwanḍen, yufa amcan mani tura:
\b
\m 
\v 18 \qt “Arruḥ n SIDI xafi,\qt*
\m \qt minzi Netta idhen ayi\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad barrḥeɣ\qt*
\m \qt s Řexbar Aṣebḥan i imezřaḍ,\qt*
\m \qt issekk ayi-dd ḥima ad ssgenfiɣ\qt*
\m \qt inni umi yarẓ wuř,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad barrḥeɣ i imeḥbas s usarreḥ,\qt*
\m \qt i idarɣařen s řxeẓrat,\qt*
\m \qt u ḥima ad ssfewwjeɣ inni ittwarẓen\qt*
\m \qt s weɣfar \tl n ddnub nsen\tl*,\qt*
\m 
\v 19 \qt ḥima ad barrḥeɣ s useggʷas n arḍa n SIDI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Ica. 42:7; 61:1, 2; Mt. 11:5. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 20 Xenni yenneḍ adlis, iwca i-t i umsexxar, iqqim, am dayes nḍaren tiṭṭawin nsen marra inni tuɣa di temzida.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ibda iqqar asen: “Aqa ass-a ttwakemmřent Tira-ya \add Iqeddsen\add* deg imezzuɣen nwem.”
\m 
\v 22 Tuɣa marra cehhden xas, tbehten s wawařen n arḍa i dd-iffɣen zeg uqemmum nnes, uca nnan: “Ma war iǧi wa d mmis n Yusuf?” \x ◘ \xo 4:22 \xt Ica. 50:4; Mt. 13:54; Mk. 6:2; Lk. 2:47; Yḥ. 6:42. \x*
\v 23 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Nican ad ayi tinim lmatal-a: ‘\add A\add* Aḍbib, sgenfa Yixef nnec! Mecḥař nesřa belli ijra di Kafarnaḥum, egg man aya ɛawed di tendint nnec.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:23 \xt Mt. 4:13. \x*
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* inna: “S tidett, ad awem iniɣ, war iǧi unabi d ameqbuř di temmurt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:24 \xt Mt. 13:57; Mk. 6:4; Yḥ. 4:44. \x*
\v 25 S tidett ad awem iniɣ: Tuɣa din tijjař aṭṭas di taddart n Israil deg wussan n Iliya umi ittwabelleɛ ujenna třata n iseggʷusa d setta n iyuren, ařami tuɣa řaẓ imɣar di temmurt marra.
\v 26 War dd-ittwassekk Iliya uřa ɣar icten zzaysent, mɣir ɣar Ṣarfat \add i iǧan di jjwayeh\add* n Ṣaydun, ɣar ict n tajjač.
\v 27 Tuɣa din di Israil di řweqt n unabi Ilicaɛ aṭṭas n iwdan i di iǧa řbarṣ, uca uřa d ijj zzaysen war ittwassizdig mɣir Naɛman zi Aram waha.” \x ◘ \xo 4:27 \xt 2 Ij. 5:14. \x*
\m 
\v 28 Umi sřin aya, ttwaccuren marra \add inni iǧan\add* di temzida, s tefqeḥt.
\v 29 Kkaren, ssuffɣen t barra i tendint, iwyen t ɣar tqiccet n wedrar i xef tuɣa tebna tendint nsen, ḥima ad t nḍaren zi jjarf yuɛřan.
\v 30 Maca Netta icuq di řwesṭ nsen, iruḥ.
\b
\s1 Asuffuɣ n ijj n řaryaḥ amengus
\m 
\v 31 Ihwa ɣar Kafarnaḥum, ict n tendint di Ljalil, tuɣa isseřmad i-ten deg wussan n ssebt. \x ◘ \xo 4:31 \xt [Mk. 1:21-28] — Mt. 4:13; Mk. 1:21. \x*
\v 32 Tbehten s useřmed nnes, minzi awař nnes tuɣa t s ṣṣulṭa. \x ◘ \xo 4:32 \xt Mt. 7:29; Mk. 1:22. \x*
\v 33 Tuɣa di temzida ijj n weryaz dayes buḥbeř n ijj n cciṭan amengus. Netta isɣuyyu s jjehd aṭṭas, \x ◘ \xo 4:33 \xt Mk. 1:23. \x*
\v 34 inna: “Tewwej \add xafi\add*! Min din jar aneɣ akidek, \add a\add* Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri? Ma tusid-dd \add da\add* ḥima ad aneɣ tᵉteḥḥid? Necc ssneɣ min teɛnid, aqa Cek d Amqeddas n AREBBI.”
\v 35 Iwebbex i-t Yasuɛ, inna as: “Sqar, ffeɣ-dd zzayes!” Inḍar i-t cciṭan di řwesṭ, iffeɣ zzayes, břa ma ad as issexsar ca.
\v 36 Yarsa utebhet x marra, uca bdan ssawařen jar asen, nnan: “Mana awař-a? Aqa s ṣṣulṭa d jjehd ittamar řaryaḥ imengas, uca ffɣen!”
\v 37 Iffeɣ-dd xas řexbar ɣar marra jjwayeh i d as dd-innḍen.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n tḍekkwač n Buṭrus
\m 
\v 38 Řami dd-iffeɣ Yasuɛ zi temzida, yudef ɣar taddart n Cimɛun. Tuɣa taḍekkʷač n Cimɛun dayes timessi aṭṭas u ttaren zzayes di ṭṭweɛ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:38 \xt [Mt. 8:14-17; Mk. 1:29-34] — Mt. 8:14; Mk. 1:29. \x*
\v 39 Iɣnes xas uca iwebbex timessi uca tejja xas \add tmessi\add*. Řexdenni tekkar, tedweř tᵉttsexxar xasen.
\m 
\v 40 Řami teɣři tfuct, iwyen-dd ɣares marra inni tuɣa ɣar iǧa imehřac i di iǧa ɛřam kuř řehřacat. Uca Netta issars afus nnes x kuř ijjen zzaysen, issgenfa i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 4:40 \xt Mt. 8:16; Mk. 1:32; 7:32; 8:23, 25. \x*
\v 41 Tuɣa ccwaṭen tteffɣen-dd ɛawed zeg waṭṭas idsen, tuɣa sɣuyyun, qqaren: “Cek d Lmasiḥ Mmis n AREBBI!” \add Maca\add* iwebbex i-ten, war ten ijji ad ssiwřen, minzi ssnen belli Netta d Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 4:41 \xt Mk. 1:34; 3:11. \x*
\b
\s1 Abarreḥ n Yasuɛ di temzidawin n Ljalil
\m 
\v 42 Řami tuɣa d aziř, iffeɣ-dd, iruḥ ɣar ijj n wemcan ixřan, tuɣa řɣaci yarezzu xas, usin-dd ɣares uca arezzun ad t mennɛen, ḥima war xasen ittriḥ. \x ◘ \xo 4:42 \xt [Mk. 1:35-39] — Mk. 1:35. \x*
\v 43 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Aqa ittxeṣṣa ayi ad barrḥeɣ ɛawed i tneddam nneɣni s Tgeldit n AREBBI, minzi i man aya umi dd-ttwassekkeɣ.”
\v 44 Uca ittbarreḥ di temzidawin n Ljalil.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Tařaɣit n Yasuɛ x imeḥḍaren imezwura
\m 
\v 1 Ařami xas imun řɣaci ḥima ad sřen i Wawař n AREBBI, \add am\add* tuɣa Netta ibedd x tma n řebḥar n Jinnisaret, \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt [Mt. 4:18-22; Mk. 1:16-20] — Mt. 13:2; Mk. 4:1. \x*
\v 2 iẓra tnayen n tɣarruba beddent x tma n řebḥar. Ineymaren n iseřman ffɣen-dd zzayes, tuɣa ssirden tiracciwin.
\v 3 Icten zi tɣarruba nni tuɣa n Cimɛun Buṭrus. Inya Yasuɛ di tɣarrabut, isseqsa ten ad aggʷejen cwayt x tma n řbař ɣar řebḥar. Xenni iqqim, isseřmad řɣaci zi tɣarrabut.
\m 
\v 4 Umi ikemmeř awař, inna i Cimɛun: “Ruḥem ɣar řaǧaɣ, nḍarem tiracciwin nwem i tneymart.”
\v 5 Yarra-dd Cimɛun, inna as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, aqa nuḥeř ǧiřet tekmeř, war neymar walu, maca x wawař nnec ad nḍareɣ tracca.”
\v 6 Umi ggin man aya, ṭṭfen aṭṭas n iseřman ařami dewřent tracciwin nsen ttcarragent.
\v 7 Aqa ciyyaren ɣar imeddukkař nsen inni tuɣa di tɣarrabut nneɣni, ḥima ad dd-asen ad ten ɛawnen. Nitni usin-dd, uca ccuren tnayen n tɣarruba ařami ɛřayen ad ɣarqent.
\m 
\v 8 Ařami iẓra Cimɛun Buṭrus man aya, iwḍa ɣar iḍaren n Yasuɛ, inna as: “Ttzawgeɣ Cek, a Sidi, aggʷej xafi, aqa necc d bnadem d amednub.”
\v 9 Itebhet netta d marra inni iǧan akides x tneymart n iseřman i ṭṭfen,
\v 10 uřa d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna, tarwa n Zabdi, inni tuɣa d icricen n Cimɛun. \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna i Cimɛun: “War tteggʷed ca, zi ssa d tsawent ad tafed tyemmared iwdan i usenjem.” \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Irm. 16:16; Ḥiz. 47:9; Mt. 4:19; Mk. 1:17. \x*
\v 11 Nitni iwyen-dd tiɣarruba ɣar řbarr, jjin kuřci uca ḍfaren t. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Mt. 4:20; 19:27; Mk. 10:28; Lk. 18:28. \x*
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n weryaz i di iǧa řbarṣ
\m 
\v 12 Umi tuɣa Yasuɛ deg icten zi tneddam \add nni\add*, yusa-dd \add ɣares\add* ijj n weryaz iřqef i-t marra řbarṣ. Umi iẓra netta Yasuɛ, iwḍa x uɣembub nnes uca izaweg i-t, inna: “A Sidi inu, mařa texsed, tzemmared ad ayi tessizdeged!” \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt [Mt. 8:1-4; Mk. 1:40-45] — Mt. 8:2; Mk. 1:40. \x*
\v 13 Isswiẓẓeḍ Yasuɛ s ufus nnes ɣares, iḥada t, inna: “Necc xseɣ, iři tizdiged!” Řexdenni iruḥ xas řbarṣ.
\v 14 Yumur i-t: “War teqqar i ḥed, maca ruḥ, scen ixef nnec i ukehhan, ewc tawhibt x usizdeg nnec, am mammec \add t\add* yumur Musa, d cchadet i nitni.” \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Lawi 13:2; 14:2; Mt. 8:4. \x*
\v 15 Ccenɛet nnes tuyur mani ma ktar ɛad uca inneyru řɣaci aṭṭas, ḥima ad as sřen u ḥima ad zzayes ttwassgenfan zi řehřacat nsen.
\v 16 Maca Netta iffeɣ-dd ɣar řexřa, ittẓaǧa din.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n weryaz d aneɛḍab
\m 
\v 17 Deg ijj n wass zeg wussan nni am tuɣa Yasuɛ isseřmad, qqimen \add din\add* Ifarisiyyen d imseřmaden n Ccariɛa inni dd-yusin zi marra dcurat n Ljalil d Yahudiyya u zi Urcalim. Tuɣa din jjehd n SIDI maḥend ad ten iggenfa. \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt [Mt. 9:1-8; Mk. 2:1-12] \x*
\v 18 Xenni iwyen-dd ijj n uneɛḍab x tassut tuɣa arezzun ad t ssidfen ɣar daxeř, maḥend ad t ssarsen zzates. \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Mt. 9:1; Mk. 2:3; Řex. 9:33. \x*
\v 19 Umi war ufin manis t i ɣa ssidfen zi ssibbet n řɣaci, geɛɛden x tzeqqa uca seyyben t zeg uqarmud ɣar wadday ak-d tassut \add nican\add* ɣar řwesṭ, zzat i Yasuɛ.
\v 20 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ l’iman nsen, inna i uneɛḍab nni: “\add A\add* bnadem, ddnub nnec ttwaɣfaren ac.”
\m 
\v 21 Bdan imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen ttxarraṣen, nnan: “Min iɛna Wa, řami Netta ittceqqaf \add ammu\add*. Wi izemmaren ad iɣfar ddnub mɣir AREBBI weḥḥdes?” \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Izhd. 32:5; Ica. 43:25. \x*
\v 22 \add Maca\add* yargeb Yasuɛ x ixarriṣen nsen, uca Netta iṭṭef deg wawař, inna asen: “Min tᵉttxarraṣem deg wuřawen nwem?
\v 23 Min ihewnen ad iniɣ: ‘Ttwaɣfaren ddnub nnec!’ niɣ ad iniɣ: ‘Kkar, uyur’?
\v 24 Maca ḥima ad tessnem belli Mmis n bnadem ɣares ṣṣulṭa x temmurt, ḥima ad iɣfar ddnub - inna i uneɛḍab - I cek umi ɣa iniɣ, kkar, ksi tassut nnec uca ruḥ ɣar taddart nnec!”
\v 25 Řexdenni ikkar zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, iksi tassut nnes uca iruḥ ɣar taddart nnes, issemɣara di AREBBI.
\v 26 Atebhet ihwa-dd x marra iwdan, ssemɣaran di AREBBI uca tudef i-ten tiggʷudi, nnan: “Aqa ass-a neẓra řeɛjayeb!”
\b
\s1 Tařaɣit n Yasuɛ x Matta Lawi
\m 
\v 27 Awarni man aya iffeɣ Yasuɛ, iẓra ijj n bu-ḍḍariba, qqaren as Lawi, iqqim deg wemcan n ḍḍariba, inna as: “Ḍfar ayi-dd!” \x ◘ \xo 5:27 \xt [Mt. 9:9-13; Mk. 2:13-17] — Mt. 9:9; Mk. 2:14, 15. \x*
\v 28 Ijja kuřci, ikkar uca iḍfar i-t-i-dd.
\m 
\v 29 Issnewji as Lawi ijj n usnewji d ameqqran di taddart nnes, uca inni akides iqqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* tuɣa aten deg waṭṭas n řɣaci zeg ayt n ḍḍariba d inneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 5:29 \xt Mt. 9:10; Mk. 2:15; Lk. 15:1. \x*
\v 30 \add Maca\add* imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen cetcan, nnan i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Mayemmi tᵉttettem, tessessem ak-d ayt n ḍḍariba d imednab?”
\v 31 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Inni iṣeḥḥen war ḥdijen ca aḍbib, maca imehřac wah.
\v 32 War dd-usiɣ ad řaɣiɣ x imseggaden, maca x imednab ɣar ttubet.” \x ◘ \xo 5:32 \xt Mt. 9:13; Lk. 19:10; 1 Tim. 1:15. \x*
\b
\s1 Aseqsi x uẓummi
\m 
\v 33 Nnan as: “Mayemmi tẓumman u ttẓaǧan imeḥḍaren n Yuḥanna aṭṭas, uřa d yinni n Ifarisiyyen, maca inni nnec ttᵉtten, sessen?” \x ◘ \xo 5:33 \xt [Mt. 9:14-17; Mk. 2:18-22] — Mt. 9:14. \x*
\v 34 Inna asen: “Ma texsem ad tejjem ayt n umuřay ad ẓummen mařa Amuřay aqa-t \add ɛad\add* akidsen! \x ◘ \xo 5:34 \xt Ica. 62:5; 2 Kur. 11:2. \x*
\v 35 Maca ad dd-awḍen wussan xmi xasen ɣa ittwammeksi Umuřay, řexdenni ad ẓummen deg wussan nni.”
\m 
\v 36 Inna asen ɛawed ijj n umedya: “War din ḥed icarreg taneqqič zeg warruḍ n jdid, uca ittegg i-tt x warruḍ abuřay, ḥima war tᵉttarri tneqqič n jdid ad tcarreg abuřay, minzi taneqqič n jdid war tᵉttřiqi abuřay.
\v 37 Uca war iǧi ḥed ittegg binu n jdid di txuncay tiqdimin n yiřem, ḥima binu n jdid war ittcarrig ca tixuncay uca ad izeǧeɛ binu, ad ḍeyyɛent txuncay. \x ◘ \xo 5:37 \xt Mt. 9:17; Mk. 2:22. \x*
\v 38 Maca tteggen binu n jdid di txuncay n jdid uca ad xemmřen s tyuya.
\v 39 Uřa d ijj, mařa iswa aqdim, war ittexs ɛad řexdenni jdid, minzi netta ad yini: ‘Aqdim ittfuḥ!’”
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Yasuɛ d Bab n ssebt
\m 
\v 1 Imsar di ssebt aqa Yasuɛ yuyur deg iyyaren n zzariɛet n imendi. Tuɣa imeḥḍaren nnes řeqqḍen tidrin, ttḥekkan tent s ifassen nsen, ttᵉtten \add tent\add*. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt [Mt. 12:1-8; Mk. 2:23-28] — Aɛwd. 23:24; Mt. 12:1; Mk. 2:23. \x*
\v 2 Ca n Ifarisiyyen nnan asen: “Mayemmi tᵉtteggem min war iḥeǧřen ad ittwagg di ssebt?” \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Uf. 20:10. \x*
\v 3 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ma war teɣrim min igga Dawud umi iǧuẓ netta d yinni akides? \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt 1 Ṣm. 21:1-6\x*
\v 4 Mammec yudef ɣar Taddart n AREBBI, iksi aɣrum n wescan i iǧan x tzewḍa n SIDI i war iḥeǧřen macca nnes mɣir i ikehhanen waha, uca icca \add zzayes\add* u iwca ɛawed i yinni tuɣa iǧan akides?”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna asen: “Aqa Mmis n bnadem d Bab n ssebt.” \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Mt. 12:8; Mk. 2:28. \x*
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n weryaz deg wass n ssebt
\m 
\v 6 Deg ijj n \add wass n\add* ssebt nneɣni yudef \add Yeccu\add* ɣar temzida, ibda issɣara. Tuɣa din ijj n bnadem wenni umi afus nnes iqucceḥ. \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt [Mt. 12:9-14; Mk. 3:1-6] — Mt. 12:9; Mk. 3:1. \x*
\v 7 Ḥḍan t imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen, ma ad issgenfa di ssebt, ḥima ad xas afen ca n ttuhmet.
\v 8 Maca Netta yargeb x ixarriṣen nsen uca inna i bnadem wenni umi iqucceḥ ufus nnes: “Kkar, bedd di řwesṭ n temzida.” Umi ikkar u tuɣa ibedd \add din\add*,
\v 9 inna asen Yasuɛ: “Ad kenniw sseqsiɣ x min iḥeǧřen ad ittwagg di ssebt. \add Ma iḥeǧeř i bnadem maḥend\add* ad igg řxar niɣ řɣar, ad issenjem ijj n řeɛmar niɣ ad \add t\add* yareddeǧ?”
\v 10 Tuɣa ixezzar ɣar marra inni d as dd-innḍen, inna as \add i bnadem nni\add*: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec!” Isswiẓẓeḍ Netta afus nnes uca idweř ufus nnes iṣeḥḥ am wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt 1 Ij. 13:6; Mt. 12:13; Mk. 3:5\x*
\v 11 \add Maca\add* nitni dewřen ccuren s zzɛaf uca ssiwřen jar asen x min ɣa ggen i Yasuɛ.
\b
\s1 Řixḍaret n tenɛac n rrusul
\m 
\v 12 Imsar deg wussan nni, aqa iffeɣ Yasuɛ ɣar ijj n wedrar, ḥima ad iẓẓaǧ uca isseɛdu din ǧiřet tekmeř, ittẓaǧa i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt [Mt. 10:1-4; Mk. 3:13-19] \x*
\v 13 Umi tuɣa d aziř, iřaɣa-dd i imeḥḍaren nnes, uca ixḍar zzaysen tenɛac, isemma ten rrusul. \f ◼ \fr 6:13 \fk rrusul\ft - niɣ ‘imazanen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:13 \xt Mt. 10:1; Mk. 3:13; 6:7; Lk. 9:1. \x*
\v 14 Cimɛun, wenni ittkennan Buṭrus, \add ‘aẓru’\add*, d Andrawus umas, d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna, d Filippus d Bar-Tulumawus
\v 15 d Matta d Tuma d Yaɛqub, mmis n Ḥalfa, d Cimɛun wenni umi ttkennan ‘Amɛessab’,
\v 16 Yahuda, mmis n Yaɛqub, d Yahuda Isxariyuṭi wenni iǧan d aɣeddar.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ isseřmad u issgenfa
\m 
\v 17 Ihwa-dd Yasuɛ akidsen uca ibedd di řewḍa. Tuɣa akides ijj n ubarru n imeḥḍaren nnes d ijj n ubarru n iwdan zi marra Yahudiyya d Urcalim u zi tma n řebḥar ɣar Ṣur d Ṣaydun. \x ◘ \xo 6:17 \xt [Mt. 4:23-25; 5:1-12] — Mt. 4:25; Mk. 3:7. \x*
\v 18 Nitni usin-dd ḥima ad as sřen u ad ttwassgenfan zi řehřac nsen, \add tuɣa akidsen\add* uřa d inni ittwaɣezzan zi řaryaḥ imengas, uca ttwassgenfan.
\v 19 Marra řɣaci tuɣa ittexs ad t iḥada, minzi tuɣa itteffeɣ-dd zzayes jjehd nni issgenfan kuřci. \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt Mk. 5:30. \x*
\b
\s1 Lbaraka d nneɛřet
\m 
\v 20 Issgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar imeḥḍaren nnes, inna:
\b
\m \qt “Sseɛd nwem, \tl kenniw, a\tl* imezřaḍ,\qt*
\m \qt minzi Tageldit n AREBBI i kenniw.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt Mt. 5:2. \x*
\m 
\v 21 \qt Sseɛd nwem, \tl kenniw,\tl* inni iǧuẓen řexxu,\qt*
\m \qt minzi kenniw ad tᵉttwassjiwnem.\qt*
\m \qt Sseɛd nwem, \tl kenniw,\tl* inni ittrun řexxu,\qt*
\m \qt minzi kenniw ad tḍeḥcem.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 6:21 \xt Ica. 61:3; 65:13; 66:10. \x*
\m 
\v 22 \qt Sseɛd nwem, umi kenniw carrhen iwdan,\qt*
\m \qt ttaẓẓřen xawem, ttekkwaren kenniw,\qt*
\m \qt uca ssfeṭṭaḥen zeg yisem nwem\qt*
\m \qt x ssibbet n Mmis n bnadem.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 6:22 \xt Mt. 5:11; 1 Bṭ. 2:19; 3:14; 4:14. \x*
\m 
\v 23 \qt Farḥem deg wass nni, negzem s řefraḥet,\qt*
\m \qt minzi, aqa řajar nwem imɣar deg ujenna,\qt*
\m \qt minzi ammu tuɣa tteggen\qt*
\m \qt řejdud nsen deg inabiyyen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 6:23 \xt Řex. 5:41; 7:51. \x*
\m 
\v 24 \qt Maca uct xawem, \tl kenniw,\tl* aytbab n wagřa,\qt*
\m \qt minzi aqa tᵉṭṭfem afewwej nwem.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 6:24 \xt Ɛam. 6:1, 8. \x*
\m 
\v 25 \qt Uct xawem, \tl kenniw,\tl* inni ijjiwnen,\qt*
\m \qt minzi ad tǧaẓem.\qt*
\m \qt Uct xawem, \tl kenniw\tl* inni iḍeḥḥcen řexxu,\qt*
\m \qt minzi ad tceḍnem, ad trum.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 6:25 \xt Ica. 65:13; Yaɛ. 4:9; 5:1. \x*
\m 
\v 26 \qt Uct xawem umi iwdan ad xawem ssiwřen mliḥ,\qt*
\m \qt minzi ammu tuɣa tteggen řejdud nsen\qt*
\m \qt ak-d inabiyyen issxarriqen.”\qt*
\b
\s1 Tayri i řɛedyan
\m 
\v 27 “Maca Necc ad awem iniɣ, i yinni ittesřan: Xsem řɛedyan nwem, thillam deg inni kenniw icarrhen, \x ◘ \xo 6:27 \xt [Mt. 5:38-48; 7:12] — Uf. 23:4; Awřn. 25:21; Mt. 5:44; Rum. 12:20; 1 Kur. 4:12. \x*
\v 28 barkem i yinni kenniw ineɛɛřen u ẓaǧem x yinni xawem ittɛeddan. \x ◘ \xo 6:28 \xt Lk. 23:34; Řex. 7:60. \x*
\v 29 I wenni cek iwtin ɣar umeggiz, arr as-dd s wenneɣni, u wenni d ac ɣa ikksen ajeǧab, war t ttᵉṭṭef ad iksi uřa d tcamir nnec. \x ◘ \xo 6:29 \xt Mt. 5:40; 1 Kur. 6:7. \x*
\v 30 Marra wenni d ac ɣa ittaren, ewc as t, u wenni i ɣa iksin min iǧan nnec, war d as \add t\add* ttᵉttar. \x ◘ \xo 6:30 \xt Aɛwd. 15:7; Mt. 5:42. \x*
\v 31 Am mammec texsed ad awem ggen iwdan, ggem uřa d kenniw daysen amenni. \x ◘ \xo 6:31 \xt Mt. 7:12. \x*
\v 32 Mařa texsem ɣar yinni kenniw ittexsen, man tcuni i ɣarwem. Aqa uřa d imednab ttexsen inni i ten ittexsen. \x ◘ \xo 6:32 \xt Mt. 5:46. \x*
\v 33 Mařa teggem řxar i yinni d awem itteggen řxar, man tcuni i ɣarwem. Aqa uřa d imednab tteggen amenni.
\v 34 U mařa tarḍřem i iwdan i zi tᵉttrajam ad awem dd-arren, man tcuni i ɣarwem? Aqa uřa d imednab arḍřen i imednab, ḥima ad asen dd-idweř amenni ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 6:34 \xt Aɛwd. 15:8; Mt. 5:42. \x*
\v 35 Maca xsem řɛedyan nwem, ggem d asen tcuni, arḍřem, war tqeṭṭɛem řayas i ca n yijjen. Xenni ad yiři řajar nwem imɣar, ad tiřim d tarwa n Umɛuǧi x kuřci, minzi aqa ittegg s ttasiɛ n řxaḍar ak-d iɛeffanen d yinni war t icekkaren. \x ◘ \xo 6:35 \xt Mt. 5:45. \x*
\m 
\v 36 Areḥmem am mammec iǧa Babatwem d arḥim.
\v 37 War ḥekkem, war tᵉttwaḥakamem. War ttḥasabem, war tᵉttwaḥasbem. Ɣfarem, ad awem ittwaɣfar. \x ◘ \xo 6:37 \xt Mt. 7:1; Rum. 2:1; 1 Kur. 4:5. \x*
\m 
\v 38 Wcem, ad awem immewc, ad nḍaren ijj n řmud icna, ideqqes, ittwassenhezz, ifeyyeḍ deg weḥsin nwem. Minzi s řmud i zi ɣa tweznem kenniw, ad zzayes tᵉttwaweznem uřa d kenniw.” \x ◘ \xo 6:38 \xt Awřn. 10:22; 19:17; Mt. 7:2; Mk. 4:24. \x*
\s1 Amedya n uxecciw d teḥnact
\m 
\v 39 Netta inna asen ijj n umedya: “Ma izemmar udarɣař ad indeh adarɣař? Ma war weṭṭin s tnayen idsen deg weḥfur? \x ◘ \xo 6:39 \xt [Mt. 7:1-5] — Ica. 42:19; Mt. 15:14. \x*
\v 40 Ameḥḍar war iǧi ca ḥsen zeg umseřmad nnes, maca kuř ameḥḍar nican ad yiři am umseřmad nnes. \x ◘ \xo 6:40 \xt Mt. 10:24; Yḥ. 13:16; 15:20. \x*
\v 41 Mayemmi txezzared ɣar uxecciw, tenni di tiṭṭ n umac, maca taḥnact, tenni di tiṭṭ nnec, war kis teřhid? \x ◘ \xo 6:41 \xt Mt. 7:3. \x*
\v 42 Mammec tᵉttegged teqqared i umac: ‘Uma, ejj ayi ad ac dd-ssuffɣeɣ axecciw i dayek di tiṭṭ nnec!’, u xzar, cek simant nnec war tᵉttwiřid ca taḥnact i ɣarek di tiṭṭ nnec. \add Cek, a\add* amnafeq, suffeɣ-dd amezwaru taḥnact nni ɣarek di tiṭṭ nnec, xenni ad tᵉttwařid \add mliḥ\add* maḥend ad tessuffɣed axecciw zi tiṭṭ n umac.”
\b
\s1 Tacejjart d řɣiǧet nnes
\m 
\v 43 “War din bu tcejjart taṣebḥant i dd-issɣemmayen řɣiǧet texsar, niɣ tacejjart ixsaren i dd-issɣemmayen řɣiǧet taṣebḥant. \f ◼ \fr 6:43 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:43 \xt [Mt. 7:17-20; 12:34-35] — Mt. 7:17; 12:33. \x*
\v 44 Minzi kuř tacejjart tᵉttwassen s řɣiǧet nnes, minzi war yrun zeg isennanen řbacur, u war řeqqḍen aḍiř zi cbarq ak-d isennanen. \x ◘ \xo 6:44 \xt Mt. 7:16. \x*
\v 45 Bnadem aṣebḥan zi řkenz n wuř nnes d aṣebḥan ad issuffeɣ min iṣebḥen uca bnadem aɛeffan zi řkenz n wuř nnes d aɛeffan ad dd-issuffeɣ tuɛeffna. S min zi iccur wuř, zzayes ssawařen iyencicen.” \x ◘ \xo 6:45 \xt Mt. 12:35. \x*
\b
\s1 Taddart x sseǧaḥ
\m 
\v 46 “Mayemmi d ayi tᵉttřaɣam: ‘\add A\add* Sidi, \add a\add* Sidi!’ uca war tᵉtteggem ca min qqareɣ? \x ◘ \xo 6:46 \xt [Mt. 7:24-27] — Mal. 1:6; Mt. 7:21; 25:11; Lk. 13:25; Rum. 2:13; Yaɛ. 1:22. \x*
\v 47 Marra wenni ɣari i dd ɣa yasen, ad iseř i wawařen inu uca ad zzaysen igg, Necc ad awem ssecneɣ min di yarwes netta. \x ◘ \xo 6:47 \xt Mt. 7:24. \x*
\v 48 Netta yarwes deg ijj n bnadem i ibnan ict n taddart. Netta iɣza, iḥfar uca issars dsas x sseǧaḥ. Umi dd-tusa sseḥřet, tqebbeḍ řḥemřet taddart nni uca war tzemmar ad tt tessenhezz, minzi tuɣa dsas nnes x sseǧaḥ.
\v 49 Maca wenni ittesřan war ittegg, yarwes di bnadem i ibnan taddart nnes x temmurt břa dsas. Umi tt-i-dd-tqebbeḍ řḥemřet, řexdenni tewḍa. Tuɣa afartek n taddart nni d ameqqran.”
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 L’iman n řqebṭan arumani
\m 
\v 1 Awarni řami ikemmeř marra awařen nnes am d as sřan iwdan, yudef Yasuɛ ɣar Kafarnaḥum. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt [Mt. 8:5-13; Yḥ. 4:43-54]\x*
\v 2 Amsexxar n ijj n řqebṭan x mya, wenni tuɣa issɛizz aṭṭas, tuɣa ihřec, war d as iqqim ca ad immet.
\v 3 Umi isřa x Yasuɛ, issekk ɣares ca n imɣaren n Wudayen, ittar \add as\add* maḥend ad dd-yas uca ad issenjem amsexxar nnes.
\v 4 Řami dd-iwḍen ɣar Yasuɛ, ḥeccmen t aṭṭas, nnan: “Aqa isdaheǧ ad as tegged aya,
\v 5 minzi netta ittexs řgens nneɣ u ibna aneɣ tamzida.”
\m 
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* iruḥ Yasuɛ akidsen. Ařami tuɣa war iggʷij ɛad x taddart, issekk řqebṭan x mya ca n imeddukkař \add ɣares\add*, uca netta inna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, war ssiḥiř ixef nnec, minzi necc war sdiheǧeɣ ad tadfed sadu tazeqqa inu.
\v 7 S uyenni necc war ḥesbeɣ ixef inu sdaheǧeɣ ḥima ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ, maca ini awař \add waha\add* uca ad iggenfa umsexxar ameẓyan inu.
\v 8 Minzi uřa d necc ɛawed d ijj n bnadem sadu ifassen i ǧiɣ u ɣari \add ɛawed\add* iɛeskariyyen swadday i ufus inu. Qqareɣ i wa: ‘Ruḥ!’, xenni ittraḥ, i wenneɣni: ‘As-dd!’, xenni ittas-dd uca i umsexxar inu: ‘Egg aya!’, xenni ittegg i-t.”
\m 
\v 9 Umi isřa Yasuɛ aya, ittebhet dayes. Inneqřeb uca inna i řɣaci wenni tuɣa i-t-i-dd-iḍeffaren: “Necc ad awem iniɣ, war ufiɣ uřa di marra Israil l’iman ameqqran am řqedd n wa.”
\v 10 Ařami ɛeqben inni ittwassekken ɣar taddart, ufin amsexxar amehřuc iggenfa.
\b
\s1 Mmis n tajjač zi Nayin
\m 
\v 11 Tiwecca nnes iruḥ ɣar ict n tendint qqaren as Nayin. Tuɣa din akides imeḥḍaren nnes d ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran.
\v 12 Ařami dd-iqarreb ɣar tewwart n tendint, xzar, ksin-dd ijj n umettin \add x řmeḥmeř\add* ɣar barra. Netta d ayenni n mmis nni tuɣa ɣar yemmas. Yemmas tuɣa-tt d tajjač u tuɣa akides aṭṭas n řɣaci zi tendint.
\v 13 Umi tt iẓra Yasuɛ, tezziǧez as, inna as: “War ttru!”
\v 14 Xenni iqarreb-dd, iḥada řmeḥmeř, uca bedden yinni t yarbun, inna: “\add A\add* abřiɣ, i cek umi ɣa iniɣ, kkar-dd!” \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Řex. 9:40. \x*
\v 15 Iqqim umettin, ibda issawař, xenni yarra as t-i-dd i yemmas.
\v 16 Tudef tiggʷudi di marra uca ssemɣaren AREBBI, nnan: “Aqa ikkar-dd dayneɣ unabi imɣar!”, uca: “Aqa issijj-dd AREBBI x řgens nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Lk. 1:68; 24:19; Yḥ. 4:19; 6:14; 9:17. \x*
\v 17 Iffeɣ řexbar-a xas ɣar marra Yahudiyya u ɣar marra jjwayeh i d asen dd-innḍen.
\b
\s1 Aseqsi n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ
\m 
\v 18 Imeḥḍaren n Yuḥanna ɛawden as man aya marra. \x ◘ \xo 7:18 \xt [Mt. 11:2-19] — Mt. 11:2. \x*
\v 19 Iřaɣa Yuḥanna i tnayen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes uca issekk i-ten ɣar Yasuɛ, iqqar \add s uqemmum nsen\add*: “Ma d Cek d wenni dd ɣa yasen, niɣ ad nraja wenneɣni?”
\v 20 Umi ruḥen yeryazen ɣar Yasuɛ, nnan as: “Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ aqa issekk aneɣ-dd ɣarek, inna: ‘Ma d Cek d wenni i dd ɣa yasen niɣ ad nraja wenneɣni?’”
\m 
\v 21 Di tsaɛɛet nni tuɣa issgenfa aṭṭas \add n iwdan\add* zi řehřacat d uweddeb \add nsen\add* u zi řaryaḥ iɛeffanen, uca yarra aṭṭas n idarɣařen ttwařan.
\v 22 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ruḥem, ɛawdem i Yuḥanna min teẓrim d min tesřim. Aqa idarɣařen ttwařan u ineɛḍaben gguren u yinni di iǧa řbarṣ ttwassizdegen u idehcar ttesřan u imettinen ttekkaren uca ittᵉttwabarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan i imezřaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 7:22 \xt Ica. 29:18; 35:5; 61:1. \x*
\v 23 Sseɛd n wenni war d ayi ittendrifen.”
\m 
\v 24 Umi ffɣen imeḥḍaren n Yuḥanna, ibda Yasuɛ iqqar i řɣaci x Yuḥanna: “Min ɣar i ɣa dd-teffɣem ɣar řexřa ad tẓarem? Ma ijj n uɣanim issenhezza t usemmiḍ? \x ◘ \xo 7:24 \xt Mt. 11:7. \x*
\v 25 Mařa lla, min ɣar tuɣa dd-teffɣem ad tẓarem? Ma ijj n bnadem yarḍ arruḍ yarḍeb? Xzar inni yarḍen arruḍ iɣřan yarḍeb u ddaren deg ufuhart, aqa aten di řeqṣur n ijeǧiden.
\v 26 Maca min ɣar tuɣa dd-teffɣem ad tẓarem? Ma ijj n unabi? Wah, ad awem iniɣ d ameqqran ktar zeg unabi.
\v 27 Aqa d wa i xef ittwari: ‘Aqa Necc ad ssekkeɣ lmalak inu zzat i uɣembub nnec, wenni i ɣa isswejden abrid nnec ɣar zzat nnec.’ \x ◘ \xo 7:27 \xt Uf. 23:20; Mal. 3:1; Mk. 1:2. \x*
\v 28 Necc ad awem iniɣ, jar inni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi temɣarin uřa d ijj war iǧi d anabi ameqqran x Yuḥanna \add Amseɣḍaṣ\add*, maca \add waxxa amenni\add* d ameẓyan qaɛ di Tgeldit n AREBBI imɣar xas.”
\v 29 Marra iwdan nni d as isřin, uřa d ayt n ḍḍariba cehden i tsegda n AREBBI, minzi nitni ttwassɣeḍṣen s useɣḍeṣ n Yuḥanna.
\v 30 Maca Ifarisiyyen d imseřmaden n idlisen ugin x ccwar n AREBBI i yixef nsen, minzi ugin ad zzayes ttwassɣeḍṣen.
\m 
\v 31 \add Inna Netta\add*: “Min zi ɣa cebbheɣ iwdan n jjiř-a? Wi di yarwesen? \x ◘ \xo 7:31 \xt Mt. 11:16. \x*
\v 32 Nitni amecnaw iḥenjiren i iqqimen di ssuq, ttřaɣan ijjen wenneɣni, qqaren: ‘Neccin newta awem di temja, kenniw war tecḍiḥem, u neccin nɣennej ijj n weẓri n wecḍan i kenniw, \add maca\add* kenniw war trum ca.’
\v 33 Minzi yusa-dd Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ, war ittett aɣrum, war isess binu uca tennam: ‘Aqa dayes cciṭan!’ \x ◘ \xo 7:33 \xt Mt. 3:4; Mk. 1:6. \x*
\v 34 Yusa-dd Mmis n bnadem ittett, isess, tennam: ‘Xzar, bnadem-a iřhef x macca d binu, aqa-t d ameddukkeř n ayt n ḍḍariba d imednab.’
\v 35 Maca tiɣit tᵉttwasegged zi marra tarwa nnes.”
\b
\s1 Adhan n iḍaren n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 36 Iɛarḍ i-t ijj n Ufarisi ḥima ad kis icc. Yudef Netta ɣar taddart n Ufarisi uca iqqim \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add*.
\v 37 Tuɣa tzeddeɣ ict n temɣart tamednubt di tendint nni. Umi tessen aqa iqqim \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* di taddart n Ufarisi, tusa-dd s ijj n uɣarraf n alabaster dayes \add zzect\add* i wedhan,
\v 38 uca umi tbedd ɣar iḍaren nnes ɣar ḍeffar nnes, tru uca tebda tessuffa iḍaren nnes s imeṭṭawen nnes uca tebda tessaẓaɣ i-ten s ucuwwaf \add n uzeǧif\add* nnes, tessudem as iḍaren uca temseḥ i-ten s ict n zzect n wedhan.
\v 39 Umi iẓra Ufarisi wenni i-t-i-dd-iɛarḍen man aya, ixarreṣ deg yixef nnec, inna: “Mařa Wa d anabi \add s tidett\add*, iři aqa issen min teɛna tanita u mammec tᵉttwassen nettat, minzi tenni t iḥadan, aqa-tt d tamednubt.”
\m 
\v 40 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “\add A\add* Cimɛun, ɣari ict n řḥajjet ad ac tt iniɣ.” Inna as: “Ini tt, \add a\add* Amseřmad inu!”
\v 41 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Ijj n bab n umarwas tuɣa ɣares tnayen ttursen as. Ijjen tuɣa itturs as xemsa-mya dinar u wenneɣni xemsin.
\v 42 Am war tuɣi ɣarsen min zi ɣa arren amarwas, isamḥ asen \add amarwas\add* s tnayen idsen. \add Ini ayi,\add* wi zzaysen t ɣa ixsen ktar?”
\v 43 Yarra-dd Cimɛun, inna: “Ittɣiř ayi wenni umi isamḥ ktar.” Inna as: “Cek tḥekmed s ṣṣaḥ.”
\v 44 \add Xas uca\add* inneqřeb Yasuɛ ɣar temɣart nni, inna i Cimɛun: “Ma tᵉttwařid tamɣart-a? Aqa udfeɣ ɣar taddart nnec. Aman i iḍaren inu war d ayi ten tewcid. Maca nettat tessuff iḍaren inu s imeṭṭawen \add nnes\add* uca tessiẓeɣ i-ten s ucuwwaf \add n uzeǧif\add* nnes.
\v 45 Cek war d ayi tessudmed, maca nettat, zeg wami dd-udfeɣ, war tbedd zeg usudem n iḍaren inu.
\v 46 S zzect war tmesḥed ca azeǧif inu, maca nettat temseḥ iḍaren inu s zzect n wedhan.
\v 47 S uyenni ad ac iniɣ: Aqa ittwaɣfar as aṭṭas n ddnub nnes, minzi texs aṭṭas. Wenni umi ittwaɣfar drus, ad ɣares yiři drus n tayri.”
\v 48 \add Xenni\add* inna as: “\add A\add* tameṭṭut, aqa ttwaɣfaren ddnub nnem.” \x ◘ \xo 7:48 \xt Mt. 9:2. \x*
\m 
\v 49 Inni akides iqqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* bdan qqaren deg ixef nsen: “Min iɛna Wanita maḥend ad iɣfar uřa i ddnub.” \x ◘ \xo 7:49 \xt Mt. 9:3. \x*
\v 50 Inna as Yasuɛ i tmeṭṭut nni: “L’iman nnem aqa iwca am Tudart. Ruḥ di řehna.”
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Timɣarin i isexxaren i Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 1 Awarni uya icuq Yasuɛ di tneddam d dcurat, ittbarreḥ s Tgeldit n AREBBI. Tuɣa akides tenɛac \add n rrusul\add* nnes, \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt [Mt. 13:1-17; Mk. 4:1-12] \x*
\v 2 uřa d temɣarin aya nni tuɣa ittwassgenfan zi řeḥřacat u zi řaryaḥ iɛeffanen: \add aqa-tt\add* Maryam, qqaren as ‘tenni n Majdala’, i zi ttwassuffɣen sebɛa n ccwaṭen, \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Mt. 27:55, 56. \x*
\v 3 d Yuḥanna, tamɣart n Xuza, awkiř n Hirudus, d Susanna, d tinneɣni aṭṭas i tuɣa ttsexxarent xasen s wagřa nsent.
\b
\s1 Amedya n umzarreɛ
\m 
\v 4 Řami din issmun ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran, usin-dd ɣares zi marra tineddam, inna s yijj n umedya: \x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt [Mt. 13:18-23; Mk. 4:13-20] — Mt. 13:3; Mk. 4:2. \x*
\v 5 “Iffeɣ-dd ijj n umzarraɛ, ḥima ad izarɛ zzariɛet nnes. Am izarreɛ, tewḍa \add cwayt n zzariɛet\add* deg webrid, iɛfes xas uca neqben i-tt ijḍaḍ.
\v 6 Tewḍa \add cwayt n zzariɛet\add* nneɣni x weẓru, umi dd-teɣmi deɣya, tuẓeɣ, minzi war ɣares tuɣi tuffet.
\v 7 Tewḍa \add cwayt n zzariɛet\add* nneɣni di řwesṭ n isennanen uca isennanen ɣemyen-dd akides uca jeyyfen tt.
\v 8 Tewḍa \add cwayt n zzariɛet\add* nneɣni di temmurt yareḍben d lemliḥ, uca umi dd-teɣmi, tegga řɣiǧet n mya imuren.” Awarni řami tuɣa iqqar man aya, iřaɣa: “Wenni ɣar iǧa imezzuɣen i useǧi, ejj i-t ad iseř.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 Sseqsan t imeḥḍaren nnes: “Min ixs ad yini umedya-a?” \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt [Mt. 13:18-23; Mk. 4:10-20] \x*
\v 10 Inna asen: “I kenniw umi immewc ad tessnem ssirr n Tgeldit n AREBBI, maca i inneɣni ad dd-yas wawař s imedya, ařami nitni ttwařan maca war ttwiřin uca ttesřan war fehhmen. \x ◘ \xo 8:10 \xt Ica. 6:9-10; Ḥiz. 12:2; Mt. 11:25; 13:14; Mk. 4:12; Yḥ. 12:40; Řex. 28:26; Rum. 11:8; 2 Kur. 3:5, 14. \x*
\v 11 D wa d \add řmeɛna n\add* umedya: zzariɛet nettat d Awař n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Mt. 13:18; Mk. 4:13. \x*
\v 12 Ina x ṭṭarf n webrid, nitni d inni ittesřan Awař, maca \add xenni\add* ittas-dd ibřis, ittekkes Awař zeg wuř nsen ařami war ttimnen uca ad ddaren.
\v 13 Ina x weẓru, nitni d inni xmi ɣa sřen, ad qebřen Awař s řefraḥet, \add maca\add* war ɣarsen bu weẓwar, ttamnen ɣar xennit, di řweqt n ujarreb ad nqarḍen. \x ◘ \xo 8:13 \xt Mt. 13:20; Mk. 4:16. \x*
\v 14 Ina i iwḍan deg isennanen, nitni d inni ittesřan Awař, xenni ttraḥen, ttbuxsuyen deg imnusen d wagřa d ṭṭamuɛ n ddunect, war ssendayen ca řɣiǧet. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Mt. 19:23; Mk. 10:23; Lk. 18:24; 1 Tim. 6:9. \x*
\v 15 Ina di temmurt yareḍben, nitni d inni ittesřan i Wawař, xemmřen t deg wuř nican, iṣbeḥ, uca ssendayen řɣiǧet s ṣṣbar.”
\b
\s1 Amedya n řefnar d řmerfeɛ
\m 
\v 16 “Uřa d ijj war issruɣi řefnar uca iqebbar xas s yijj n uqedduḥ niɣ issrusa t sadu qama, maca \add s řemqřub\add* issrusa t x řmerfeɛ, ḥima inni dd-ittadfen ad ẓaren tafawt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt [Mk. 4:21-25] — Mt. 5:15; Mk. 4:21; Lk. 11:33. \x*
\v 17 Minzi war din min idřin, war dd-itteffiɣ ɣar barra, u \add war din\add* min innuffaren, war ittwissin, war dd-itteffiɣ ɣar barra. \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Ayub 12:22; Mt. 10:26; Mk. 4:22; Lk. 12:2. \x*
\v 18 Ḥḍam mammec tᵉttesřam, minzi wenni ɣar iǧa ad as immarni, u wenni war ɣar iǧi, min d as ittɣiř ɣares, ad zzayes ittwakkes.” \x ◘ \xo 8:18 \xt Mt. 13:12; 25:29; Mk. 4:25; Lk. 19:26. \x*
\b
\s1 Man wen iǧan d yemmas d aytmas n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 19 Yemmas d aytmas usin-dd ɣares, war zemmaren ad akides ssiwřen s ssibbet n řɣaci. \x ◘ \xo 8:19 \xt [Mt. 12:46-50; Mk. 3:31-35] — Mt. 12:46; 13:55; Mk. 3:31. \x*
\v 20 Nnan as: “Yemmac d aytmac bedden barra, xsen ad Cek ẓaren.”
\v 21 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Yemma d aytma, aqa d inni ittesřan Awař n AREBBI u tteggen zzayes.” \x ◘ \xo 8:21 \xt Yḥ. 15:14; 2 Kur. 5:16. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d tḥaryaḍt
\m 
\v 22 Deg ijjen zeg wussan nni inya deg ict n tɣarrabut, Netta d imeḥḍaren nnes. Inna asen: “Ejj aneɣ ad neẓwa ɣar ujemmaḍin n řebḥar!” \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt [Mt. 8:23-27; Mk. 4:35-41] — Mt. 8:23; Mk. 4:35, 36. \x*
\v 23 Am ten tuɣa ruḥen di řebḥar, ikka yiḍeṣ x Yasuɛ. Xenni tehwa-dd ict n tḥaryaḍt n usemmiḍ di řebḥar, tebda tɣarrabut ɛřayen ad tehwa.
\v 24 Qarrben ɣares uca ssfaqen t, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, \add a\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, aqa nɣarreq.” Netta ikkar-dd, iwebbex asemmiḍ d řemwaj n waman uca ssqaren, yarsa řḥař.
\v 25 Xenni inna asen: “Mani iǧa l’iman nwem?” Ggʷeden, tbehten, nnan jar asen: “Min iɛna Wa, aqa ittamar uřa d asemmiḍ d waman uca ttᵉṭṭaɛen as.” \x ◘ \xo 8:25 \xt Ayub 26:12; Izhd. 107:25. \x*
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n umeryaḥ
\m 
\v 26 Uyuren s tɣarrabut, usin-dd ɣar temmurt n Gadarinus tenni qibač i Ljalil. \x ◘ \xo 8:26 \xt [Mt. 8:28-34; Mk. 5:1-20] — Mt. 8:28; Mk. 5:1. \x*
\v 27 Umi dd-iffeɣ ɣar temmurt, iřqa t-i-dd ijj n weryaz zi tendint. Aṭṭas zeg wami tuɣa dayes ijj n cciṭan u tuɣa war ittirḍ arruḍ, war izeddeɣ di taddart maca deg imeḍřan.
\v 28 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ, isɣuy, iwḍa ɣar iḍaren nnes, inna s jjehd “Min din jar aneɣ necc d Cek a Yasuɛ, Mmis n AREBBI, Amɛuǧi x kuřci? Ttzawageɣ Cek, war d ayi tɛeddibed?”
\v 29 Maɣar Netta yumur i řaryaḥ amengus, ḥima ad dd-iffeɣ zi bnadem nni, minzi tuɣa-t dayes \add ɛad\add* ijj n řmijar n řweqt d ameqqran. \add Tuɣa arezzun\add* ad t carfen s ssnaseř d iceddiyyen, maca netta tuɣa ittareẓẓa iceddiyyen nnes uca \add xenni\add* yuẓẓeř xas ijj n cciṭan ɣar řexřa.
\v 30 Isseqsa t Yasuɛ: “Mammec d ac qqaren?” Inna as: “Lixyun ”, minzi ccwaṭen aṭṭas tuɣa udfen dayes.
\v 31 Nitni ttaren zzayes, ḥima war ten ittamar ad raḥen ɣar weḥfur.
\m 
\v 32 Tuɣa din ict n tḥimart d tameqqrant n iřfan, tuɣa thedda deg wedrar. Ttaren zzayes ḥima ad ten ijj ad adfen deg iřfan. Uca Netta isamḥ asen.
\v 33 Ffɣen ccwaṭen zi bnadem \add nni\add*, udfen deg iřfan. \add Xenni\add* teqnunni tḥimart zi jjarf di řebḥar uca tɣarq. \x ◘ \xo 8:33 \xt Mk. 5:13\x*
\m 
\v 34 Umi ẓrin imeksawen min imsaren, arewřen uca ɛawden t di tendint u di dcurat.
\v 35 Ffɣen-dd iwdan ḥima ad ẓaren min imsaren. Nitni usin-dd ɣar Yasuɛ, ufin bnadem nni zi ffɣen ccwaṭen, yarḍ, s řeɛqeř, iqqim ɣar iḍaren n Yasuɛ, uca ggʷeden.
\v 36 Inni iẓrin man aya, ɛawden asen mammec ittwassgenfa umaryaḥ.
\v 37 Řɣaci n Ijadariyyen zawgen t, ḥima ad xasen iggʷej, minzi tudef i-ten tiggʷudi temɣar. \add Xas uca\add* yenya Yasuɛ di tɣarrabut, iggʷej xasen. \x ◘ \xo 8:37 \xt Řex. 16:39. \x*
\m 
\v 38 Aryaz i zi ffɣen ccwaṭen, ittar zzayes, ma ad taɣ izemmar ad ɣares iqqim, maca Yasuɛ issekk i-t, inna as: \x ◘ \xo 8:38 \xt Mk. 5:18. \x*
\v 39 “Ɛqeb ɣar taddart nnec, ɛawed \add i ayt bab n taddart\add* min dayek igga AREBBI.” \add Xas uca\add* iruḥ, ibarreḥ di qaɛ tandint s marra min dayes igga Yasuɛ.
\b
\s1 Yeǧis n Yayrus d ict n temɣart teḥřec zeg usizzeř n idammen
\m 
\v 40 Ařami dd-iɛqeb Yasuɛ, yareḥḥeb zzayes ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran, minzi marra ttrajan t. \x ◘ \xo 8:40 \xt [Mt. 9:18-26; Mk. 5:21-43] \x*
\v 41 U xzar, yusa-dd ijj n weryaz qqaren as Yayrus, tuɣa-t d ameqqran n temzida, iwḍa ɣar iḍaren n Yasuɛ uca izawg i-t ad yadef ɣar taddart nnes, \x ◘ \xo 8:41 \xt Mt. 9:18; Mk. 5:22. \x*
\v 42 minzi ayenni n yeǧis i ɣares tenni ɣar iǧa tenɛac n iseggʷusa, tuɣa ɛřayen ad temmet. Am kides iggur Yasuɛ, issdeḥḥes i-t řɣaci.
\m 
\v 43 Ict n temɣart, tuɣa ttazzřen zzayes idammen řqedd n tenɛac n iseggʷusa, tseyyar marra řeɛweč nnes x iḍbiben, war izemmar ḥed ad tt issgenfa, \x ◘ \xo 8:43 \xt Lawi 15:25; Mt. 9:20; Mk. 5:25. \x*
\v 44 tusa-dd ɣares zi ḍeffar, tḥada abeḥřuř n warruḍ nnes, uca řexdenni ibedd usizzeř n idammen nnes.
\v 45 \add Xas uca\add* Inna Yasuɛ: “Wi d ayi iḥadan?” Umi nkaren marra, inna Cimɛun Buṭrus d yinni akides: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, řɣaci issdeḥḥes i-c u Cek teqqared: ‘Wi d ayi iḥadan?’”
\v 46 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna: “Aqa ijjen iḥada ayi, minzi Necc uciɣ jjehd iffeɣ zzayi.”
\v 47 Umi tessen temɣart, belli war teqqim war temẓar, tusa-dd s uqefqef uca tewḍa ɣar iḍaren n Yasuɛ, isjed as. Qibač i marra iwdan txebbar x man ssibbet i zi t tḥada d mammec tᵉttwassgenfa deɣya.
\v 48 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Egg uř, a yeǧi, aqa l’iman nnem iwca am Tudart. Ruḥ di řehna.”
\m 
\v 49 Am issawař \add ɛad\add*, yusa-dd ijj n weryaz zi taddart n umeqqran n temzida, inna as: “Aqa yeǧic temmut, war ssaḥař ɛad Amseɣɣar.” \x ◘ \xo 8:49 \xt Mk. 5:35. \x*
\v 50 Maca Yasuɛ isřa man aya, inna i babas n tḥenjirt: “War teggʷed ca! Amen waha, nettat ad teddar!”
\v 51 Umi dd-yusa Yasuɛ ɣar taddart, war ijji uřa d ijjen ad yadef mɣir Cimɛun d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna d babas n tḥenjirt d yemmas.
\v 52 Tuɣa marra ittru, wtin xas agejdur. Netta inna: “War ttrum, nettat war temmut ca, maca nettat tᵉṭṭeṣ.” \x ◘ \xo 8:52 \xt Yḥ. 11:11. \x*
\v 53 Nitni ḍeḥcen dayes, ssnen belli nettat tuɣa temmut.
\m 
\v 54 Maca awarni řami issuffeɣ marra, iṭṭef i-tt zeg ufus nnes, iřaɣa, inna as: “\add A\add* taḥenjirt, kkar!”
\v 55 Idweř-dd dayes buḥbeř uca tekkar řexdenni. Xenni yumur ad as wcen min ɣa tecc.
\v 56 Tbehten lwalidin nnes, maca Netta iweṣṣa i-ten, war qqaren i ḥed min imsaren.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Yasuɛ issekk tenɛac n rrusul nnes
\m 
\v 1 Yasuɛ iřaɣa-dd \add ɣares\add* tenɛac \add n rrusul\add* nnes, iwca asen jjehd d ṣṣulṭa x marra ccwaṭen u \add x marra\add* řehřacat, ḥima ad ssgenfan \add iwdan\add*. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt [Mt. 10:5-15; Mk. 6:7-13] — Mt. 10:1; Mk. 3:13; 6:7; Lk. 6:13. \x*
\v 2 Issekk i-ten ḥima ad barrḥen s Tgeldit n AREBBI u ḥima ad ssgenfan imehřac. \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Mt. 10:7. \x*
\v 3 Inna asen: “War kessim walu deg webrid niɣ taɣɣarct niɣ ttesṭim niɣ aɣrum uřa d nnuqart, uca war kessim uřa d tnayen n tcamirat. \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Mt. 10:9; Mk. 6:8; Lk. 22:35. \x*
\v 4 Man taddart i ɣa tadfem, qqimem dinni uca ffɣem ssenni.
\v 5 Mařa teffɣem zi tendint, zerzem \add xenni\add* taɛejjajt zeg iḍaren nwem qibač i yinni war kenniw iqebbřen, d cchadet xasen.” \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Mt. 10:14; Mk. 6:11; Lk. 10:11; 21:13; 24:48; Řex. 13:51; 18:6. \x*
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* ffɣen rrusul, tuɣa ttcuqan di dcurat d tneddam. Nitni ttbarrḥen s Řexbar Aṣebḥan, ssgenfan \add imehřac\add* di kuř amcan.
\b
\s1 Hirudus yarjef umi isřa x marra min igga Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 7 Hirudus, řḥakem x ijj n arbeɛ n temmurt isřa x marra min ittwaggen zzayes uca yarjef, minzi ca \add n iwdan\add* nnan, aqa Yuḥanna ikkar-dd zi taddart n imettinen. \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt [Mt. 14:1-12; Mk. 6:14-29] — Mt. 14:1; Mk. 6:14. \x*
\v 8 Ca nneɣni nnan aqa Iliya iḍhar-dd u ca nneɣni \add ɛawed\add* aqa ijjen zeg inabiyyen n wecḥař uya ikkar-dd. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Mt. 16:14; Mk. 6:15; 8:28; Lk. 9:19\x*
\v 9 Inna Hirudus: “Aqa d necc i iqessen azeǧif n Yuḥanna, maca manis Wa i xef sřiɣ \add marra\add* man aya?” Uca tuɣa yarezzu ad t iẓar.
\b
\s1 Lmuɛjiza n usecci amezwaru
\m 
\v 10 Umi dd-ɛeqben rrusul, ɛawden i Yasuɛ marra min ggin. Xenni yiwyi ten akides ɣar ijj n wemcan ixřa ɣar Bayt-Ṣayda, \add ḥima ad iřin\add* weḥḥedsen akides. \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt [Mt. 14:13-21; Mk. 6:30-44; Yḥ. 6:1-14] — Mt. 14:13; Mk. 6:30, 31, 32. \x*
\v 11 Umi yargeb řɣaci x man aya, iḍfar i-t. Netta tuɣa yareḥḥeb zzaysen, issiweř akidsen x Tgeldit n AREBBI u inni ḥdajen ad ttwassgenfan, issgenfa i-ten.
\m 
\v 12 Řami ibda řḥař issutum, qarrben-dd ɣares imeḥḍaren nnes, nnan as: “Sekk řɣaci, ḥima ad raḥen ɣar ředcur d iyyaren i d asen dd-innḍen, ad dinni afen mani ɣa ssensen d min ɣa ccen, minzi aqa aneɣ da deg ijj n wemcan ixřan.” \x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Mt. 14:15; Mk. 6:35; Yḥ. 6:5. \x*
\v 13 Maca Yasuɛ inna asen: “Wcem asen kenniw ḥima ad ccen.” Nnan as: “War ɣarneɣ mɣir xemsa n tecnifin d tnayen n iseřman, niɣ ittxeṣṣa ad nraḥ ad nseɣ macca i marra iwdan-a!” \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Mt. 14:16; Mk. 6:37; Yḥ. 6:9. \x*
\v 14 Minzi tuɣa aten di ca n xemsařaf n yeryazen. \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna asen: “Sɣimem ten di tɛurricin n xemsin.”
\v 15 Uca ggin imeḥḍaren amenni uca ssɣimen ten marra.
\v 16 Iksi Yasuɛ ticnifin s xemsa uřa d tnayen n iseřman \add nni\add*, issgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnes ɣar ujenna, uca ibark \add i-tent\add*, yarẓa uca iwca \add zi tecnifin nni\add* i imeḥḍaren nnes, ḥima ad wcen i řɣaci. \x ◘ \xo 9:16 \xt 1 Ṣm. 9:13; Mk. 6:41\x*
\v 17 Ccin, jjiwnen marra. Ařami d jarwen min iqqimen zeg iřeqqwaz, tuɣa dinni tenɛac n tsuǧatin.
\b
\s1 Cchadet n Cimɛun Buṭrus
\m 
\v 18 Am tuɣa Yasuɛ ittẓaǧa weḥḥdes, am tuɣa imeḥḍaren akides, isseqsa ten, inna: “Min iqqar řɣaci min ɛniɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 9:18 \xt [Mt. 16:13-19; Mk. 8:27-29] — Mt. 16:13; Mk. 8:27. \x*
\v 19 Arrin-dd, nnan as: “‘Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ!’, u inneɣni: ‘Iliya!’, u ca inneɣni: ‘Aqa ikkar-dd ijj n unabi, ijjen zeg inabiyyen n wecḥař uya’.” \x ◘ \xo 9:19 \xt Mt. 14:2; Mt. 16:14; Mk. 6:15; 8:28; Lk. 9:8\x*
\v 20 Inna asen: “I kenniw, min teqqarem min ɛniɣ?” Yarra-dd Cimɛun, inna: “Lmasiḥ n AREBBI.”
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* iɛřem asen s jjehd uca iweṣṣa ten, war t qqaren i ḥed.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes i twařa tamezwarut
\m 
\v 22 Inna asen: “Ittxeṣṣa i Mmis n bnadem ad iweddeb aṭṭas uca ad immenḍar zeg imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen, ad ittwaneɣ uca deg wass wiss třata ad dd-ikkar.” \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt [Mt. 16:21-28; Mk. 8:30-9:1] — Mt. 16:21; 17:22; Mk. 8:31; 9:31; 10:33; Lk. 18:31; 24:7. \x*
\v 23 \add Xas uca\add* inna i marra: “Mařa ixs ḥed ad dd-yas awarni ayi, ittxeṣṣa as ad inkar ixef nnes, ad iksi ṣṣalib nnes kuř ass uca ad ayi dd-iḍfar. \x ◘ \xo 9:23 \xt Mt. 10:38; 16:24; Mk. 8:34; Lk. 14:27. \x*
\v 24 Minzi wi ixsen ad issenjem tudart nnes, ad tt iweddar. Maca wi ixsen ad iweddar tudart nnes di ṭṭweɛ inu, ad tt issenjem. \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt Mt. 10:39; 16:25; Mk. 8:35; Lk. 17:33; Yḥ. 12:25. \x*
\v 25 Minzi man řefḍeř i bnadem mařa yarbeḥ ddunect marra, maca ad yareddeǧ řeɛmar nnes niɣ ad t iweddar?
\v 26 Minzi wenni i ɣa iseḍḥan zzayi u zeg wawařen inu, ad zzayes iseḍḥa \add ɛawed\add* Mmis n bnadem xmi dd ɣa yas deg uɛuǧi nnes u deg uɛuǧi n Babas ak-d lmalakat nnes iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 9:26 \xt Mt. 10:33; Mk. 8:38; Lk. 12:9; 2 Tim. 2:12; 1 Yḥ. 2:23. \x*
\v 27 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa ca zeg inni da iḥḍaren, war ttqisin ca řmewt ař ɣa ẓaren Tageldit n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 9:27 \xt Mt. 16:28; Mk. 9:1. \x*
\b
\s1 Asɛuǧi n Yasuɛ x wedrar
\m 
\v 28 Ɛřaḥař tmenya n wussan awarni řami \add inna\add* awařen-a, iwyi-dd Yasuɛ akides Cimɛun d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna uca igeɛɛed ɣar wedrar, ḥima ad iẓẓaǧ. \x ◘ \xo 9:28 \xt [Mt. 17:1-8; Mk. 9:2-8] — Mt. 17:1; Mk. 9:2. \x*
\v 29 Am tuɣa ittẓaǧa, ibeddeř wudem n uɣembub nnes u arruḍ nnes idweř d acemřař ittissiqen.
\v 30 Xzar, tnayen n yeryazen ssiwřen akides, tuɣa aten d Musa d Iliya,
\v 31 inni dd-iḍharen s uɛuǧi, tuɣa ssawařen x wuffuɣ nnes i tuɣa i ɣa ittwakemmeř di Urcalim.
\v 32 Cimɛun d yinni akides, tuɣa ikka xasen yiḍeṣ, ařami ɛřayen war zemmaren ad qqimen faqen. Nitni ẓrin aɛuǧi nnes d tnayen n yeryazen bedden akides.
\v 33 Ařami xas farqen ina, inna Cimɛun i Yasuɛ: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, aqa mliḥ umi i da neǧa. Ejj aneɣ ad newwet třata n iɛuccuten n tseṭṭa, ijjen i Cek, ijjen i Musa u ijjen i Iliya.” Netta \add maca\add* war issin min inna.
\v 34 Awarni řami inna man aya, ikka-dd xasen ijj n useynu, issduriy i-ten uca nitni dewřen ggʷeden umi ẓrin Musa d Iliya udfen ɣar useynu.
\v 35 Tusa-dd ict n tmijja zeg ujenna, teqqar: “D wa d Mmi Iɛizzen, sřem ɣares!” \x ◘ \xo 9:35 \xt Aɛwd. 18:15; Ica. 42:1; Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 1:11; 9:7; Lk. 3:22; Řex. 3:22; Kul. 1:13; 2 Bṭ. 1:17. \x*
\v 36 Ařami dd-tusa tmijja, ufin Yasuɛ weḥḥdes. Nitni ssqaren uca war xebbaren ḥed deg wussan nni s min ẓrin.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n uḥenjir dayes řaryaḥ d amengus
\m 
\v 37 Tiwecca nnes, ařami tuɣa dd-hekkwan zeg wedrar, iřqa ten-i-dd ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 9:37 \xt [Mt. 17:14-18; Mk. 9:14-27] — Mt. 17:14; Mk. 9:17. \x*
\v 38 U xzar, ijj n weryaz zi řɣaci isɣuy, inna: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, ttzawgeɣ Cek, ḥinn xafi, aqa-t d ayenni n mmis i ɣari.
\v 39 Xzar, itteṭṭef i-t ijj n řaryaḥ, xenni isɣuyyu deɣya, ittɣeẓẓa tiɣmas u ittekk as-dd kuffu zeg uqemmum, ɛřaḥar war d as yarexxu am t iyezzem \add ammu\add*.
\v 40 Ttareɣ zeg imeḥḍaren nnec ad t ssuffɣen, maca war zemmaren.”
\v 41 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna: “A jjiř i war yuminen imɛewwjen, mecḥař ɣarwem i ɣa kkeɣ ad kenniw ksiɣ? Awi-dd mmic da!”
\v 42 Ařami ɣares t-i-dd-issqarreb, inḍar i-t cciṭan \add di temmurt\add*, imezzeq i-t. Maca Yasuɛ iwebbex řaryaḥ amengus, issgenfa aḥenjir uca yarra i-t i babas.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes i twařa wiss tnayen
\m 
\v 43 Marra tuɣa ttɛejjben di řemɣaret n AREBBI. Uca umi tbehten marra nitni di marra min igga Yasuɛ, inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: \x ◘ \xo 9:43 \xt [Mt. 17:22-23; Mk. 9:30-32]\x*
\v 44 “Ggem awařen-a deg imezzuɣen nwem, minzi Mmis n bnadem ad immewc deg ifassen n iwdan.” \x ◘ \xo 9:44 \xt Mt. 17:22; Mk. 9:31. \x*
\v 45 Maca nitni war fhimen i wawař-a, tuɣa ittwassnuffar xasen maḥend war t fehhmen. Uca nitni ggʷeden ad t sseqsan x wawař-a. \x ◘ \xo 9:45 \xt Lk. 2:50; 18:34. \x*
\b
\s1 Man wen iǧan d ameqqran?
\m 
\v 46 Yudef i-ten ijj n umcubbec x man wen zzaysen i ɣa yiřin d ameqqran qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 9:46 \xt [Mt. 18:1-5; Mk. 9:33-37] — Mt. 18:1; Mk. 9:33; Lk. 22:24. \x*
\v 47 Maca issen Yasuɛ axarreṣ n wuřawen nsen uca iksi ijj n uḥenjir issbedd i-t ɣares.
\v 48 Inna asen: “Wi ɣa iqebřen aḥenjir-a s Yisem inu, iqbeř ayi Necc, u wi d ayi ɣa iqebřen, iqbeř wenni d ayi dd-issekken. Minzi wenni d ameẓyan qaɛ jar awem, netta ad yiři d ameqqran.” \x ◘ \xo 9:48 \xt Mt. 18:5; 23:11; Mk. 9:37; Lk. 10:16; 14:11; 18:14; Yḥ. 13:20. \x*
\b
\s1 Wi war iǧin ḍidd nwem, netta aqa-t akidwem
\m 
\v 49 Iṭṭef Yuḥanna deg wawař, inna: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, neẓra ijjen issuffuɣ ccwaṭen s Yisem nnec uca nessbedd i-t, minzi netta war Cek iḍeffar \add jmiɛ\add* akidneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 9:49 \xt [Mk. 9:38-40] — Mk. 9:38. \x*
\v 50 Inna as Yasuɛ: “War t sbeddam, minzi wi war iǧin ḍidd nwem, aqa-t akidwem.” \x ◘ \xo 9:50 \xt Mt. 12:30; Mk. 9:39; Lk. 9:50; 11:23. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ deg ijj n dcar n Isamiriyyen
\m 
\v 51 Umi dd-iwḍen ad kemmřen wussan n tmeksit nnes nnes \add ɣar ujenna\add*, yarra aɣembub nnes ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 9:51 \xt Mk. 16:19; Řex. 1:2; 1 Tim. 3:16. \x*
\v 52 Issekk zzates ireqqasen, uca ina udfen ɣar ijj n dcar n Isamariyyen, ḥima ad as wejden \add din\add*.
\v 53 Nitni \add maca\add* war t qbiřen, minzi yarra aɣembub nnes, ḥima ad iraḥ ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 9:53 \xt Yḥ. 4:9. \x*
\v 54 Umi ẓrin Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna, imeḥḍaren nnes, man aya, nnan: “A Siditneɣ, ma texsed ad numur, ḥima ad dd-tehwa tmessi zeg ujenna, maḥend ad ten tecc am mammec igga ɛawed Iliya?”
\v 55 \add Maca\add* am dd-inneqřeb, iwebbex i-ten, inna: “War tessinem ca man arruḥ i zi teǧam kenniw!
\v 56 Minzi Mmis n bnadem war dd-yusi ca ḥima ad isshellek řeɛmur n iwdan, maca ḥima ad iwc Tudart!” Xenni ruḥen ɣar dcurat nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 9:56 \xt Yḥ. 3:17; 12:47. \x*
\b
\s1 Aḍfar n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 57 Am gguren nitni deg webrid, inna as ijj n weryaz: “A Sidi inu, ad Cek ḍfareɣ mani ma i ɣa traḥed.” \x ◘ \xo 9:57 \xt [Mt. 8:19-22] — Mt. 8:19. \x*
\v 58 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Iceɛbawen ɣarsen ifran d ijḍaḍ n ujenna ɣarsen řeɛwacc, maca Mmis n bnadem war ɣares uřa mani ɣa isenned azeǧif nnes.”
\m 
\v 59 Inna i wenneɣni: “Ḍfar ayi-dd!” Maca wanita inna: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, ejj ayi amezwar ad areggʷeḥeɣ ad neḍřeɣ baba!” \x ◘ \xo 9:59 \xt Mt. 8:21. \x*
\v 60 \add Maca\add* inna as Yasuɛ: “Ejj imettinen ad neḍřen imettinen nsen, maca cek ruḥ, tbarrḥed s Tgeldit n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 9:60 \xt Mt. 8:22. \x*
\m 
\v 61 Inna as wenneɣni: “Ad Cek ḍfareɣ, \add a\add* Sidi, maca ejj ayi amezwar ad ggeɣ allah ihennik x yinni ɣari di taddart inu, \add xenni\add* ad dd-aseɣ.”
\v 62 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Uřa d ijj, mařa issrusa afus nnes x usɣar, xenni ad ixzar ɣar ḍeffar, ad iṣřeḥ i Tgeldit n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 9:62 \xt Awřn. 26:11; Fil. 3:14; Ɛbr. 6:5; 2 Bṭ. 2:20. \x*
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Asekki n sebɛin n imeḥḍaren
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya iřeqqem Yasuɛ ɛawed sebɛin nneɣni zeg imeḥḍaren nnes uca issekk i-ten tyuya tyuya qibač i uɣembub nnes ɣar marra tineddam d jjwayeh mani tuɣa Netta igga ad iraḥ. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt [Mt. 11:20-27; 13:16-17] \x*
\v 2 Inna asen: “Tameyra aṭṭas, maca ixeddamen drus, s uyenni ttarem i Bab n tmeyra, ḥima ad issekk ixeddamen ɣar tmeyra nnes. \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt Mt. 9:37; Yḥ. 4:35; 2 Ts. 3:1. \x*
\v 3 Ruḥem! Aqa ad kenniw ssekkeɣ am wuǧi jar wuccanen. \x ◘ \xo 10:3 \xt Mt. 10:16. \x*
\v 4 War kiwem kessim ticyarin řa d ttesṭayem uřa d sandaliyat, war ttseǧamem x ḥed deg webrid. \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt 2 Ij. 4:29; Mt. 10:9; Mk. 6:8; Lk. 9:3; 22:35. \x*
\v 5 Man ma taddart i ɣa tadfem, inim d amezwaru: ‘Řehna x taddart-a.’ \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt Mt. 10:12; Mk. 6:10. \x*
\v 6 Mařa din mmis n řehna, řehna nwem ad xas yarsa, mařa war iǧi amenni, řehna nwem ad ɣarwem dd-iɛqeb.
\v 7 Qqimem di taddart nni, ccem, swem zi min ɣarsen, minzi axeddam isdaheǧ řmunet nnes. \add S uya\add* war ggurem ca zi taddart ɣar taddart nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 10:7 \xt Lawi 19:13; Aɛwd. 24:14; 25:4; Mt. 10:10; 1 Kur. 9:4, 14; 10:27; 1 Tim. 5:18. \x*
\v 8 Man tandint i ɣa tadfem uca ad kenniw qebřen, ccem \add din\add* min d awem ɣa wcen.
\v 9 Sgenfam imehřac i din iǧan, inim asen: “Aqa tqarreb-dd ɣarwem Tgeldit n AREBBI.”
\v 10 Man ma tandint i ɣa tadfem, war kenniw qbiřen, ffɣem ɣar zznaqi nnes, inim: \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt Mt. 10:14; Mk. 6:11; Lk. 9:5. \x*
\v 11 “Ɛad uřa d taɛejjajt i dayneɣ iřeṣqen x \add iḍaren\add* nneɣ n tendint nwem, ad tt nezzerz xawem. Maca snem aya, aqa tqarreb-dd ɣarwem Tgeldit n AREBBI! \x ◘ \xo 10:11 \xt Řex. 13:51; 18:6. \x*
\v 12 Ad awem iniɣ belli deg wass nni ad yiři řḥař n Sadum ihwen zi tendint nni.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 \bd Uct xam, \add a\add* Xurazin, uct xam, \add a\add* Bayt-Ṣayda!\bd* Mři msarent di Ṣur d Ṣaydun řeɛjayeb i ittwaggen daykent, ad tiři tubent zi zzman am qqiment di txancet n wecḍan d yiɣɣeḍ \add x izeǧifen nsent\add*. \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt Mt. 11:20-24\x*
\v 14 Maca ad yiři řḥař n Ṣur d Ṣaydun ihwen zi řḥař nkent di lḥisab.
\v 15 U cem, \add a\add* Kafarnaḥum, tenni tuɣa ittwassgeɛɛden ɣar ujenna, aqa ad tᵉttwassehwid ɣar řaxart!
\m 
\v 16 Wi zzaywem i ɣa isřen, ad zzayi iseř, wi kenniw ɣa yagin, ad ayi yagi, u wi d ayi ɣa yagin, ad yagi wenni d ayi dd-issekken.” \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Mt. 10:40; Mk. 9:37; Yḥ. 13:20. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* ɛeqben sebɛin nni s řefraḥet aṭṭas, nnan as: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, uřa d ccwaṭen ṭṭaɛen aneɣ s Yisem nnec.”
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* inna asen: “Ẓriɣ cciṭan iwḍa-dd amecnaw assam zeg ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Asa. 12:8, 9. \x*
\v 19 Xzar, Necc ad awem wceɣ ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad tɛefsem x ifiɣran d iɣarḍmiwen uřa \add d ṣṣulṭa\add* x marra jjehd n řeɛdu. Uřa d ict n řḥajjet war kenniw tḍarri. \x ◘ \xo 10:19 \xt Mk. 16:18; Řex. 28:5. \x*
\v 20 Maca war farrḥem ca s uya, belli aqa ccwaṭen ad awem ṭṭaɛen, maca farḥem belli aqa ismawen nwem ttwazemmemen deg ijenwan.” \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Uf. 32:32; Ica. 4:3; Dan. 12:1; Fil. 4:3. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 Di tsaɛɛet nni ifarḥ Yasuɛ di Arruḥ Iqeddsen, inna: \bd “Necc ttqadiɣ Cek, a Baba, Bab n ujenna d temmurt\bd*, minzi tessnuffared timesřayin-a x imiɣisen u x aytbab n řeɛqeř uca tessaregbed tent i iḥenjiren. Wah, a Baba, ammu i tuɣa ixs řxaḍar nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 10:21 \xt [Mt. 11:25-27; 13:16-17] — Ayub 5:12; Ica. 29:14; Mt. 11:25; 1 Kur. 1:19; 2:7, 8; 2 Kur. 3:14. \x*
\v 22 \add Xas uca\add* inneqřeb ɣar imeḥḍaren nnes, inna: “Kuřci immewc ayi zi Baba uca uřa d ijj war issin man wen d Mmis mɣir Babas uca \add uřa d ijj war issin\add* man wen d Babas mɣir Mmis, d wenni umi ixs Mmis ad \add t\add* issargeb.” \x ◘ \xo 10:22 \xt Izhd. 8:7; Yḥ. 1:18; 3:35; 6:44, 45; 17:2; 1 Kur. 15:27; Fil. 2:10; Ɛbr. 2:8. \x*
\m 
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* inneqřeb-dd ɣar imeḥḍaren weḥḥedsen, inna: “Sseɛd n tiṭṭawin i ittwařan min tᵉttwařam kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt Mt. 13:16. \x*
\v 24 Minzi Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa aṭṭas n inabiyyen d ijeǧiden tuɣa xsen ad ẓaren min tᵉttwařam kenniw, \add maca\add* war tt ttwiřin, uřa ad sřen min tᵉttesřam, \add maca\add* war tt sřin.” \x ◘ \xo 10:24 \xt 1 Bṭ. 1:10. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n weryaz d arḥim zi Samarya
\m 
\v 25 Xzar, ijj n umseřmad n idlisen ikkar ḥima ad t ijarreb, inna: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, min ɣa ggeɣ ḥima ad warteɣ Tudart ittduman?”
\v 26 Yasuɛ inna as: “Mammec t yurin di Ccariɛa? Mammec teqqared?”
\v 27 Yarra-dd, inna as: “Ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec s marra wuř nnec, s marra řeɛmar nnec, s marra jjehd nnec, s marra řeɛqeř nnec, uca \add ad texsed\add* jjar nnec amecnaw ixef nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 10:27 \xt Lawi 19:18; Aɛwd. 6:5; 10:12; 30:6; Mt. 22:37; Mk. 12:30; Rum. 13:9; Gal. 5:14; Yaɛ. 2:8. \x*
\v 28 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Aqa tarrid nican. Egg man aya uca ad teddared.”
\v 29 Maca netta ixs ad issegged ixef nnes, inna as: “Man wen iǧan d jjar inu?”
\m 
\v 30 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ, inna as: “Ijj n weryaz ihwa-dd zi Urcalim ɣar Ariḥa uca iwḍa deg ifassen n iceffaren, kksen as arruḍ, wtin t s weɛmud, xenni ruḥen, jjin t jar řmewt d tudart.
\v 31 Xenni ihwa-dd ijj n ukehhan ɣar webrid nni. Netta iẓra i-t, maca ikka \add xas\add*.
\v 32 Ammu ɛawed uřa d ijj n Ulawi iɛdu-dd x wemcan nni, iẓra i-t, maca ikka \add xas\add*.
\v 33 Maca ijj n weryaz Asamiri, tuɣa-t deg usafar, yiweḍ-dd ɣares, iẓra i-t uca iḥinn xas.
\v 34 Iqarreb-dd ɣares, icedd as iyezzimen nnes, iseyyeḥ xasen binu d zzect. \add Xenni\add* issenya i-t x zzayřet nnes, yiwyi i-t ɣar wenwař, ithella dayes.
\v 35 Tiwecca nnes řami iruḥ, iwca tnayen dinar i bab n wenwař, inna as: ‘Thilla dayes u mařa txeǧṣed ktar zi man aya, ad cek xeǧṣeɣ xmi dd ɣa ɛeqbeɣ.’
\v 36 Man wen zi třata nni tᵉttwařid d jjar n wenni iwḍan deg \add ifassen n\add* iceffaren?”
\v 37 Inna as: “Wenni xas iḥinnen!” Inna as Yasuɛ: “Iwa uyur, uřa d cek tegged amenni!”
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ di taddart n Maryam d Marta
\m 
\v 38 Am tuɣa gguren nitni, yudef ɣar ijj n dcar, uca ict n temɣart, qqaren as Marta, tareḥḥeb zzayes di taddart nnes.
\v 39 Tuɣa ɣar ta ict n učmas, qqaren as Maryam, tenni tuɣa teqqim ɣar iḍaren n Siditneɣ uca tuɣa tessḥessa i wawař nnes.
\v 40 Maca Marta tuɣa tecɣeř aṭṭas s tsexxart. Nettat tusa-dd \add ɣares\add*, tenna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, ma war d ac icqi belli učma tejja ayi ttsexxareɣ weḥḥdi? Ini as ḥima ad ayi tɛawen.”
\v 41 Maca Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna as: “Marta, Marta, cem tceɣřed u tqeǧiqed x waṭṭas n tmesřayin,
\v 42 maca ittxeṣṣa ict n řḥajjet \add waha\add*! Aqa Maryam tixḍar tasɣart taṣebḥant tenni war zzayes ittwattekksen.”
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Yasuɛ isseřmad mammec icuwwar ad ẓaǧen
\m 
\v 1 Am tuɣa ittẓaǧa deg ijj n wemcan, imsar, umi ikemmeř Netta taẓaǧit nnes, aqa ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes inna as: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, seřmed aneɣ ad neẓẓaǧ am mammec tuɣa Yuḥanna isseřmad ɛawed imeḥḍaren nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt [Mt. 6:9-15; 7:7-11]\x*
\v 2 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Meřmi ma teẓẓuǧem, inim:
\b
\m ‘\bdit Babatneɣ i iǧan deg ijenwan\bdit*,
\m \qt ad ittwaqeddes Isem nnec,\qt*
\m \qt ad dd-tas Tgeldit nnec,\qt*
\m \qt ad tᵉttwagg am mammec texsed Cek,\qt*
\m \qt am deg ujenna, \tl ammu\tl* ɛawed di temmurt.\qt*
\m 
\v 3 \qt Ewc aneɣ kuř ass aɣrum nneɣ i kuř ass,\qt*
\m 
\v 4 \qt uca ɣfar aneɣ ddnub nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt minzi uřa d neccin nsameḥ i marra\qt*
\m \qt inni dayneɣ ittursen.\qt*
\m \qt War d aneɣ ssidif ca deg ujarreb,\qt*
\m \qt maca senjem aneɣ zeg umɛeffan.’”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 5 Xenni inna asen: “Man wen zzaywem i ɣar iǧa ijj n umeddukkeř, ad ɣares iraḥ deg wezyen n ǧiřet uca ad as ini: ‘\bd \bdit A\bdit* ameddukkeř, arḍeř ayi třata n tecnifin\bd*, \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt [Mt. 7:7-11]\x*
\v 6 minzi ijj n umeddukkeř inu, ixecc-dd ɣari zeg usafar, war ɣari min d as ɣa qeddmeɣ!’,
\v 7 uca \add xenni\add* ad xas dd-yarr umeddukkeř nnes zi daxeř, ad as yini: ‘War dd ayi ttṣeddaɛ, tawwart tbelleɛ u tarwa aqa-tt akidi di tassut, war zemmareɣ ad dd-kkareɣ maḥend ad ac wceɣ \add aɣrum\add*.’
\v 8 Ad awem iniɣ, mařa war dd-ikkar ḥima ad as iwc umi netta d ameddukkeř nnes, iwa ad dd-ikkar ad as iwc mecḥař ma iḥdaj x ssibbet n řewɛaret \add n umeddukkeř\add* nnes.
\m 
\v 9 Ad awem iniɣ: \bd Ttarem, xenni ad awem immewc\bd*, arzum, xenni ad tafem, ssqarqbem, xenni ad awem arezmen. \x ◘ \xo 11:9 \xt Mt. 7:7; 21:22; Mk. 11:24; Yḥ. 14:13; 15:7; 16:24; Yaɛ. 1:5, 6; 1 Yḥ. 3:22; 5:14. \x*
\v 10 Minzi marra wi ɣa ittaren ad iksi, u wi ɣa yarzun ad yaf, u wi ɣa issqarqben ad as ittwarzem.
\v 11 Niɣ din jar awem babas, wenni umi d as i ɣa ittar mmis aɣrum, ad as iwc aẓru? Niɣ umi ɣa ittar asřem, ad as iwc afiɣar deg wemcan n wesřem? \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt Mt. 7:9. \x*
\v 12 Niɣ mařa ittar zzayes tameǧač, ad as iwc taɣarḍent?
\v 13 Mařa kenniw, inni iǧan d iɛeffanen, tessnem ad tewcem timewca tiṣebḥanin i tarwa nwem, mecḥař s waṭṭas ad iwc Babatwem i iǧan deg ijenwan Arruḥ Iqeddsen i yinni d as t ittaren!”
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d Bᵉɛalzabub
\m 
\v 14 Umi issuffeɣ Netta ijj n cciṭan agnaw, imsar, awarni řami issuffeɣ cciṭan nni, aqa agnaw ibda issawař. \add Uca xenni\add* itebhet řɣaci \add marra\add*. \x ◘ \xo 11:14 \xt [Mt. 12:22-30; Mk. 3:20-27] — Mt. 9:32; 12:22. \x*
\v 15 Maca ca zzaysen nnan: “Issuffuɣ ccwaṭen s Bᵉɛalzabub, ameqqran n ccwaṭen.” \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt Mt. 9:34; 12:24; Mk. 3:22. \x*
\v 16 Inneɣni jarrben t, ttaren zzayes ict n řeɛřamet zeg ujenna.
\m 
\v 17 Maca Netta yargeb x ixarriṣen nsen, inna asen: “Kuř tageldit i ibḍan x yixef nnes ad tᵉttwareddeǧ u taddart i ibḍan x yixef nnes, ad tewḍa. \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Mt. 12:25; Mk. 3:24. \x*
\v 18 Mařa ibḍa cciṭan x yixef nnes, mammec ɣa teqqim tgeldit nnes? Minzi kenniw teqqarem belli Necc ssuffuɣeɣ ccwaṭen s Bᵉɛalzabub.
\v 19 Mařa Necc ssuffuɣeɣ ccwaṭen s Bᵉɛalzabub, s minzi i ten ssuffuɣen tarwa nwem? S uyenni ad iřin nitni d lquḍat xawem.
\v 20 Maca mařa tuɣa s uḍaḍ n AREBBI i zi ssuffuɣeɣ ccwaṭen, xenni aqa tqarreb-dd ɣarwem Tgeldit n AREBBI.
\v 21 Min ɣa yekk weryaz ijehden iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ ittɛessa x řemraḥ nnes, ad yiři wagřa nnes di řaman.
\v 22 Maca meřmi i dd ɣa yas wenni iǧan d jjiheř xas, uca ad t iɣřeb, aqa netta ad as ikkes řesnaḥ min xef tuɣa ittcař, uca ad ibḍa min tuɣa zzayes iksi.
\m 
\v 23 Wenni war iǧin akidi, aqa-t ḍidd inu u wenni war kidi issmunin, aqa netta ittzeǧaɛ.” \x ◘ \xo 11:23 \xt Mt. 12:30; Mk. 9:39; Lk. 9:50; 11:23. \x*
\b
\s1 Řaryaḥ amengus nni yarezzun ad dd-iɛqeb
\m 
\v 24 “Xmi ɣa iffeɣ řaryaḥ amengus zi bnadem, ad icuq deg imucan war daysen bu waman, ad yarzu arraḥet uca xmi war tt ittif, ad yini: ‘Ad ɛeqbeɣ ɣar taddart inu tenni zi dd-ffɣeɣ.’ \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt [Mt. 12:43-45] — Mt. 12:43. \x*
\v 25 Xmi dd ɣa yas, ad tt yaf, tfarḍ, teɛdeř.
\v 26 Xenni ad iraḥ, ad iksi sebɛa n řaryaḥ nneɣni iɛeffanen xas, ad dd-adfen uca ad zedɣen dinni. Xenni ad idweř uneggar n bnadem nni d aɛeffan mahu x mammec t tuɣa ɣar umezwar.” \x ◘ \xo 11:26 \xt Yḥ. 5:14; Ɛbr. 6:4, 5; 10:26; 2 Bṭ. 2:20. \x*
\m 
\v 27 Am issawař s uya, tessgeɛɛed ict n temɣart zi řɣaci tmijja nnes, tenna as: “Sseɛd n uɛeddis i Cek iksin u tabbuct i zi tᵉṭṭḍed!”
\v 28 Netta inna: “Sseɛd n yinni ittesřan awař n AREBBI uca ḥeffḍen t.” \x ◘ \xo 11:28 \xt Mt. 7:21; Yḥ. 6:29; Rum. 2:13. \x*
\b
\s1 Řeɛřamet n Yunus
\m 
\v 29 Am tuɣa imun řɣaci, ibda iqqar: “Ttaṣiřet-a d taɛeffant tᵉttᵉttar řeɛřamet, war d as tᵉttmewci řeɛřamet mɣir řeɛřamet n Yunus anabi. \x ◘ \xo 11:29 \xt [Mt. 12:38-42; Mk. 8:12] — Yun. 2:1, 11. \x*
\v 30 Minzi am mammec tuɣa Yunus d řeɛřamet i aytbab n Ninwa, ammu i ɣa yiři Mmis n bnadem ɛawed \add d řeɛřamet\add* i jjiř-a.
\v 31 Tajeǧidt n ljanub ad tekkar deg \add wass n\add* lḥisab ak-d yeryazen n jjiř-a, ad ten tḥaseb. Minzi tusa-dd zi tneggarut n temmurt, ḥima ad tseř i tiɣit n Suliman. Xzar, aqa da wenni imɣaren x Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 11:31 \xt 1 Ij. 10:1; 2 Im. 9:1; Mt. 12:42. \x*
\v 32 Iryazen n Ninwa ad dd-kkaren deg \add wass n\add* lḥisab ak-d jjiř-a uca ad t ḥasben, minzi nitni tuben awarni i ubarreḥ n Yunus. Xzar, aqa da wenni imɣaren x Yunus!” \x ◘ \xo 11:32 \xt Yun. 3:5. \x*
\b
\s1 Řqendiř n arrimet
\m 
\v 33 Uřa d ijj war issreqqi řqendiř uca issrusa t deg wemcan inuffaren niɣ sadu řmud n imendi, maca \add issrusa i-t\add* x řmerfeɛ, ḥima inni dd ɣa yadfen ad ẓaren tfawt. \x ◘ \xo 11:33 \xt [Mt. 5:15; 6:22-23] — Mt. 5:15; Mk. 4:24; Lk. 8:16. \x*
\v 34 Řqendiř n arrimet nnec d tiṭṭ nnec. Mařa tiṭṭ nnec teṣfa, ad tiři tfawt uřa di marra arrimet nnec. Mařa \add tiṭṭ nnec\add* d taɛeffant, uřa d arrimet nnec ad tiři d taǧest. \x ◘ \xo 11:34 \xt Mt. 6:22. \x*
\v 35 Ḥḍa xenni, ḥima tafawt i dayek \add iǧan\add*, war tᵉttiři d taǧest.
\v 36 Mařa marra arrimet nnec teccur s tfawt, war dayes uřa d ijj n uɣezdis ibarrcen, xenni ad dayes tiři tfawt kuřci am mammec xmi yareqq řqendiř s uceɛɛař nnes.”
\b
\s1 Uct x Ifarisiyyen d Imseřmaden n idlisen
\m 
\v 37 Am tuɣa issawař s man aya, iɛarḍ i-t ijj n Ufarisi ɣar umecři akides. Xenni yudef, iqqim ɣar ṭṭabřa. \x ◘ \xo 11:37 \xt [Mt. 23:1-36; Mk. 12:38-40; Lk. 20:45-47]\x*
\v 38 Umi t iẓra Ufarisi, itebhet minzi Netta war issird ca d amezwar qbeř i umecři. \x ◘ \xo 11:38 \xt Mk. 7:3, 4\x*
\m 
\v 39 Maca Yasuɛ inna as: “Kenniw, \add a\add* Ifarisiyyen, tessizdagem barra n řkas d ṭṭebṣi, maca di daxeř nwem tcurrem s \add ṭṭmeɛ n\add* tkeccaḍt d řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 11:39 \xt Mt. 23:25; Tit. 1:15. \x*
\v 40 Kenniw, \add a\add* ifɣař, ma war iǧi Wenni iggin min iǧan ɣar barra, igga uřa d min iǧan daxeř?
\v 41 Maca mařa ad tewcem \add marra\add* min iǧan daxeř d ṣṣedqet, xzar, marra min daywem ad yiři d amezdag.” \x ◘ \xo 11:41 \xt Ica. 58:7; Dan. 4:24; Lk. 12:33. \x*
\m 
\v 42 Maca \bd uct xawem\bd*, \add a\add* Ifarisiyyen minzi tᵉttɛeccaram nneɛnaɛ d wazar d marra tibbi, \add maca\add* tejjim řḥukm d tayri n AREBBI ɣar uɣezdis. Iwa ittxeṣṣa awem ad teggem timesřayin-a, nhřa ma ad tᵉttum inneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 11:42 \xt 1 Ṣm. 15:22; Ḥuc. 6:6; Mixa 6:8; Mt. 9:13; 12:7; 23:23. \x*
\m 
\v 43 \bd Uct xawem\bd*, \add a\add* Ifarisiyyen, minzi iɛjeb awem ad teqqimem x řekrasi n zzat di temzidawin u iɛjeb awem ad xawem seǧmen \add iwdan\add* di řeswaq. \x ◘ \xo 11:43 \xt Mt. 23:6; Mk. 12:38; Lk. 20:46. \x*
\m 
\v 44 \bd Uct xawem\bd*, a imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen, \add kenniw, a\add* imnafqen, minzi kenniw tᵉtteggem am yimeḍřan idduryen min xef gguren iwdan am war ssinen.” \x ◘ \xo 11:44 \xt Mt. 23:27. \x*
\m 
\v 45 Ijjen zeg imseřmaden n idlisen iṭṭef deg wawař, inna as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, aqa xmi teqqared aya, tessfeṭṭaḥed aneɣ uřa d neccin.”
\m 
\v 46 Maca Netta inna: \bd “Uct xawem\bd*, \add a\add* imseřmaden n idlisen, minzi tessarebbum řeḥmuř iḍeqřen i tkessit x iwdan, maca kenniw s yixef nwem war tᵉttḥidim řeḥmuř nni uřa s ijjen zeg iḍewḍan nwem! \x ◘ \xo 11:46 \xt Ica. 10:1; Mt. 23:4; Řex. 15:10. \x*
\m 
\v 47 \bd Uct xawem\bd*, minzi tbennam imeḍřan n inabiyyen, am řejdud nwem nɣin ten. \x ◘ \xo 11:47 \xt Mt. 23:29. \x*
\v 48 S man aya tneɛɛmem, aqa kenniw tareṭṭam s min ggin řejdud nwem, minzi nitni nɣin ten uca kenniw tbennam imeḍřan nsen.
\v 49 S uyenni tiɣit n AREBBI tenna: “Aqa ad asen dd-ssekkeɣ inabiyyen d rrusul. Ad aẓẓřen nitni x \add ca\add* zzaysen uca ad ten nɣen, \x ◘ \xo 11:49 \xt Mt. 10:16; Lk. 10:3; Yḥ. 16:2; Řex. 7:51; Ɛbr. 11:35. \x*
\v 50 ḥima ad ttwattaren zi jjiř-a idammen n marra inabiyyen i ittwassizzřen zeg wami tᵉttwagg ddunect:
\v 51 zeg idammen n Habil ař idammen n Zakariyya, wenni nɣin jar Zzawect Tameqqrant d uɛalṭar! Wah, ad awem iniɣ belli ggur ad ttwattaren \add idammen nsen\add* zi jjiř-a. \x ◘ \xo 11:51 \xt Amz. 4:8; 2 Im. 24:21; Ɛbr. 11:4. \x*
\m 
\v 52 \bd Uct xawem\bd*, \add a\add* imseřmaden n idlisen, minzi tkessim tisarutin n tussna. Kenniw s yixef nwem war tᵉttidfem u inni ittadfen, tᵉṭṭfem ten.” \x ◘ \xo 11:52 \xt Mt. 23:13. \x*
\m 
\v 53 Am tuɣa akidsen issawař s uya, bdan imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen ttḍaddan t aṭṭas. Ffugmen, ḥeccen x wawařen nnes,
\v 54 uca ggin zzayes s tḥraymect aṭṭas, arezzun ad t ṭṭfen s ca zeg uqemmum nnes, ḥima ad t ḍeřmen.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař ɣar imeḥḍaren nnes d řɣaci
\m 
\v 1 Umi munen ibarruten n řɣaci s waṭṭas, ařami bdan \add ɛřayen\add* ɛeffsen ijj x wenneɣni, ibda iqqar i imeḥḍaren nnes: “\bd Ɣar umezwar ḥḍam ixef nwem zeg wentun n Ifarisiyyen, aqa-t d nnifaq!\bd*\x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt [Mt. 10:28-33; 12:32; 10:19-20] — Mt. 16:16; Mk. 8:15. \x*
\v 2 Minzi war din min idřin, war ittᵉttwasseḍhar, u \add war din\add* min inuffaren, war ittᵉttwissin. \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt Ayub 12:22; Mt. 10:26; Mk. 4:22; Lk. 8:17. \x*
\v 3 Minzi marra min tennam di taǧest, ad ittwaseř di tfawt, u min xef tessiwřem deg umezzuɣ deg wexxam n daxeř, ad ittwabarreḥ zzayes x tzeɣwin.”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Necc ad awem iniɣ, \add a\add* imeddukkař inu: \bd War teggʷdem ca zeg inni ineqqen arrimet\bd*, \add maca\add* awarni man aya war zemmaren ad ggen ktar ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Ica. 51:7; Irm. 1:8; Mt. 10:28. \x*
\v 5 Maca Necc ad awem ssecneɣ wenni zi ɣa teggʷedem: Ggʷedem zeg Wenni ɣar iǧa ṣṣulṭa, maḥend ad inḍar di jᵉhennama awarni řami inɣa. Wah, ad awem iniɣ, zeg Wanita i ɣa teggʷedem!
\v 6 Ma war ttmenzin xemsa n ẓẓawec s tnayen n iṣuldiyyen n nnḥas? Uca uřa d ijj zzaysen war ittᵉttwattu zzat i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Mt. 10:29. \x*
\v 7 Maca zzaywem, ɛad iẓuṭṭan n ucuwwaf n uzeǧif nwem ttwaḥesben. S uyenni war teggʷdem ca, kenniw ḥsen zi ẓẓawec aṭṭas!” \f ◼ \fr 12:7 \fk ẓẓawec\ft - niɣ: ‘iẓẓawjiwen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt 1 Ṣm. 14:45; 2 Ṣm. 14:11; 1 Ij. 1:52; Lk. 21:18. \x*
\m 
\v 8 “Necc ad awem iniɣ, marra wi zzayi i ɣa icehden qibač i iwdan, ad zzayes iched ɛawed Mmis n bnadem zzat i lmalakat n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Mt. 10:32. \x*
\v 9 Maca wi d ayi ɣa inkaren qibač i iwdan, uřa d netta s yixef nnes ad ittwankar qibač i lmalakat n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 12:9 \xt Mt. 10:33; Mk. 8:38; Lk. 9:26; 2 Tim. 2:12; 1 Yḥ. 2:23. \x*
\m 
\v 10 Kuř ijj wenni i ɣa inin awař ḍidd n Mmis n bnadem, aqa ad as ittwaɣfar man aya. Maca wenni i ɣa iceqqfen di Arruḥ Iqeddsen war d as ittᵉttwaɣfar ca man aya!” \x ◘ \xo 12:10 \xt 1 Yḥ. 5:16. \x*
\m 
\v 11 “Xmi kenniw i ɣa nedhen ɣar temzidawin, zzat i řḥukkam d ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa, war kessim ca s wemnus min zi i dd ɣa tarrem niɣ min ɣa tinim, \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt Mt. 10:19; Mk. 13:11; Lk. 21:14. \x*
\v 12 minzi Arruḥ Iqeddsen ad awem isseřmed di tsaɛɛet nni min ittxeṣṣa ad tinim.”
\b
\s1 Amedya n bab n wagřa
\m 
\v 13 Inna as ijjen zi řɣaci: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, ini as i uma, ḥima ad kidi ibḍa řwart.”
\v 14 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna as: “\add A\add* bnadem, wi d ayi yarrin xawem d řqaḍi niɣ d řɛadeř?”
\v 15 Inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Ɣarwem, ḥḍam ixef nwem zi ṭṭmeɛ, maɣar tudart war teǧi deg ufeyyeḍ n wagřa.” \x ◘ \xo 12:15 \xt 1 Tim. 6:7. \x*
\m 
\v 16 \add Xas uca\add* iḥaja asen ijj n umedya: “Tammurt n ijj n weryaz d bab n wagřa tiwyi as-dd ṣṣabet aṭṭas.
\v 17 Ixarreṣ deg ixef nnes: ‘Min ɣa ggeɣ?, minzi war ɣari bu řmarsi i di i ɣa yarweɣ \add marra\add* řɣiǧet inu.’
\v 18 Inna: ‘Ammu i ɣa ggeɣ: Ad hedmeɣ řemrasi inu, xenni ad bniɣ \add řemrasi\add* d imeqqranen xasen uca ad daysen xezneɣ marra řɣiǧet d wagřa inu.
\v 19 Ad iniɣ i yixef inu: ‘\add A\add* řeɛmar \add inu\add*, ɣarek aṭṭas n wagřa i ittwaxzen din i waṭṭas n iseggʷusa. Areyyeḥ, tecced, teswed u tfarḥed!’ \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt Amb. 11:9; 1 Kur. 15:32; Yaɛ. 5:5. \x*
\v 20 Maca inna as AREBBI: ‘\add A\add* afɣuř, aqa ǧiřet-a ad zzayek ittwattar řeɛmar nnec. Xenni i umi ɣa yiři min tesswejded?’ \x ◘ \xo 12:20 \xt Izhd. 39:7; Izhd. 52:7; Amb. 2:18, 19; Irm. 17:11. \x*
\v 21 Ammu i ɣa imsar i wenni iyarrwen řeknuz i yixef nnes, \add maca\add* war iǧi d bab n wagřa di AREBBI.”
\b
\s1 Tageldit n Arebbi d amezwaru
\m 
\v 22 Inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: “S uyenni Necc ad awem iniɣ: War kessim s wemnus i řeɛmar nwem min ɣa teccem, uřa i arrimet nwem min ɣa tyarḍem. \x ◘ \xo 12:22 \xt [Mt. 6:19-21; 25-34] — Izhd. 55:23; Mt. 6:25; Fil. 4:6; 1 Tim. 6:8; 1 Bṭ. 5:7. \x*
\v 23 Řeɛmar ktar zi macca u arrimet ktar zeg werruḍ.
\v 24 Xzarem ɣar ibaɣřiwen! Aqa war zarrɛen, war mejjaren, war ɣarsen tisrafin niɣ d řemrasi, \add maca\add* AREBBI issecca i-ten. Mecḥař aṭṭas tsekkwim kenniw ktar x ijḍaḍ! \x ◘ \xo 12:24 \xt Ayub 38:41; Izhd. 147:9. \x*
\v 25 Man wen zzaywem izemmar s wemnus nnes ad yarni di tuzzeggart nnes ijj n uɣiř \add waha\add*? \x ◘ \xo 12:25 \xt Mt. 6:27. \x*
\v 26 Mařa kenniw war tzemmarem uřa x min iǧan d ameẓyan qaɛ, mayemmi ɣa teksim s wemnus x min iqqimen?”
\b
\m 
\v 27 “Xzarem mammec ɣemmyent tlillicin! War xeddment, war ttqareḍcent, \add maca\add* Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa uřa d Suliman di qaɛ aɛuǧi nnes war yarḍ ca am uřa d ict zzaysent. \f ◼ \fr 12:27 \fk tilillicin\ft - ijj n marka n nnuwarat daysen aẓri aṭṭas.\f*
\v 28 Mařa AREBBI issyarḍ ammu arbiɛ i iǧan ass-a deg iyyar uca tiwecca ad immenḍar di tefqunt, mecḥař iḥřa aṭṭas ad issyarḍ Netta kenniw i di iǧa drus n l’iman!”
\b
\m 
\v 29 “S uyenni war arezzum ca x min ɣa teccem uřa x min ɣa teswem, war ttejjim ixarriṣen nwem ad ɣefřem x man aya.
\v 30 Minzi marra timesřayin-a arezzun daysent řegnus n ddunect, maca Babatwem issen belli teḥdajem tent.
\v 31 Maca arzum Tageldit n AREBBI uca timesřayin-a marra ad awem ttwammarnint.” \x ◘ \xo 12:31 \xt 1 Im. 3:13; Izhd. 37:25. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 32 “War tteggʷed, \add cem,\add* \add a\add* taḥimart tameẓyant, minzi yarḍa Babatwem ad awem iwc Tageldit.
\v 33 Zenzem min ɣarwem, wcem ṣṣedqet! Ggem i yixef nwem ticyarin n tmenyat i war yareccin, uca \add xemmřem\add* ijj n řkenz i war iqeṭṭin deg ijenwan, mani war ittidef uceffar uřa d tcinda war tᵉttegg ssuss. \x ◘ \xo 12:33 \xt Mt. 6:20; 19:21; Lk. 16:9; 1 Tim. 6:19. \x*
\v 34 Minzi mani ɣa yiři řkenz nwem, dinni i ɣa yiři ɛawed wuř nwem.”
\b
\s1 Aɛqab n bab n taddart
\m 
\v 35 “Ad iřint tejɛinnatin nwem ḥezzmemt s ibuyas u řefnarat nwem areqqent. \x ◘ \xo 12:35 \xt [Mt. 24:45-51] — Afa. 6:14; 1 Bṭ. 1:13. \x*
\v 36 Iřim am iwdan i ittrajan sidi nsen xmi dd ɣa yeɛqeb zeg wexxam n wurar, ḥima, xmi dd ɣa yas, ad issqarqeb, zemmaren ad as arzmen deɣya.
\v 37 Sseɛd n imsexxaren nni, xmi dd ɣa yas siditsen, ad ten yaf faqen. S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa ad iḥezzem ixef nnes uca ad ten issɣim, xenni ad dd-yas ad xasen isexxar.
\v 38 Mařa yusa-dd ɣar ḥeṭṭu wiss tnayen n ǧiřet niɣ ɣar ḥeṭṭu wiss třata uca yufa i-ten ammu, sseɛd n imsexxaren nni. \x ◘ \xo 12:38 \xt Mt. 24:42. \x*
\v 39 Maca ssnem aya: mařa bab n taddart issen di man tsaɛɛet i di ɣa ixecc uceffar, xenni ad yiři ifaq, war ittejji taddart nnes ad tt acaren. \x ◘ \xo 12:39 \xt Mt. 24:43; 1 Ts. 5:2; 2 Bṭ. 3:10; Asa. 3:3; 16:15. \x*
\v 40 Iřim kenniw ɛawed twejdem, minzi Mmis n bnadem ad dd-yas deg ict n tsaɛɛet i war tᵉttrijim.” \x ◘ \xo 12:40 \xt Mt. 24:44; 25:13; Mk. 13:33; Lk. 21:34; 1 Ts. 5:6. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n wewkiř amtiqqi
\m 
\v 41 Inna as Cimɛun Buṭrus: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, ma i neccin i tɛawded amedya-ya niɣ i marra?”
\v 42 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Man wen iǧan xenni d awkiř amiɣis i di iǧa řaman, d wenni i ɣa yegg sidis x imsexxaren nnes ḥima ad \add asen\add* iwc řeɛweč \add nsen\add* di řweqt nnes? \x ◘ \xo 12:42 \xt Mt. 24:45; 25:21; 1 Kur. 4:2. \x*
\v 43 Sseɛd n umsexxar nni i ɣa yaf sidi nnes, xmi dd ɣa yas, ittegg ammu.
\v 44 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, belli ad t yegg x marra agřa nnes.
\v 45 Maca mařa amsexxar nni ad yini deg wuř nnes: ‘Aqa sidi inu iɛeṭṭař x weɛqab!’, uca ibda iccat imsexxaren d tiyya, ittett, isess, iscar,
\v 46 xenni ad dd-yas sidi n umsexxar nni deg ijj n wass war ittriji u deg ict n tsaɛɛet i war issin. Wanita ad t iqeṭṭes d iceǧiqen, ad igg tasɣart nnes ak-d iɣeddaren.
\v 47 Amsexxar nni issnen řxaḍar n sidi nnes uca war issewjed ixef nnes uřa war iggi ɛlaḥsab řxaḍar n sides, ad iksi tiyyita aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 12:47 \xt Yaɛ. 4:17. \x*
\v 48 Maca wenni war issinen \add řxaḍar n sides\add* \add am\add* igga ca min isdaheǧen tiyyita, ad ittwawwet s drus n tiyyita. Zi kuř ijjen umi immewc aṭṭas, ad zzayes ittwattar aṭṭas, u wi umi ittwakellef aṭṭas, ad zzayes ittwattar ktar.”
\b
\s1 Tawasit n Yasuɛ ad tawi abeṭṭu
\m 
\v 49 “Usiɣ-dd ḥima ad nḍareɣ timessi x temmurt u meɛlik ufiɣ ad tiři tarɣa. \x ◘ \xo 12:49 \xt [Mt. 10:34-36] \x*
\v 50 \add Maca\add* ɣari ijj n useɣḍeṣ i zi ɣa ttwassɣeḍṣeɣ, u ttwaḥṣareɣ aṭṭas ař d ɣa ittwakemmeř. \x ◘ \xo 12:50 \xt Mt. 20:22; Mk. 10:38. \x*
\v 51 Ma ittɣiř awem belli usiɣ-dd ḥima ad ssiwḍeɣ řehna x temmurt? Lla, ad awem iniɣ, d amezwar abeṭṭu. \x ◘ \xo 12:51 \xt Mt. 10:34. \x*
\v 52 Minzi zi řexxu d tsawent ad mmsebḍan xemsa deg ict n taddart, třata ḍidd tnayen u tnayen ḍidd třata.
\v 53 Babas ad immsebḍa x mmis, u mmis x babas, u yemmas x yeǧis, u yeǧis x yemmas, u řallas x tesřit, u tasřit x řallas.” \x ◘ \xo 12:53 \xt Mixa 7:6\x*
\b
\s1 Ittxeṣṣa ad nmeyyez zzamanat
\m 
\v 54 Inna i řɣaci: “Xmi ɣa tẓarem ijj n useynu igeɛɛed-dd zi řɣarb, deɣya ad tinim: ‘Ad yiři wenẓar!’ uca ammu i ɣa imsar! \x ◘ \xo 12:54 \xt [Mt. 16:2-3]\x*
\v 55 Xmi ɣa tẓarem asemmiḍ n ljanub ittsuḍ, xenni ad tinim: ‘Ad yiři řeḥmu!’, uca \add ammu\add* i ɣa imsar.
\v 56 \add A\add* imnafqen, aqa tessnem ad tmeyyzem udem n temmurt d ujenna. Ma zzman-a mammec war tzemmaren ad t tmeyyzem?”
\b
\s1 Ggem aṣřaḥ ak-d weɣrim nnek
\m 
\v 57 “Mayemmi war tḥekkmem s yixef nwem min iǧan d ṣṣaḥ? \x ◘ \xo 12:57 \xt [Mt. 5:25-26]\x*
\v 58 Minzi, xmi ɣa traḥed ɣar řḥakem ak-d weɣrim nnec, egg tizemmar am teǧid ɛad \add akis\add* deg webrid maḥend ad zzayes tᵉttwafekked, ḥima war cek ittjarri ɣar řqaḍi uca řqaḍi ad cek isellem i wemxazni, xenni ad cek inḍar umxazni di řeḥbes.
\v 59 Ad ac iniɣ, cek war dd ssenni tᵉtteffɣed ař ɣa txeǧṣed aṣuldi aneggaru!”
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Amedya n wartu i war itticcen řɣiǧet
\m 
\v 1 Di řweqt nni usin-dd \add ɣares\add* ca n iwdan, xebbaren t x Ijaliliyyen inni ixeǧeḍ Pilaṭus idammen nsen ak-d tɣarṣin nsen.
\v 2 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ma ittɣiř awem belli Ijaliliyyen-a d imednab ktar zeg Ijaliliyyen nneɣni umi d asen imsar uweddeb-a?
\v 3 Ad awem iniɣ, lla! Maca kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem marra am nitni, mařa war tᵉttubem.
\v 4 U zi jjihet n tmenṭac \add n iwdan\add* i xef dd-tewḍa ṣṣumɛet di Siluwam uca mmuten zzayes, ma ittɣiř awem aqa aten d imednab ktar zeg iwdan \add nneɣni\add* i izeddɣen di Urcalim?
\v 5 Ad awem iniɣ, lla! Maca kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem marra am nitni, mařa war tᵉttubem!”
\b
\m 
\v 6 Inna asen amedya-ya: “Tuɣa ɣar ijj n weryaz ijj n wartu i ittwaẓẓun deg umarjeɛ nnes n uḍiř, uca netta yusa-dd, yarezzu dayes tazart, \add maca\add* war tt yufi.
\v 7 Inna i bab n umarjeɛ n uḍiř: ‘Aqa třata n iseggʷusa ttaseɣ-dd, arezzuɣ tazart deg wartu-ya, war tt ufiɣ. Qess i-tt \add xenni\add*, mayemmi tessaḥař ɛad tammurt?’
\v 8 Yarra-dd xas ufeǧaḥ: ‘A sidi, ejj i-tt \add ad tbedd\add* ɛad aseggʷas-a. Ad tt ɣziɣ, u ad as ggeɣ řeɣbar.
\v 9 Ad taɣ ad tarr řɣiǧet, mařa lla, xenni qess i-tt deg useggʷas i dd ɣa yasen.’”
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ict n temɣart deg wass n ssebt
\m 
\v 10 Řami tuɣa isseřmad Yasuɛ deg icten zi temzidawin di ssebt,
\v 11 tuɣa din ict n temɣart i iḍɛef buḥbeř nnes řmijař n tmenṭac n iseggʷusa. Tuɣa teqwes, war tzemmar ad tseggem aɛrur.
\v 12 Umi tt iẓra Yasuɛ, iřaɣa-dd xas ɣares, inna as: “\add A\add* tamɣart, aqa cem tenfekked zi tuḍɛeft nnem!”
\v 13 Issars xas afus nnes uca nettat tedweř tseggem řexdenni, tebda tessemɣara di AREBBI!
\v 14 Maca ameqqran n temzida, umi ixeyyeq, minzi Yasuɛ issgenfa \add ijjen\add* di ssebt, iṭṭef deg wawař, inna i řɣaci: “Aqa di setta n wussan ittxeṣṣa řxedmet, asem-dd deg wussan nni maḥend ad tᵉttwassgenfam, war iǧi deg wass n ssebt!” \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt Uf. 20:9; Aɛwd. 5:13; Ḥiz. 20:12. \x*
\v 15 \add Maca\add* yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “\add A cek,\add* amnafeq! Ma war ifessi kuř ijjen zzaywem di ssebt i ufunas nnes niɣ i weɣyuř nnes zi řmedwed, xenni ad t indeh maḥend ad t iward? \x ◘ \xo 13:15 \xt Uf. 23:5; Aɛwd. 22:4; Lk. 14:5. \x*
\v 16 Maca tamɣart-a aqa-tt d yeǧis n Ibrahim, tenni icedd ibřis, xzar, \add ɛad\add* řmijař n tmenṭac n iseggʷusa, ma war d as dd-yusi ad tᵉttwafekk zeg uceddi-ya deg wass n ssebt?”
\v 17 Am inna man aya, seḍḥan marra inni tuɣa akides ittemɛařan, \add maca\add* marra řɣaci ifarḥ zi lmuɛjizat nni tuɣa ittwaggen s ufus nnes.
\b
\s1 Imedya n tḥebbuct n zzariɛet n uxerdel u n wentun
\m 
\v 18 Yasuɛ inna: “Min di tarwes Tgeldit n AREBBI uca min zi tt ɣa ssemquddeɣ? \x ◘ \xo 13:18 \xt [Mt. 13:31-33; Mk. 4:30-32] — Mt. 13:31; Mk. 4:30. \x*
\v 19 Aqa-tt am yict n tḥebbuct n zzariɛet n uxerdel iksi tt ijj n weryaz, inḍar i-tt di teḥwict nnes, uca teɣmi-dd, tedweř d tacejjart temɣar uca ggin ijḍaḍ n ujenna řeɛwacc nsen di řefruɛ nnes.” \f ◼ \fr 13:19 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’). \fk axerdel\ft - s Tafransist: ‘mutardi’.\f*
\m 
\v 20 Yasuɛ inna ɛawed: “S min zi ɣa ssemquddeɣ Tageldit n AREBBI? \x ◘ \xo 13:20 \xt Mt. 13:33. \x*
\v 21 Aqa-tt am wentun, teysi t temɣart, teffar i-t di třata n řemdud n waren, ařami issmemm marra!”
\b
\s1 Tawwart iḥsaren
\m 
\v 22 Iẓwa tineddam d dcurat, am tuɣa isseřmad, iggur ɣar Urcalim. \f ◼ \fr 13:22 \fk dcurat\ft - niɣ ‘ředcur’ niɣ ‘ibilajen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:22 \xt [Mt. 7:13-14; 21-23] — Mt. 9:35; Mk. 6:6. \x*
\v 23 Ijjen isseqsa i-t, ma aqa din drus n yinni i ɣa ṭṭfen Tudart.
\v 24 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ggem jjehd nwem, ḥima ad tadfem zi tewwart iḥṣaren, aqa Necc ad awem iniɣ, aṭṭas ad arzun ad dd-adfen, \add maca\add* war zemmaren. \x ◘ \xo 13:24 \xt Mt. 7:13. \x*
\v 25 Zeg wami i ɣa ikkar Bab n taddart maḥend ad ibelleɛ tawwart, xenni ad tbeddem di barra, ad tessqareqbem, ad tebdam ad tinim: ‘\add A\add* Siditneɣ, \add a\add* Siditneɣ, arzem aneɣ!’ Maca Netta ad dd-yarr, ad yini: ‘Necc war kenniw ssineɣ, manis kenniw?’ \x ◘ \xo 13:25 \xt Mt. 25:11, 12; Lk. 6:46. \x*
\v 26 Ad tebdam ad tinim: ‘Neccin aḥeqqa tuɣa necca neswa qibač nnec, uca Cek tuɣa tesseřmaded deg imesraq nneɣ!’
\v 27 \add Maca\add* Netta ad yini: ‘War kenniw ssineɣ, \add war ssineɣ\add* manis kenniw! Aggʷejem xafi, kenniw inni itteggen řmuɛṣiyyet!’ \x ◘ \xo 13:27 \xt Izhd. 6:9; Mt. 7:23; 25:12,41. \x*
\v 28 Ad din tiři tɣuyyit d uɣezzi n teɣmas, xmi ɣa tẓarem Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub d marra inabiyyen di Tgeldit n AREBBI, maca kenniw ad temmenḍarem barra. \x ◘ \xo 13:28 \xt Mt. 8:11, 12; 13:42; 24:51. \x*
\v 29 Ad dd-asen zi manis d tneqqar tfuct u zi mani tɣeǧi tfuct uřa zi ccamal uřa zi ljanub, ad qqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* di Tgeldit n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 13:29 \xt Ica. 2:2; Mal. 1:11; Mt. 8:11. \x*
\v 30 Xzar, aqa din ineggura inni i ɣa yiřin d imezwura, u aqa din imezwura inni i ɣa yiřin d ineggura.” \x ◘ \xo 13:30 \xt Mt. 19:30; 20:16; Mk. 10:31. \x*
\b
\s1 Awařen ineggura n Yasuɛ x Urcalim
\m 
\v 31 Deg wass nni qarrben-dd ca n Ifarisiyyen, nnan as: “Ffeɣ, ruḥ ssa, minzi Hirudus ixs ad Cek ineɣ!” \x ◘ \xo 13:31 \xt [Mt. 23:37-39]\x*
\v 32 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Ruḥem, inim as i wecɛeb-a: ‘Xẓar, aqa Necc ssuffuɣeɣ ccwaṭen, ssgenfiɣ ass-a d tiwecca, uca deg wass wiss třata ad iwḍeɣ ɣar řekmaret.” \f ◼ \fr 13:32 \fk ad iwḍeɣ ɣar řekmaret\ft - ixs ad yini ‘ad qḍiɣ řxedmet inu’. Xzar Mat. 5:17.\f*
\v 33 Maca ittxeṣṣa ayi ad xedmeɣ ass-a d tiwecca, uca deg wass awarni as ad raḥeɣ, minzi war izemmar ad ittwaneɣ ijj n unabi barra i Urcalim.
\v 34 \add A\add* Urcalim, \add a\add* Urcalim, tenni ineqqen inabiyyen d tenni yarejjmen inni i ɣarem dd-ittwassekken, mecḥař n twařawin tuɣa xseɣ ad ssmuneɣ tarwa nnem am mammec tessmuna tyaẓiḍt ifiǧusen nnes sadu wafriwen nnes, \add maca\add* kenniw war texsem. \x ◘ \xo 13:34 \xt Izhd. 17:8; 91:4; Mt. 23:37. \x*
\v 35 Xzar, taddart nwem ad awem teqqim d řxarbet. Maɣar Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa war d ayi tẓarrem ař dd ɣa tas řweqt i di i ɣa tinim: ‘Lbaraka i Wenni dd ɣa yasen s Yisem n SIDI’.” \x ◘ \xo 13:35 \xt Izhd. 69:26; 118:26; Ica. 1:7; Irm. 7:34; Mixa 3:12; Mt. 23:38; Řex. 1:20. \x*
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n umehřuc s tuffet n waman deg wass n ssebt
\m 
\v 1 Řami yudef ɣar taddart n ijj zeg imeqqranen n Ifarisiyyen ḥima ad icc aɣrum deg wass n ssebt, tuɣa ḥeṭṭan t.
\v 2 U xzar, ibedd din qibač nnes ijj n bnadem ihřec s tuffet n waman \add n arrimet nnes\add*.
\v 3 Iṭṭef Yasuɛ deg wawař, inna i imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen, inna: “Ma iḥeǧeř usgenfi di ssebt?”
\v 4 Nitni sqaren waha. \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef i-t, issgenfa i-t uca ijja i-t ad iraḥ.
\v 5 Xenni yarra-dd xasen inna: “Man wen zzaywem, mařa mmis niɣ afunas nnes iwḍa as deg wanu, war t-i-dd-issuffuɣ zzayes deɣya deg wass n ssebt?” \x ◘ \xo 14:5 \xt Uf. 23:5; Aɛwd. 22:4; Lk. 13:15. \x*
\v 6 War ufin s min zi xas dd ɣa yarren.
\b
\s1 Amedya x uwaḍeɛ
\m 
\v 7 Iɛawed ijj n umedya i inewjiwen am d asen iḥekkar ixḍaren imucan imezwura. \add Inna asen\add*:
\v 8 “Mařa iɛarḍ ḥed i cek ɣar ijj n wurar xenni war ttɣimi deg wemcan amezwaru, ḥima war ittwaɛarḍ wenneɣni yuɛřan \add xak\add*, maḥend ad iqqim din,
\v 9 uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-yas wenni xak iɛarḍen, ad ac yini: ‘Egg amcan i weryaz-a!’, \add uca xenni\add* ad tseḍḥid, ad tekkared ḥima ad teksid amcan aneggaru.
\v 10 Mařa cek tᵉttwaɛarḍed, ruḥ, qqim deg wemcan aneggaru, ḥima, xmi dd ɣa yadef wenni xak iɛarḍen, ad taɣ ad ac yini: ‘\add A\add* ameddukkeř, geɛɛed, qqim!’ Xenni ad ac yiři ccan zzat i yinni akidek iqqimen. \x ◘ \xo 14:10 \xt Awřn. 25:6, 7. \x*
\v 11 Minzi marra wi ɣa issuɛřan ixef nnes ad ittwasswaḍeɛ u wi ɣa isswaḍɛen ixef nnes ad ittwassuɛřa.” \x ◘ \xo 14:11 \xt Ayub 22:29; Awřn. 29:23; Mt. 23:12; Lk. 1:51; 18:14; Yaɛ. 4:6, 10; 1 Bṭ. 5:5. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n yinni ittwaɛarḍen i umensi
\m 
\v 12 Inna ɛawed i wenni t iɛarḍen: “Mařa cek teggid ijj n umecři niɣ amensi, war ɛarreḍ imeddukkař nnec niɣ aytmac, uřa d řaǧ nnec niɣ jjiran nnec i ɣar iǧa wagřa, niɣ aqa ad cek ɛarḍen uřa d nitni uca ad ɣarek yiři řexřaṣ. \x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt [Mt. 22:1-10] — Naḥ. 8:10; Awřn. 3:28. \x*
\v 13 Mařa tɛarḍed \add x iwdan\add*, xenni ɛarḍ x imezřaḍ d iqiydaren d ineɛḍaben d idarɣařen.
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ad tiřid d amesɛud umi war ɣarsen s minzi cek i ɣa xeǧṣen, minzi ad tᵉṭṭfed řexraṣ nnec di tnukra n imseggaden.”
\m 
\v 15 Umi isřa aya ijjen zeg inni din iqqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add*, inna as wanita: “Sseɛd n wenni i ɣa iccen aɣrum di Tgeldit n AREBBI!”
\v 16 Yasuɛ inna as: “Ijj n weryaz igga ict n zzardet temɣar uca iɛarḍ aṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*. \x ◘ \xo 14:16 \xt Ica. 25:6; Mt. 22:2; Asa. 19:7, 9. \x*
\v 17 Issekk amsexxar nnes di tsaɛɛet n zzardet, ḥima ad ini i inewjiwen: ‘Xzar, kuřci aqa iwjed i kenniw. Araḥem-dd!’
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* ibda kuř ijjen zzaysen ad igg ssibbet. Inna as umezwar: ‘Sɣiɣ ijj n iyyar, aqa ittxeṣṣa ayi ad raḥeɣ ad t ẓareɣ. Ttareɣ ac ad ayi tsamḥed!’
\v 19 Wenneɣni inna: ‘Sɣiɣ xemsa n tyuya n iyenduzen, aqa ad raḥeɣ ad ten jarrbeɣ, ttareɣ ac ad ayi tsamḥed!’
\v 20 U wenneɣni inna: ‘Aqa mammec meřceɣ tamɣart, x uyenni war zemmareɣ ad dd-aseɣ!’
\m 
\v 21 Idweř-dd umsexxar nni uca ixebbar sidi nnes s man aya. Xenni ixeyyeq bab n taddart, inna i umsexxar nnes: ‘Ruḥ deɣya ɣar wazzayen d zznaqi n tendint, uca ndeh-dd imezřaḍ d iqiydaren d ineɛḍaben d idarɣařen!’
\v 22 Inna umsexxar: ‘\add A\add* sidi, aqa imsar am mammec i tumured, uca aqa din ɛad amcan.’
\v 23 Inna bab i umsexxar nnes: ‘Ffeɣ ɣar ibriden d zznaqi uca ḥṣar i-ten ad adfen ař ɣa teccur taddart inu,
\v 24 minzi Necc ad awem iniɣ, belli uřa d ijj zeg yeryazen inni tuɣa ittwaɛarḍen, ad yiři ɣar zzardet inu’”
\b
\s1 Aḍfar n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 25 Am tuɣa ijj n ubarru d ameqqran n řɣaci iggur akides, inneqřeb-dd, inna asen: \x ◘ \xo 14:25 \xt [Mt. 10:37-38]\x*
\v 26 “Mařa yusa-dd ḥed ɣari uca war icarreh babas niɣ yemmas, aytmas niɣ suyᵉtmas, tamɣart nnes niɣ tarwa nnes, u ɛad uřa d ixef nnes, war izemmar ad yiři d ameḥḍar inu. \x ◘ \xo 14:26 \xt Aɛwd. 13:7; 33:9; Mt. 10:37. \x*
\v 27 Wenni war iksin ṣṣalib nnes, ad ayi dd-iḍfar, war izemmar ad yiři d ameḥḍar inu. \x ◘ \xo 14:27 \xt Mt. 10:38; 16:24; Mk. 8:34; Lk. 9:23. \x*
\v 28 U man wen zzaywem i ixsen ad ibna ict n ṣṣumɛet, war ittɣimi amezwar ḥima ad igg řeḥsab, ma ɣares min ixeṣṣen i ukemmeř,
\v 29 ḥima, mařa issars dsas, \add xenni\add* war izemmar ad as ikemmeř, war xas ḍeḥḥcen marra inni t iẓrin,
\v 30 ad inin: ‘Aryaz-a ibda řebni uca war izemmar ad t ikemmeř.’
\m 
\v 31 Niɣ man ajeǧid, mařa iffeɣ ɣar umenɣi ḍidd n ijj n ujeǧid nneɣni, war ittemcawar amezwar ma izemmar ad imqudda s ɛecra-ařaf ak-d wenni ɣares i dd ɣa yasen s ɛicrin-ařef?
\v 32 Mařa war iǧi amenni, xenni ad dd-issekk ireqqasen am iǧa \add ujeǧid\add* nni ɛad ɣar řaggʷaj, ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* ittar aṣřaḥ.
\m 
\v 33 S uyenni uřa d ijj zzaywem wenni war ittejji marra agřa nnes, war izemmar ad yiři d ameḥḍar inu.”
\b
\s1 Amedya n tmeǧaḥt
\m 
\v 34 “Tameǧaḥt teḥřa, maca mařa texsar tmeǧaḥt aředdi nnes, s min zi tt i ɣa iɛedřen? \x ◘ \xo 14:34 \xt [Mt. 5:13; Mk. 9:50] \x*
\v 35 War tṣeǧeḥ ca i temmurt uřa i tzubač, xenni ad tt nḍaren. Wenni ɣar iǧa imezzuɣen i useǧi, ejj i-t ad iseř.”
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Amedya n uḥuři iweddaren
\m 
\v 1 Xenni tuɣa ayt n ḍḍariba d imednab ttqarraben ɣares ḥima ad as sřen. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt [Mt. 18:12-14] — Mt. 9:10; Mk. 2:15; Lk. 5:29. \x*
\v 2 Ttmeɛmiɛen imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen, qqaren: “Aqa Wa yareḥḥeb s imednab uca ittett akidsen.”
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iḥaja asen Yasuɛ amedya-ya:
\v 4 “Man bnadem zzaywem i ɣar iǧa mya n iḥuřiyyen uca iweddar as ijjen zzaysen, ma war ittejji tesɛa u tesɛin di řexřa uca ad yarzu x wenni iweddaren ař t ɣa yaf?
\v 5 U xmi t ɣa yaf, ad ifraḥ, ad t issars x tɣardin nnes.
\v 6 Xmi dd ɣa yaweḍ ɣar taddart, ad iřaɣa x imeddukkař nnes d jjiran nnes, ad asen yini: ‘Farḥem akidi, minzi ufiɣ ahuři inu iweddaren!’
\v 7 Necc ad awem iniɣ, ammu i ɣa tiři řefraḥet deg ujenna x ijj n umednub i ɣa ituben ktar x tesɛa u-tesɛin n imseggaden i war ixsen ad tuben!” \x ◘ \xo 15:7 \xt Lk. 5:32. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n uṣuldi iweddaren
\m 
\v 8 “Niɣ man tamɣart i ɣar iǧa ɛecra \add n tepyisin n ijj n\add* ‘jjuz’, mařa iweddar icten zzaysent, ma war tessruɣi řqendiř, ad tfarḍ taddart uca ad tarzu mliḥ ař tt ɣa taf? \f ◼ \fr 15:8 \fk dirham\ft - s Tyunanit: ‘draxma’, ijj n uṣuldi di řweqt n Irumaniyyen. S iřes n Tramit: ‘zuza’.\f*
\v 9 Mařa tufi tt, ad třaɣa x tmeddukař d tijjarin, ad asent tini: ‘Farḥent akidi, minzi ufiɣ \add tapyist n\add* ‘jjuz’ nni tuɣa d ayi iweddaren.’
\v 10 Necc ad awem iniɣ, ammu i ɣa tiři řefraḥet qibač i lmalakat n AREBBI s yijj n umednub i ɣa ituben.”
\b
\s1 Amedya n mmis iweddaren
\m 
\v 11 Yasuɛ inna asen ɛawed: “Ijj n bnadem tuɣa ɣares tnayen n iḥenjiren.
\v 12 Inna umaẓuẓ nsen i babas: ‘A baba, ewc ayi tasɣart tenni d ayi dd-yusin zeg wagřa nnec!’ \add Xas uca\add* ibḍa asen \add babas\add* agřa nnes.
\v 13 Awarni ca n wussan issmun mmis amaẓuẓ kuřci min d as immewcen, xenni isafar ɣar ict n temmurt tiggʷej. Iqarḍ marra agřa nnes am isseɛdu dinni ict n tudart n ufecceḥ.
\m 
\v 14 Awarni řami iqarḍ kuřci, iwḍa-dd ijj n řaẓ iwɛar di temmurt nni uca ibda ad iḥwaj.
\v 15 Iruḥ uca iřṣeq deg ijjen zeg imezdaɣ n temmurt nni uca wanita issekk i-t ɣar iyyar nnes ḥima ad yarwes iřfan.
\v 16 Tuɣa immeẓri ad iccur aɛeddis nnes s tesriɣwa, tenni ittetten iřfan, \add maca\add* uřa d ijj war d as iwci ca.
\v 17 Idweř ɣar řeɛqeř nnes, inna: ‘Mecḥař n ixemmasen n baba i ɣar iǧa aɣrum aṭṭas u necc da ttmettiɣ s řaẓ!
\v 18 Ad kkareɣ, ad raḥeɣ ɣar baba uca ad as iniɣ: ‘\add A\add* baba, aqa xḍiɣ ak-d ujenna u akidek!
\v 19 War sdiheǧeɣ ad ayi třaɣid d mmic. Egg ayi am yijjen zeg icuwwaren nnec.’
\m 
\v 20 Ikkar uca iɛqeb ɣar babas. Am t tuɣa ɛad ɣar řaggʷaj, ibarq i-t babas, iḥinn xas, uca yuzzeř ɣares, ingez as x yiri, issudem i-t. \x ◘ \xo 15:20 \xt Řex. 2:39; Afa. 2:12, 17. \x*
\v 21 Inna as mmis: ‘\add A\add* baba, xḍiɣ ak-d ujenna u akidek. War sdiheǧeɣ ad ayi řaɣan mmic.’
\v 22 Maca babas inna i imsexxaren nnes: ‘Suffɣem-dd arruḍ iḥřan aṭṭas, syarḍem as t, ggem txadent deg ufus nnes uca qqnem as sandaliyat \add i iḍaren nnes\add*.
\v 23 Awyem-dd ayenduz iṣeḥḥen, tɣarṣem as, xenni ad necc, ad nfarḥ,
\v 24 minzi mmi wanita tuɣa immut, iddar. Tuɣa iweddar, \add maca\add* ittwaf.’ Xenni bdan ad farḥen!
\m 
\v 25 Maca mmis ameqqran tuɣa deg iyyar. Ařami dd-yareggʷeḥ, idweř iqarreb-dd ɣar taddart, xenni isřa i ǧɣa d uɣennej n waṭṭas n iwdan.
\v 26 Iřaɣa i yijjen zeg imsexxaren imeẓyanen nnes, isseqsa t: ‘Man aya?’
\v 27 Wanita inna as: ‘Umac yusa-dd, babac iɣarṣ i uyenduz iṣeḥḥen, minzi iɛqeb-dd ɣares mliḥ!’
\v 28 Maca \add mmis ameqqran\add* ixeyyeq, war ixs ad yadef. Xenni iffeɣ babas ɣar barra, iḥeccem i-t.
\v 29 Maca netta yarra-dd, inna as i babas: ‘Aqa necc xedmeɣ ɣarek řexxu aṭṭas n iseggʷusa, ɛemmarṣ war jjiɣ zi tewṣeyyet nnec. \add Maca\add* cek war d ayi tewcid ɛemmarṣ uřa d ijj n iɣayḍ, ḥima ad farḥeɣ ak-d imeddukkař inu.
\v 30 Maca umi dd-yusa mmic wanita wenni iccen agřa nnec ak-d temɣarin n farq-ccɣeř, tɣarṣed as i uyenduz iṣeḥḥen!’
\v 31 Inna as babas: ‘A mmi, tuɣa cek akidi řebda, aqa marra min iǧan inu, aqa nnec.
\v 32 Aqa iɛeddeř i neccin ad nfarḥ ad nezhu, minzi umac wanita tuɣa immut, \add maca\add* iddar \add ɛawed\add*, tuɣa iweddar uca ittwaf!’”
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Amedya n wewkiř d aɛeffan
\m 
\v 1 Inna ɛawed i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Tuɣa din ijj n bnadem, aqa-t d bab n wagřa, ɣares ijj n wewkiř nni zi cetcan \add iwdan\add*, aqa zeɛma tuɣa ittzuzzar agřa n sides.
\v 2 Iřaɣa as, inna as: ‘Man aya i xak ttesřiɣ? Ewc řeḥsab i uwekkeř nnec, minzi war izemmar ad tiřid ɛad d awkiř!’
\v 3 Inna wewkiř ak-d ixef nnes: ‘Min ɣa ggeɣ umi sidi inu ad xafi ikkes awekkeř-a? War zemmareɣ i uqqaz n temmurt u ttseḍḥiɣ tutra!
\v 4 Aqa ssneɣ min ɣa ggeɣ ḥima, xmi ɣa ttwaḥuzeɣ x uwekkeř, ad ayi qebřen di tudrin nsen.’
\v 5 Uca iřaɣa-dd i kuř ijjen zeg aytbab n umarwas n sides. Inna as i umezwar: ‘Mecḥař d ac itturs sidi?’
\v 6 Yarra-dd xas netta: ‘Mya n ibidawen n zzect!’ Inna as: ‘Ksi řciɣed n umarwas nnec, qqim deɣya, tarid: Xemsin n ibidawen.’
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* inna i wenneɣni: ‘I cek, mecḥař d ac itturs sidi?’ Yarra-dd xas: ‘Mya n txuncay timeqqranin n yirden.’ Inna as: ‘Ksi řciɣed n umarwas nnec, tarid: Tmanyin.’
\v 8 Siditneɣ igga řfaǧ deg wewkiř iɣecc, aqa tuɣa ittegg s tiɣit, minzi tarwa n ddunect-a d imiɣisen di jjiř nsen wanita x tarwa n Tfawt.
\v 9 Ɛawed Necc ad awem iniɣ: ‘Ggem imeddukkař i yixef nwem s wagřa-ya n řɣecc, ḥima, xmi ɣa iqḍa, ad kenniw qebřen deg iqiḍan nsen n řebda.’” \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt Mt. 6:19; 19:21; 1 Tim. 6:19. \x*
\b
\s1 Tasexxart i AREBBI d tewkiřt n tenɛacin
\m 
\v 10 “Wenni iǧan d amtiqqi di drus, aqa-t d amtiqqi uřa deg waṭṭas, u wenni iɣeccen di drus, aqa iɣecc uřa deg waṭṭas.
\v 11 Mařa war teǧim d imtiqqan zi jjihet n wagřa n řɣecc, wi kenniw i ɣa iwekkřen x min iǧan nican?
\v 12 Mařa war teǧim d imtiqqan di min iǧan n wenneɣni, wi d awem i ɣa iwcin min iǧan nwem?
\m 
\v 13 Uřa d ijj n umsexxar war izemmar ad ixdem tnayen n isiditen, minzi niɣ ad icarh ijjen uca ad issɛizz wenneɣni, niɣ ad icebbar deg ijjen uca ad isseḥqar wenneɣni. War tzemmarem ad tsexxarem i AREBBI d wagřa. \x ◘ \xo 16:13 \xt Mt. 6:24. \x*
\b
\s1 Ccariɛa n Sidi Arebbi war ttbeṭṭiř ca
\m 
\v 14 Řami sřin Ifarisiyyen marra man aya, sseḥqaren t, minzi nitni tuɣa ttexsen tmenyat. \x ◘ \xo 16:14 \xt [Mt. 11:12-13] — Mt. 23:14. \x*
\v 15 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Kenniw d inni isseggden ixef nwem zzat i iwdan, maca AREBBI yargeb x wuřawen nwem, minzi min yuɛřan ɣar iwdan, aqa-t d nnɛi zzat i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:7; Izhd. 7:10. \x*
\v 16 Ccariɛa d Inabiyyen aqa aten ař Yuḥanna. Zi řweqt nni ittwabarreḥ s Tgeldit n AREBBI uca marra idsen ttemsedḥasen ɣares ḥima ad din adfen. \x ◘ \xo 16:16 \xt Mt. 11:12, 13. \x*
\v 17 Maca tikkest n ujenna d temmurt tehwen x uweṭṭu n ict n tneqqiṭ zi Ccariɛa.” \x ◘ \xo 16:17 \xt Izhd. 102:27; Ica. 40:8; 51:6; Mt. 5:18. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Marra wi ɣa iǧfen i temɣart nnes uca ad imřec ak-d tenneɣnit, aqa izna, u marra wi ɣa imeřcen tamɣart tenni umi iǧfen, aqa netta izna.” \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt Mt. 5:32; 19:9; Mk. 10:11; 1 Kur. 7:10. \x*
\b
\s1 Bab n wagřa d umeẓřuḍ Aliɛazar
\m 
\v 19 “Tuɣa din ijj n bnadem, aqa-t d bab n wagřa, yarḍ řeqṭen acemřař azdad d \add řeḥrir d\add* azeggʷaɣ. Ittɣebba zzhu kuř ass.
\v 20 Tuɣa din ɛawed ijj n umezřuḍ qqaren as Aliɛazar. Tuɣa ssbuẓẓřen t ɣar tewwart n bab n wagřa, iccur s řḥebb.
\v 21 Tuɣa dayes meẓri ad ijjiwen s iřeqqwaz i dd-iweṭṭan zi ṭṭabřa n bab n wagřa. Ttasen-dd yiṭan ɛawed, řessḥen ibuɛrusen nnes.
\v 22 Immut umezřuḍ, ksint t lmalakat ɣar weḥsin n Ibrahim. Uřa d bab n wagřa immut, neḍřen t.
\m 
\v 23 Am tuɣa ittɛeddab di řaxart, issgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnes, iẓra Ibrahim zi řaggʷaj u Aliɛazar tuɣa-t deg weḥsin nnes.
\v 24 Iřaɣa s jjehd: ‘\add A\add* baba Ibrahim, arḥem ayi. Sekk-dd Aliɛazar ḥima ad issuff ixef n uḍaḍ nnes s waman uca ad issesmeḍ iřes inu, minzi aqa ttɛeddabeɣ di tmessi-ya.’
\m 
\v 25 Inna as Ibrahim: ‘A mmi, ɛqeř aqa tkemmřed marra řxar nnec di tudart nnec, uca ammu i ikemmeř Aliɛazar řɣar. Řexxu netta ittᵉttwafewwej u cek tᵉttwaɛeddabed. \x ◘ \xo 16:25 \xt Ayub 21:13. \x*
\v 26 Sennej i man aya marra, aqa jar aneɣ neccin d kenniw ijj n ttasiɛ imɣar, ařami inni ixsen ad ɣarwem dd-ẓwan ssa, war zemmaren uca uřa d inni din iǧan war zemmaren ad ɣarneɣ dd-ẓwan ssenni.’
\v 27 Inna as: ‘Ttzawgeɣ cek xenni, a baba, ad t tessekked ɣar taddart n baba,
\v 28 minzi ɣari xemsa n aytma. Ejj i-t ad asen iɛřem, ḥima war dd-ttisen uřa d nitni ɣar wemcan-a n uɛeddeb.’
\v 29 Inna as Ibrahim: ‘Aqa ɣarsen Musa d inabiyyen. Ejj i-ten ad ɣarsen sřen!’ \x ◘ \xo 16:29 \xt Ica. 8:20; 34:16; Yḥ. 5:39; Řex. 17:11. \x*
\v 30 Maca netta inna as: ‘Lla, \add a\add* baba Ibrahim, mařa iruḥ ɣarsen ijjen zeg imettinen, xenni ad tuben!’
\v 31 Inna as Ibrahim: ‘Mařa nitni war sřin ɣar Musa d inabiyyen, xenni war zzayes ttwassqenɛen ɛawed, \add ɛad\add* xmi dd ɣa ikkar ijjen jar imettinen!’”
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 X uɣekkwi ɣar ddenb u x smaḥet
\m 
\v 1 Inna Yasuɛ i imeḥḍaren nnes: “War tɛeddeř ila ad iřint tɛenkrifin, maca uct x wenni zi i dd ɣa yasent! \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt [Mt. 18:6-7; 21-22; Mk. 9:42] — Mt. 18:7; Mk. 9:42. \x*
\v 2 Iḥřa as ad xas tᵉttwagg ict n teṣḍart n tsirt tedqeř ɣar yiri nnes uca ad immenḍar di řebḥar x minni ɣa issenqarḍ ijjen zeg imeẓyanen-a.
\v 3 Ḥḍam ixef nwem. Mařa ixḍa umac, webbex i-t, u mařa itub, samḥ as. \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt Lawi 19:17; Awřn. 17:10; Mt. 18:15; Yaɛ. 5:19. \x*
\v 4 Mařa ixḍa akidek sebɛa n twařawin deg ijj n wass uca idweř-dd ɣarek sebɛa n twařawin, iqqar: ‘Aqa tubeɣ!’, ittxeṣṣa ad as tsamḥed.” \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Mt. 18:21. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n tḥebbuct n zzariɛet n uxerdel
\m 
\v 5 Nnan rrusul: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, arni aneɣ l’iman nneɣ!”
\v 6 Netta inna asen: “Mři tuɣa daywem l’iman am yict n tḥebbuct n zzariɛet n uxerdel uca ad tinim i tcejjart-a n tut: ‘Twaqřeɛ zeg iẓewran nnem, twaẓẓu di řebḥar!’, xenni ad awem tᵉṭṭaɛ.” \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Mt. 17:20; 21:21; Mk. 11:23. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n bab d umsexxar nnes
\m 
\v 7 Man wen zzaywem i ɣar iǧa umsexxar icarrez niɣ yarekkwes uǧi, ad as yini deɣya mařa iɛqeb-dd zeg iyyar uca yudef \add ɣar taddart\add*: ‘Qarreb-dd, teqqimed \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add*’?
\v 8 Ma war d as iqqar: ‘Sewjed min ɣa mmunesweɣ, tbeysed, tsexxared xafi ař ɣa cceɣ, sweɣ. Awarni man aya ad tecced, ad teswed uřa d cek’?
\v 9 Ma ad iksi umsexxar nni aqadi, minzi netta igga min d as ittwannan ad t yegg? Ittɣiř ayi, lla!
\v 10 Ammu uřa d kenniw, xmi teggim marra min d awem yumuren, \add ittxeṣṣa\add* ad tinim: ‘Aqa neccin d imsexxaren war ineffɛen, minzi negga min tuɣa xaneɣ’.”
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ɛecra i di iǧa řbarṣ
\m 
\v 11 Rami iruḥ Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim icuq di řwesṭ \add n temmurt\add* n Isamariyyen, tenni iǧan zzat n Ljalil.
\v 12 Ařami tuɣa ittadef ɣar ijj n dcar, řqan t ɛecra n yeryazen daysen řbarṣ, qqimen bedden ɣar řaggʷaj.
\v 13 Ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen, nnan: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, Yasuɛ, arḥem aneɣ!’”
\v 14 Umi daysen ixzar, inna asen: “Ruḥem, secnem ixef nwem i ikehhanen!” Xenni imsar, am gguren nitni, aqa ttwassizedgen. \x ◘ \xo 17:14 \xt Lawi 13:2; 14:2; Mt. 8:4; Lk. 5:14. \x*
\m 
\v 15 Ijjen zzaysen iɛqeb, umi iẓra belli iggenfa, uca issemɣara di AREBBI s tmijja tejhed.
\v 16 Iwḍa x uɣembub nnes ɣar iḍaren n Yasuɛ, iqada t. Wa tuɣa d ijj n \add weryaz\add* Asamiri.
\v 17 Iṭṭef Yasuɛ deg wawař, inna: “Ma war ttwassizedgen marra s ɛecra? Mani qqimen tesɛa?
\v 18 Mayemmi jjin nitni ad dd-asen ḥima ad ssɛuǧen AREBBI, mɣir wanita waha, wenni iǧan zeg ijj n řgens d abarrani?” \x ◘ \xo 17:18 \xt Lk. 4:25-27\x*
\v 19 Xenni inna as: “Kkar, truḥed, aqa l’iman nnec issenjem i cek!”
\b
\s1 Tawasit n Tgeldit n Arebbi
\m 
\v 20 Umi Ifarisiyyen sseqsan Yasuɛ: “Meřmi i dd ɣa tas Tgeldit n AREBBI?”, yarra-dd xasen, inna: “War dd-tᵉttis Tgeldit n AREBBI s yijj n wudem ittwasscanen. \x ◘ \xo 17:20 \xt [Mt. 24:23-28; 37-41] \x*
\v 21 War qqaren: ‘Aqa-tt da!’, niɣ: ‘Aqa-tt diha!’, minzi Tageldit n AREBBI aqa-tt di \add ca\add* zzaywem.” \x ◘ \xo 17:21 \xt Mt. 24:23; Mk. 13:21; Lk. 21:7, 8. \x*
\v 22 Inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Ad dd-awḍen wussan i di i ɣa texsem ad tẓarem ijj n wass waha zeg wussan n Mmis n bnadem, \add maca\add* kenniw war \add t\add* tẓarrem.
\v 23 Mařa nnan awem: ‘Aqa-t da!’ niɣ: ‘Aqa-t diha!’, war din ttriḥem. \x ◘ \xo 17:23 \xt Mt. 24:23; Mk. 13:21. \x*
\v 24 Minzi am mammec iccat wassam zi ṭṭarf sadu ujenna ɣar ṭṭarf nneɣni sadu ujenna, ammu ɛawed ad yiři Mmis n bnadem deg wass nnes.
\v 25 Maca ittxeṣṣa as amezwaru ad iweddeb aṭṭas uca ad ittwammenḍar zi jjiř-a! \x ◘ \xo 17:25 \xt Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:18; Mk. 8:31; 9:31; 10:33; Lk. 9:22; 18:31; 24:6, 7\x*
\m 
\v 26 Am mammec tuɣa deg wussan n Nuḥ, ammu i ɣa yiři \add ɛawed\add* deg wussan n Mmis n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 17:26 \xt Amz. 6:2; 7:7; Mt. 24:37,38; 1 Bṭ. 3:20. \x*
\v 27 Tuɣa ttᵉtten, sessen, ttawyen timɣarin, smeǧacen \add timɣarin\add* i yeryazen ař ass i di yudef Nuḥ ɣar uɣarrabu uca yusa-dd ṭṭufan, isshellek i-ten marra.
\v 28 Ammu tuɣa imsar ɛawed deg wussan n Lut. Tuɣa ttᵉtten, sessen, ssaɣen, zznuzan, tteẓẓun, bennan.
\v 29 Maca deg wass i di dd-iffeɣ Lut zi Sadum, ijja SIDI ad dd-tewḍa tmessi d řecbareyyet zeg ujenna, iteḥḥa ten marra. \x ◘ \xo 17:29 \xt Amz. 19:24; Aɛwd. 29:22; Ica. 13:19; Irm. 50:40; Ḥuc. 11:8; Ɛam. 4:11; Yah. 7. \x*
\m 
\v 30 Ammu i ɣa yiři deg wass i di i ɣa ittwassargeb Mmis n bnadem.
\v 31 Wenni iǧan x tzeqqa deg wass nni u řqecc nnes aqa-t di taddart, war dd-ihekkwi ca maḥend ad t iksi. Ammu uřa d wenni iǧan deg iyyar, war dd-ittɛiqib ca.
\v 32 Ɛeqřem x temɣart n Lut! \x ◘ \xo 17:32 \xt Amz. 19:15-17, 26. \x*
\v 33 Wenni yarezzun ad issenjem tudart nnes, ad tt ixsar, u wenni tt i ɣa ixsaren, ad tt issenjem. \x ◘ \xo 17:33 \xt Mt. 10:39; 16:25; Mk. 8:35; Lk. 9:24; Yḥ. 12:25. \x*
\v 34 Ad awem iniɣ, aqa di ǧiřet nni ad din iřin tnayen x ict n tassut: ijjen ad ittwaksi, wenneɣni ad ittwajj. \x ◘ \xo 17:34 \xt Mt. 24:40,41; 1 Ts. 4:17. \x*
\v 35 Ad din iřint tnayen n temɣarin ḥarryent jmiɛ, ict ad tᵉttwaksi, tenneɣni ad tᵉttwajj.
\v 36 Ad din iřin tnayen deg iyyar: ijjen ad ittwaksi, wenneɣni ad ittwajj.”
\m 
\v 37 Arrin-d, nnan as: “Mani, a Siditneɣ?” Netta inna asen: “Mani teǧa arrimet din ittmunan ɛawed igidaren.” \x ◘ \xo 17:37 \xt Ayub 39:30; Mt. 24:28. \x*
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Amedya n tajjač d řqaḍi
\m 
\v 1 Inna asen ɛawed ijj n umedya belli aqa ittxeṣṣa asen ad ẓẓaǧen di kuř řweqt břa amelli. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt Rum. 12:12; Afa. 6:18; Kul. 4:2; 1 Ts. 5:17. \x*
\m 
\v 2 “Tuɣa deg ict n tendint ijj n řqaḍi war itteggʷed ca AREBBI, war ittweqqar bnadem.
\v 3 Ict n tajjač di tendint nni tusa-dd ɣares, tenna as: ‘Ewc ayi tasɣart inu x weɣrim inu!’
\v 4 Aṭṭas i ikka tuɣa yugi. Xenni inna deg ixef nnes: ‘Necc zeɛma war tteggʷedeɣ ca AREBBI u war ttweqqireɣ bnadem,
\v 5 qaɛ ammu, minzi tajjač-a thekkweř ayi \add břa qeṭṭu\add*, ad as wceɣ tasɣart nnes, ḥima war dd-tᵉttɛiqqib řebda uca ad ayi tarẓ azeǧif.’”
\m 
\v 6 Siditneɣ inna: “Sřem min iqqar řqaḍi aɣeccac!
\v 7 Ma war ittic AREBBI tasɣart ktar aṭṭas i yinni zzayes ittwafarzen, inni ɣares dd-isɣuyyun ass d ǧiřet? Ma war ittegg Netta \add ktar aṭṭas\add* s ttasiɛ n řxaḍar xasen? \x ◘ \xo 18:7 \xt Asa. 6:10. \x*
\v 8 Ad awem iniɣ, aqa ad asen iwc tasɣart deɣya. Maca xmi dd ɣa iɛqeb Mmis n bnadem, ma ad yaf l’iman di temmurt?”
\b
\s1 Amedya n Ufarisi d ijj n bu-ḍḍariba
\m 
\v 9 Inna amedya-ya i iwdan nni ɣar teǧa ttiqqet deg yixef nsen aqa aten d imseggaden u sseḥqaran inneɣni marra.
\v 10 “Gaɛɛden tnayen n iwdan ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, ḥima ad ẓẓaǧen, ijjen d Afarisi u wenneɣni d ijj n bu-ḍḍariba.
\v 11 Ibedd Ufarisi, ittẓaǧa ak-d yixef nnes: ‘\add A\add* AREBBI, ttqadiɣ Cek umi war ǧiɣ ca am iwdan nneɣni: iɣeccacen d yinni iḥeṣṣaren d yinni izennan, uřa am bu-ḍḍariba wanita. \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt Ica. 1:15; 58:2; Asa. 3:17, 18. \x*
\v 12 Necc ttẓummiɣ tnayen n imuren di ssimana, tticeɣ řeɛcur zi marra min ɣari iǧan d agřa.’
\v 13 Maca bu-ḍḍariba wenni ibedden ɣar řaggʷaj, war izɛim uřa ad issiři tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar ujenna, maca iwta ixef nnes ɣar idmaren, inna: ‘\add A\add* AREBBI, arḥem ayi, aqa necc d amednub!’
\v 14 Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa wanita ad yiři ittwasegged s waṭṭas x Ufarisi nni umi dd-ihwa ɣar taddart nnes. Minzi marra wenni i ɣa issuɛřan ixef nnes ad ittwasswaḍeɛ, u wenni i ɣa isswaḍɛen ixef nnes ad ittwassuɛřa.” \x ◘ \xo 18:14 \xt Ayub 22:29; Awřn. 29:23; Mt. 23:12; Lk. 14:11; Yaɛ. 4:6, 10; 1 Bṭ. 5:5. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d iḥenjiren
\m 
\v 15 Iwyen as-dd iḥenjiren imeẓyanen ḥima ad ten isřuf. Umi ten ẓrin imeḥḍaren, webbxen ten. \x ◘ \xo 18:15 \xt [Mt. 19:13-15; Mk. 10:13-16] — Mt. 19:13; Mk. 10:13. \x*
\v 16 Maca Yasuɛ iřaɣa xasen, inna asen: “Jjem iḥenjiren ad ɣari dd-asen, war ten ttᵉṭṭfem, minzi Tageldit n ijenwan i yinni am yina. \x ◘ \xo 18:16 \xt Mt. 18:3; 19:14; 1 Kur. 14:20; 1 Bṭ. 2:2. \x*
\v 17 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Wenni war iqbiřen Tageldit n AREBBI am uḥenjir war tt ittidef ɛemmarṣ!”
\b
\s1 Aseqsi n ijj n bab n wagřa i Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 18 Isseqsa t ijj n umeqqran, inna as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar Aṣebḥan, min ɣa ggeɣ, ḥima ad warteɣ Tudart ittduman?” \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt [Mt. 19:16-30; Mk. 10:17-31] — Mt. 19:16; Mk. 10:17. \x*
\v 19 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Mayemmi d ayi třaɣid s ‘Aṣebḥan’? Uřa d ijj war iǧi d aṣebḥan mɣir ijjen, aqa-t d AREBBI.
\v 20 Cek tessned tiweṣṣa: War zenni, war neqq, war tticar, war cehhed s ẓur, weqqar babac d yemmac!” \x ◘ \xo 18:20 \xt Uf. 20:12-16; Aɛwd. 5:17-20; Rum. 13:9; Afa. 6:2; Kul. 3:20. \x*
\v 21 Inna as: “Aqa marra tina ḥḍiɣ tent zi temẓi inu.”
\v 22 Umi isřa Yasuɛ aya, inna as: “Ict teqqim ac. Uyur, zenz marra min ɣarek, farq i-t x imezřaḍ uca ad ɣarek yiři řkenz deg ijenwan, \add xenni\add* ḍfar ayi-dd.” \x ◘ \xo 18:22 \xt Mt. 6:19; 19:21; 1 Tim. 6:19. \x*
\m 
\v 23 Umi isřa man aya, icḍen minzi tuɣa-t d bab n wagřa ameqqran.
\v 24 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ belli netta icḍen, inna: “Mammec yewɛar x aytbab n wagřa maḥend ad dd-adfen ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 18:24 \xt Awřn. 11:28; Mt. 19:23; Mk. 10:23. \x*
\v 25 Minzi adaf n weřɣem zi tiṭṭ n tsineft ihwen x wadaf n bab n wagřa ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI.”
\v 26 Inni tuɣa ittesřan aya, nnan: “Wi izemmaren \add xenni\add* ad ittwassenjem?”
\v 27 Yasuɛ inna: “Min war izemmaren ad yiři ɣar iwdan, ɣar AREBBI izemmar ad yiři.” \x ◘ \xo 18:27 \xt Ayub 42:2; Irm. 32:17; Zak. 8:6; Lk. 1:37. \x*
\b
\s1 Řmunet n weḍfar n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 28 Inna asen Buṭrus: “Aqa neccin nejja kuřci uca neḍfar i Cek.” \x ◘ \xo 18:28 \xt Mt. 4:20; 19:27; Mk. 10:28; Lk. 5:11. \x*
\v 29 Yasuɛ inna as: “S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, war din uřa d ijj i ittejjin taddart niɣ lwalidin niɣ tawmat, niɣ tamɣart niɣ tarrawt di ṭṭweɛ n Tgeldit n AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 18:29 \xt Aɛwd. 33:9. \x*
\v 30 i war iksin aḍeffus x uḍeffus n tseqqar di řweqt-a, uca di zzman i dd ɣa yasen \add ad iksi\add* Tudart ittduman.” \x ◘ \xo 18:30 \xt Ayub 42:12. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes i twařa wiss třata
\m 
\v 31 Yasuɛ iksi tenɛac \add n rrusul\add* nnes ɣares, inna asen: “Ad ngeɛɛed ɣar Urcalim uca marra min yuran s ufus n inabiyyen x Mmis n bnadem ad ittwaqfeř. \x ◘ \xo 18:31 \xt [Mt. 20:17-19; Mk. 10:32-34] — Izhd. 22:7; Ica. 53:7; Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:17; Mk. 8:31; 9:31; 10:32; Lk. 9:22; 24:7. \x*
\v 32 Minzi Netta ad ittwasellem i řegnus, uca ad zzayes stehzan, ad xas ssusfen x uɣembub nnes, \x ◘ \xo 18:32 \xt Mt. 27:2; Lk. 23:1; Yḥ. 18:28; Řex. 3:13. \x*
\v 33 ad t hettken s urekkuḍ, ad t sseḥqaren, ad t nɣen uca deg wass wiss třata ad dd-ikkar.”
\v 34 Nitni war fhimen walu zi man aya. Tuɣa awař-a iwɛar xasen, u nitni war fhimen min d asen ittwannan.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n udarɣař
\m 
\v 35 Ařami dd-qarrben ɣar Ariḥa tuɣa ijj n udarɣař iqqim deg webrid, ittᵉttar. \x ◘ \xo 18:35 \xt [Mt. 20:29-34; Mk. 10:46-52] — Mt. 20:29; Mk. 10:46. \x*
\v 36 Řami isřa i řḥess n řɣaci iɛdu, isseqsa: “Man aya?”
\v 37 Nnan as: “Yeccu Nnaṣiri iɛeddu.”
\v 38 Iřaɣa, inna: “\add A\add* Yasuɛ, \add a\add* Mmis n Dawud, arḥem ayi!”
\v 39 Inni tuɣa igguren ɣar zzat n Yasuɛ, webbxen t maḥend ad isqar, maca netta ibda ittřaɣa s jjehd ktar: “\add A\add* Mmis n Dawud, arḥem ayi!”
\v 40 Ibedd Yasuɛ uca yumur ad t-i-dd-awyen ɣares. Umi dd ɣares iqarreb, isseqsa t,
\v 41 inna as: “Min texsed ad ac t ggeɣ?” Inna: “\add A\add* Sidi, xseɣ ad dewřeɣ ttwařiɣ!”
\v 42 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Twařa, aqa l’iman nnec issgenfa cek.”
\v 43 Řexdenni ittwařa uca iḍfar i-t, issemɣara di AREBBI. Marra iwdan i iẓrin man aya, ssɛuǧen AREBBI.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Yasuɛ d Zakkayu
\m 
\v 1 Umi yudef Yasuɛ ɣar Ariḥa, icuq \add tendint nni\add*,
\v 2 tuɣa din ijj n weryaz qqaren as Zakkayu. Wanita tuɣa d bab n wagřa uřa d ameqqran n ayt n ḍḍariba.
\v 3 Netta tuɣa yarezzu ad iẓar Yasuɛ d min iɛna, \add maca\add* war izemmar s ssibbet n řɣaci, minzi tuɣa Zakkayu d aquḍaḍ n tiddi.
\v 4 \add S uyenni\add* izwar i Yasuɛ uca igeɛɛed x ijj n wartu n řexřa, ḥima ad t iẓar, minzi tuɣa Netta igga ad dd-yekk ssenni.
\v 5 Umi dd-yusa Yasuɛ ɣar wemcan nni, ixzar ɣar ujenna, ibarq i-t. Inna as: “\add A\add* Zakkayu, qeǧeq-dd, hwa-dd deɣya, minzi ass-a ittxeṣṣa ayi ad qqimeɣ di taddart nnec!”
\m 
\v 6 Iqeǧeq-dd, ihwa-dd deɣya uca yareḥḥeb zzayes s řefraḥet.
\v 7 Marra inni iẓrin man aya, bdan ttmeɛmiɛen xas, nnan: “Aqa yudef ɣar ijj n weryaz d amednub, ḥima ad ɣares iqqim!”
\v 8 Ikkar Zakkayu, inna i Yasuɛ: “Xzar, Sidi, ad wceɣ azyen n wagřa inu i imezřaḍ u marra wenni zi kkseɣ ca n řḥajjet s řɣecc, ad \add as t\add* arreɣ arebɛa n tseqqar!”
\v 9 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Ass-a tiweḍ-dd Tudart i taddart-a, minzi uřa d wa d ijj n mmis n Ibrahim. \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt Lk. 13:16. \x*
\v 10 Minzi Mmis n bnadem yusa-dd ḥima ad yarzu u ad issenjem min iweddaren.” \x ◘ \xo 19:10 \xt Mt. 10:6; 15:24; 18:11; Řex. 13:46. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n ɛecra n řwuznat
\m 
\v 11 Umi tuɣa ttesřan aya, yarni-dd ɛawed ijj n umedya, minzi ittɣiř asen, umi tuɣa dd-iqarreb ɣar Urcalim, aqa Tageldit n AREBBI ad dd-teḍhar deɣya. \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt [Mt. 25:14-30]\x*
\v 12 Inna: “Ijj n bnadem zi řejwad iruḥ ɣar ict n temmurt tiggʷej, ḥima ad iṭṭef tagelda i yixef nnes, uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-idweř \add awarni man aya\add*. \x ◘ \xo 19:12 \xt Mt. 25:14; Mk. 13:34. \x*
\v 13 Iřaɣa-dd i ɛecra n imsexxaren nnes uca iwca asen ɛecra n řminat uca inna asen: ‘Ggem ttijara ař dd ɣa ɛeqbeɣ’.
\v 14 Maca imezdaɣ n tendint tuɣa carrhen t uca ssekken awarni as ireqqasen, nnan: ‘War nexs wanita ad yiři d ajeǧid xaneɣ!’
\m 
\v 15 Umi dd-iɛqeb awarni řami d iksi tagelda, yumur maḥend ad řaɣan i imsexxaren nni umi iwca nnuqart, ḥima ad issen arbeḥ i dd-yiwi kuř ijjen di tsebbabt nnes.
\v 16 Yusa-dd umezwar, inna: ‘\add A\add* sidi, řmina nnec tiwi-dd ɛecra řminat’.
\v 17 Inna as: ‘Mliḥ cek, \add a\add* amsexxar aṣebḥan, minzi tuɣa cek d amtiqqi x drus, ad tiřid d azeǧif x ɛecra n tneddam.’
\v 18 Yusa-dd wenni wiss tnayen, inna: ‘\add A\add* sidi, řmina nnec tiwi-dd xemsa řminat.’
\v 19 Inna i wanita ɛawed: ‘Uřa d cek ad tiřid d azeǧif x xemsa n tneddam!’
\m 
\v 20 Xenni yusa-dd wenneɣni, inna: ‘A sidi, xzar řmina nnec i tuɣa xemmřeɣ deg \add ijj n zzif n\add* řeqṭen.
\v 21 Minzi ggʷedeɣ zzayek, minzi cek d ijj n bnadem tqesḥed. Cek tkessid min war tessrusid u tmejjared min war tzarɛed!’
\v 22 Inna as: ‘S uqemmum nnec ad xak carrɛeɣ, \add a\add* amsexxar aɛeffan! Tessned belli necc d bnadem iqseḥ, kessiɣ min war ssrusiɣ, mejjareɣ min war zarɛeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 19:22 \xt 2 Ṣm. 1:16; Mt. 12:37. \x*
\v 23 Mayemmi war tessarsed \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqart inu di řbanku? Xenni xmi dd ɣa yaseɣ, ad tent ksiɣ s lfayda.’
\v 24 Inna i yinni din ibedden akides: ‘Ksim xas řmina nnes, wcem tt i wenni ɣar iǧa ɛecra n řminat.’”
\m 
\v 25 Nnan as: ‘\add A\add* Siditneɣ, aqa ɣares ɛecra n řminat \add ɛad\add*?”
\v 26 “Netta inna asen: ‘Ad awem iniɣ, belli marra wenni ɣar iǧa, ad as immewc, maca wenni war ɣar iǧi, ad as ittwakkes ɛad uřa d min ɣares. \x ◘ \xo 19:26 \xt Mt. 13:12; 25:29; Mk. 4:25; Lk. 8:18. \x*
\v 27 Maca řɛedyan inu inni war ixsen ad xasen dewřeɣ d ajeǧid, awyem ten-dd danita uca ɣarṣem asen zzati.’”
\b
\s1 Adaf n Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim
\m 
\v 28 Awarni řami inna Yasuɛ man aya, izwar asen uca igeɛɛed ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 19:28 \xt [Mt. 21:1-11; Mk. 11:1-11; Yḥ. 12:12-19]\x*
\v 29 Ařami dd-iqarreb ɣar Bayt-Faji d Bayt-Ɛanya ɣar uɣezdis n wedrar umi qqaren ‘Taddart n Zzitun’, issekk tnayen n imeḥḍaren nnes, \x ◘ \xo 19:29 \xt Mt. 21:1; Mk. 11:1. \x*
\v 30 inna asen: “Ruḥem ɣar dcar i iǧan ɣar zzat nwem. Xzar, xmi din i ɣa tadfem, ad tafem ijj n wesnus iqqen, war xas inyi uřa d ijj n bnadem ɛad. Fesyem as uca awyem t-i-dd \add da\add*.
\v 31 Mařa isseqsa kenniw ca n ijjen: ‘Mayemmi d as tfesyem?’, ad as tinim ammu: ‘Aqa Siditneɣ iḥwaj i-t!’”
\m 
\v 32 Inni dd-ittwassekken ruḥen uca ufin \add t\add* am mammec d asen inna.
\v 33 Ařami d fesyen i wesnus, sseqsan ten aytbab nnes: “Mayemmi tfessyem i wesnus?”
\v 34 Nnan asen: “Aqa Siditneɣ iḥwaj i-t!”
\v 35 Usin-dd zzayes ɣar Yasuɛ, nḍaren arruḍ nsen x wesnus, ssenyen Yasuɛ xas. \x ◘ \xo 19:35 \xt Yḥ. 12:14. \x*
\v 36 Am tuɣa iggur, ssun nitni abrid s warruḍ nsen.
\v 37 Umi dd-iqarreb ɣar teysart \add n wedrar\add* n ‘Taddart n Zzitun’, ibda řɣaci n imeḥḍaren marra ad farḥen, ttsebbaḥen AREBBI s ict n tmijja tejhed aṭṭas x ssibbet n lmuɛjizat timeqqranin nni tuɣa ẓrin.
\v 38 Nitni nnan:
\b
\m \qt “Lbaraka i Ujeǧid i dd-yusin\qt*
\m \qt s Yisem n SIDI!\qt*
\m \qt Řehna deg ujenna\qt*
\m \qt d uɛuǧi di řuɛřa x řuɛřa qaɛ!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:38 \xt Izhd. 118:26; Lk. 2:14; Afa. 2:14. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 39 Maca ca n Ifarisiyyen jar řɣaci nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, webbex imeḥḍaren nnec!”
\v 40 Inna asen: “Ad awem iniɣ, mařa sqaren ina, xenni ad řaɣan yeẓra.” \x ◘ \xo 19:40 \xt Ḥab. 2:11. \x*
\v 41 Ařami dd-iqarreb uca iẓra tandint, iru xas,
\v 42 inna: “Mři tfehmed min d am dd ɣa yawyen řehna nnem, ɛad deg wass-a nnem! Maca řexxu aqa man aya inuffar x tiṭṭawin nnem.
\v 43 Aqa ad ɣarem dd-asen wussan i d am dd ɣa quwwaren řɛedyan nnem u ad cem ḥṣaren zi marra iɣezdisen.
\v 44 Ad cem areddǧen, cem d tarwa nnem akidem, war dayem ttejjin aẓru ibedd x weẓru nneɣni, minzi war teftined i řweqt n warzef \add n Arebbi\add* ɣarem.” \x ◘ \xo 19:44 \xt 1 Ij. 9:7, 8; Mixa 3:12; Mt. 24:1, 2; Mk. 13:2; Lk. 21:6. \x*
\b
\s1 Asizdeg n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 45 Umi yudef ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, ibda issuffuɣ inni i tuɣa issaɣen u izznuzan dayes. \x ◘ \xo 19:45 \xt [Mt. 21:12-17; Mk. 11:15-19; Yḥ. 2:13-22]\x*
\v 46 Inna asen: “Aqa tura: ‘Taddart inu d Taddart n tẓaǧit!’, maca kenniw tarrim tt d ijj n ifri n iceffaren!” \x ◘ \xo 19:46 \xt 1 Ij. 8:29; Ica. 56:7; Irm. 7:11; Mt. 21:13; Mk. 11:17. \x*
\v 47 Tuɣa isseřmad marra ussan di Zzawect Tameqqrant, maca imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen d imɣaren n řgens tuɣa arezzun ḥima ad t nɣen. \x ◘ \xo 19:47 \xt Mk. 11:18; Yḥ. 7:19; 8:37. \x*
\v 48 \add Maca\add* war ufin min xas ɣa ggen, minzi marra iwdan tuɣa řeṣqen dayes, ttesřan ɣares.
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Aseqsi x man ttesriḥ i zi ittegg Yasuɛ řeɛjayeb nnes
\m 
\v 1 Deg ijj zeg wussan nni, am tuɣa netta isseřmad řgens di Zzawect Tameqqrant, ittbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan, \add xenni\add* ɣewwɣen xas imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen ak-d imɣaren \add n řgens\add*. \x ◘ \xo 20:1 \xt [Mt. 21:23-27; Mk. 11:27-33] — Mt. 21:23; Mk. 11:27; Řex. 4:7; 7:27. \x*
\v 2 Ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Ini aneɣ, s man ttesriḥ i tᵉttegged aya, niɣ man wen i d ac iwcin ttesriḥ-a?”
\v 3 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Uřa d Necc ad kenniw sseqsiɣ ijj n useqsi. Inim ayi:
\v 4 Ma aseɣḍeṣ n Yuḥanna zeg ujenna niɣ zeg iwdan?”
\v 5 Mcawaren jar asen, nnan: “Mařa nenna: ‘Zeg ujenna!’, ad yini: ‘Mayemmi xenni war zzayes tuminem?’
\v 6 Mařa nenna: ‘Zeg iwdan!’, ad aneɣ yarjem marra řgens, minzi nitni ttwassqenɛen belli Yuḥanna d anabi.”
\v 7 Nnan as: “Neccin war nessin zi manis!”
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna asen Yasuɛ: “Xenni uřa d Necc war d awem qqareɣ s man ttesriḥ i tteggeɣ aya!”
\b
\s1 Amedya n umarjuɛ n uḍiř d ixemmasen iɛeffanen
\m 
\v 9 Ibda ittɛawad i řgens amedya-ya: “Ijj n bnadem igga ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř, iẓẓu dayes tizayarin, icra amarjeɛ i ixemmasen, uca isafar ijj n řmijař n řweqt d azirar. \x ◘ \xo 20:9 \xt [Mt. 21:33-46; Mk. 12:1-12] — Izhd. 80:9; Ica. 5:1; Irm. 2:21; 12:10; Mt. 21:33; Mk. 12:1. \x*
\v 10 Ařami dd-yiweḍ řḥař, issekk ijj n umsexxar ɣar ixemmasen ḥima ad as wcen zeg uḍiř n umarjeɛ. Wtin t ixemmasen \add nni\add* uca ssekken t-i-dd ixwa.
\v 11 Xenni issekk ɛawed ijj n umsexxar nneɣni, wtin t ɛawed, deǧen t, xenni sekken t-i-dd ixwa.
\v 12 Issekk ɛawed \add amsexxar\add* wiss třata, maca nitni ssyezmen t ɛawed uca nḍaren t ɣar barra.
\m 
\v 13 Inna bab n umarjeɛ n uḍiř: ‘Min ɣa ggeɣ? Ad ssekkeɣ mmi iɛizzen. Xmi t ɣa ẓaren, ad t weqqaren nican.’
\v 14 Umi t ẓrin ixemmasen, mcawaren jar asen, nnan: ‘Aqa d wa d awrit. Zid ad t nneɣ, ḥima ad ɣarneɣ dd-idweř řwart.’ \x ◘ \xo 20:14 \xt Amz. 37:17; Izhd. 2:1, 8; Mt. 26:3; 27:1; Yḥ. 11:53; Ɛbr. 1:2. \x*
\v 15 Mmenḍaren t barra i umarjeɛ n uḍiř uca nɣin t. Min zzaysen i ɣa yegg xenni bab n umarjeɛ n uḍiř?
\v 16 Ad dd-yas, ad ineɣ ixemmasen nni, uca ad iwc amarjeɛ n uḍiř i inneɣni.” Umi sřin aya, nnan as: “Ɛemmarṣ!”
\v 17 Maca Netta ixzar ɣarsen, inna: “Min ixs ad yini xenni \add wawař-a\add* i yuran:
\b
\m \qt ‘Aẓru i tuɣa iɛiffen ibennayen,\qt*
\m \qt aqa idweř d \tl aẓru n\tl* Uzeǧif n teɣmart!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 20:17 \xt Izhd. 118:22; Ica. 8:14; 28:16; Mt. 21:42; Mk. 12:10; Řex. 4:11; Rum. 9:33; 1 Bṭ. 2:4, 7. \x*
\m 
\v 18 \qt Marra wi ɣa iwḍan x weẓru-ya,\qt*
\m \qt ad ifartek,\qt*
\m \qt u wenni xef i ɣa iwḍa,\qt*
\m \qt ad t iřbez’?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 20:18 \xt Ica. 8:15; Dan. 2:34; Zak. 12:3. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 19 Arezzun imseřmaden n idlisen d imeqqranen n ikehhanen ad xas ssarsen ifassen di tsaɛɛet nni, maca nitni ggʷeden zeg iwdan, minzi ssnen belli Netta inna amedya-ya xasen.
\b
\s1 Aseqsi x uxeǧeṣ n ḍḍariba i qayṣar
\m 
\v 20 Ḥḍan t uca ssekken ibergagen inni iggin ixef nsen amecnaw imseggaden, ḥima ad as ggen ijj n řfex di ssibbet n ijj n wawař, maḥend ad t sellmen i řqaḍi d jjehd n lɛamil. \x ◘ \xo 20:20 \xt [Mt. 22:15-22; Mk. 12:13-17] — Mt. 22:16; Mk. 12:13. \x*
\v 21 Sseqsan t, nnan: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, nessen belli Cek tessawařed u tesseřmaded nican, war tᵉttegged ca s wudmawen u tesseřmaded abrid n AREBBI s tidett.
\v 22 Ma iḥeǧeř aneɣ ad newc řeɛcur i kuř ijjen uzeǧif i qayṣar niɣ lla?”
\v 23 Yuca s teḥraymect nsen uca inna asen: “Mayemmi d ayi tᵉttjarrabem?
\v 24 Secnem ayi-dd dinar. Wi yiřan taṣwirt-a d tira-ya?” Nnan as: “N qayṣar!”
\v 25 \add Xas uca\add* inna asen Yasuɛ: “Wcem xenni i qayṣar min iǧan i qayṣar u i AREBBI min iǧan i AREBBI!” \x ◘ \xo 20:25 \xt Mt. 17:25; 22:21; Rum. 13:7. \x*
\v 26 War zemmaren ad t ṭṭfen s wawař nnes qibač i iwdan, \add maca\add* qqimen ttbehten s temwarrit nnes uca sseɣden.
\b
\s1 Aseqsi n Iṣaduqiyyen x tnukra
\m 
\v 27 Usin-dd ca zeg Iṣaduqiyyen inni iqqaren, war din bu tnukra \add zi řmewt\add*. Sseqsan t, \x ◘ \xo 20:27 \xt [Mt. 22:23-33; Mk. 12:18-27] — Mt. 22:23; Mk. 12:18; Řex. 23:8. \x*
\v 28 nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, yura aneɣ Musa, mařa immut i weryaz umas i ɣar iǧa tamɣart uca immut břa iḥenjiren, xenni ad yawi umas tamɣart nni, maḥend ad dd-yejj aḥenjir i umas. \x ◘ \xo 20:28 \xt Aɛwd. 25:5-6. \x*
\v 29 Tuɣa din sebɛa n wawmaten. Amezwar yiwi ict n temɣart, \add maca\add* immut břa iḥenjiren.
\v 30 Yiwi wenni d wiss tnayen tamɣart nni uca uřa d netta immut břa iḥenjiren.
\v 31 Xenni wenni d wiss třata yiwi tamɣart nni uca ammu inneɣni ař wiss sebɛa. Mmuten nitni \add marra idsen\add*, war dd-jjin ca iḥenjiren.
\v 32 Ɣar uneggar temmut temɣart ɛawed.
\v 33 Di tnukra i man wen zzaysen i ɣa tiři d tamɣart? Minzi marra sebɛa nni iwyen tt \add d tamɣart\add*!”
\m 
\v 34 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Ayt n ddunect-a iwyen timɣarin, u timɣarin ttwassmeǧacent i yeryazen.
\v 35 Maca inni ittwaḥesben sdaheǧen ad awḍen ɣar ddunect nni u ɣar tnukra zi taddart n imettinen, war ttiwyen timɣarin, u timɣarin war ttiřint i yeryazen.
\v 36 Maɣar war zemmaren ɛad ad mmten, minzi nitni am lmalakat u nitni d tarwa n AREBBI, minzi nitni dewřen d tarwa n tnukra. \x ◘ \xo 20:36 \xt 1 Yḥ. 3:2. \x*
\v 37 Maca zi jjihet n imettinen ad ttwassnekkaren, tuɣa issbeyyan Musa ɛawed umi iḥaja x cbarq ak-d isennanen, aqa SIDI inna: ‘\add NECC\add* d AREBBI n Ibrahim d AREBBI n Isḥaq d AREBBI n Yaɛqub.’ \x ◘ \xo 20:37 \xt Uf. 3:6; Řex. 7:32; Ɛbr. 11:16. \x*
\v 38 Netta war iǧi ca d AREBBI n imettinen, maca n yinni iddaren, minzi ɣares Netta nitni marra ddaren.”
\v 39 Arrin-dd ca zeg imseřmaden n idlisen, nnan: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, tessiwřed mliḥ aṭṭas!”
\v 40 Uca war zɛimen ɛad ad t sseqsan x ca.
\b
\s1 Man wen iǧan d mmis n Dawud?
\m 
\v 41 Inna asen: “Mammec zemmaren imseřmaden n idlisen ad inin belli Lmasiḥ d Mmis n Dawud? \x ◘ \xo 20:41 \xt [Mt. 22:41-46; Mk. 12:35-37] — Mt. 22:42; Mk. 12:35. \x*
\v 42 Dawud \add simant nnes\add* iqqar deg wedlis n Izehhiden:
\b
\m \qt ‘SIDI inna i Sidi inu:\qt*
\m \qt Qqim x ufusi inu,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 20:42 \xt Izhd. 110:1; Řex. 2:34; 1 Kur. 15:25; Ɛbr. 1:13; 10:13. \x*
\m 
\v 43 \qt ař d ɣa ssarseɣ řɛedyan nnec\qt*
\m \qt sadu iḍaren nnec.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 20:43 \xt Izhd. 110:1. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 44 Mařa Dawud isemma t ‘Sidi’, mammec ɣa yiři Netta d mmis?”
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d Imseřmaden n idlisen
\m 
\v 45 Am tuɣa marra iwdan \add zemmaren\add* ad sřen, inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: \x ◘ \xo 20:45 \xt [Mt. 23:1-36; Mk. 12:38-40; Lk. 11:37-54]\x*
\v 46 “Ḥḍam ixef nwem zeg imseřmaden n idlisen inni ittexsen ad uyuren s ijeǧaben iziraren, inni umi itteɛjib asen ad xasen seǧmen iwdan di řeswaq u ad qqimen x řekrasi iṣebḥen di temzidawin u x imucan imezwura ɣar imensiwen. \x ◘ \xo 20:46 \xt Mt. 23:5, 6; Mk. 12:38, 39; Lk. 11:43. \x*
\v 47 Nitni ttᵉtten tudrin n tijjař am ttᵉttaren tiwhibin di ṭṭweɛ n tẓaǧatin nsen tizirarin. Aqa ina ad ksin ijj n řḥukm iqseḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 20:47 \xt Mt. 23:14; Mk. 12:40; 2 Tim. 3:6; Tit. 1:11. \x*
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Ṣṣedqet n tajjač
\m 
\v 1 Xenni isweḍ Yasuɛ ɣar aytbab n wagřa ssrusan ṣṣdaqi nsen di ssenduq. \x ◘ \xo 21:1 \xt [Mk. 12:41-44] — 2 Ij. 12:10; Mk. 12:41. \x*
\v 2 Iẓra ɛawed ict n tajjač tamezřuḍt tessars dayes tnayen n \add uqiyyat, semman tent\add* ‘camunat’.
\v 3 Inna asen: “S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa tajjač-a řmeskina tenḍar \add dayes\add* ktar zzaysen marra. \x ◘ \xo 21:3 \xt 2 Kur. 8:12. \x*
\v 4 Minzi marra nitni nḍaren zi zziyada n wagřa nsen \add ict n ṣṣedqet\add* deg wexxam n ṣṣdaqi n AREBBI, maca nettat zi řexṣeṣ nnes aqa tenḍar dayes marra min ɣares.”
\b
\s1 Awař n Yasuɛ x řweqt aneggaru
\m 
\v 5 Ařami tuɣa ca \add n iwdan\add* ssawařen x Zzawect Tameqqrant, tenni tzewweq s iẓra iṣebḥen d ṣṣdaqi, inna asen Yasuɛ: \x ◘ \xo 21:5 \xt [Mt. 24:1-14; Mk. 13:1-13] — Mt. 24:1; Mk. 13:1. \x*
\v 6 “Ma tᵉttwařam timesřayin-a? Ad dd-asen wussan war ittɣimi uřa d ijj n weẓru x weẓru nneɣni i war ittareddǧen.” \x ◘ \xo 21:6 \xt 1 Ij. 9:7; Mixa 3:12; Lk. 19:44. \x*
\v 7 Sseqsan t, nnan: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, meřmi i ɣa yiři uya d man řeɛřamet aqa timesřayin-a udsent-i-dd?”
\v 8 Inna asen: “Ɛessem, war tᵉttwaɣarrem, minzi aṭṭas ad dd-asen s Yisem inu, ad inin: ‘Aqa Necc d Lmasiḥ!’ u: ‘Řweqt aqa tiweḍ-dd!’, maca war ggurem awarni asen. \x ◘ \xo 21:8 \xt Irm. 29:8; Mt. 24:4; Afa. 5:6; Kul. 2:18; 2 Ts. 2:2; 1 Yḥ. 4:1. \x*
\v 9 Mařa tesřim x řbaruḍ d iɣewwɣen, war ttnexřiɛem ca, minzi s uɣiř ad yiři uya d amezwar, maca war ittiři ɛad deɣya uneggar.
\m 
\v 10 Maɣar ijj n řgens ad dd-igeɛɛed ḍidd n ijj n řgens \add nneɣni\add* u ict n tgeldit ḍidd n ict n tgeldit \add nneɣnit\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:10 \xt Ica. 19:2. \x*
\v 11 Ad iřin inhezziyyen n temmurt mɣaren di ɛřam kuř imucan d řaẓ d jjrayeḥ d tiggʷudi d usnexřiɛ. Uca ad dd-banent řeɛřamat mɣarent zeg ujenna u ad din iřint tḥaryaḍin ijehden.
\v 12 Maca qbeř man aya marra ad xawem ssarsen ifassen, ad kenniw sellmen ɣar temzidawin d řeḥbusat, uca ad kenniw nedhen zzat i ijeǧiden d řḥukkam x ssibbet n Yisem inu. \x ◘ \xo 21:12 \xt Mt. 10:17; 24:9; Mk. 13:9; Yḥ. 16:2; Řex. 4:3; 5:18; 12:4; 16:24; Asa. 2:10. \x*
\v 13 Maca man aya ad yarra kenniw ad tcehdem. \x ◘ \xo 21:13 \xt Lk. 9:15; 21:13; 24:48\x*
\v 14 Ggem deg wuřawen nwem maḥend war \add tarezzum\add* ad třemdem mammec i dd ɣa tarrem. \x ◘ \xo 21:14 \xt Mt. 10:19; Mk. 13:11. \x*
\v 15 Minzi Necc ad awem wceɣ aqemmum d tiɣit i war zemmaren ad ten ssbedden marra řɛedyan nwem. \x ◘ \xo 21:15 \xt Uf. 4:12; Ica. 54:17; Mt. 10:19; Řex. 6:10. \x*
\v 16 Ad kenniw sellmem lwalidin nwem d tawmat nwem d řaǧ nwem d imeddukkař nwem uca ad nɣen ca zzaywem, \x ◘ \xo 21:16 \xt Mixa 7:6; Řex. 7:59; 12:2. \x*
\v 17 u kenniw ad tᵉttwacarhem zi marra s ssibbet n Yisem inu. \x ◘ \xo 21:17 \xt Mt. 10:22; Mk. 13:13. \x*
\v 18 \add Waxxa amenni\add* uřa d ijj n uẓeṭṭu \add n ucuwwaf\add* n uzeǧif nwem war ittweddari ca, \x ◘ \xo 21:18 \xt 1 Ṣm. 14:45; 2 Ṣm. 14:11; 1 Ij. 1:52; Mt. 10:30. \x*
\v 19 maca s ṣṣbar nwem ad tarebḥem řeɛmur nwem.”
\b
\s1 Areddeǧ n Urcalim
\m 
\v 20 “Xmi ɣa tẓarem Urcalim aqa inneḍ as-dd řɛeskar, xenni snem belli aqa iqarreb-dd wareddeǧ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:20 \xt [Mt. 24:15-21; 24:29-35; Mk. 13:14-19; 13:24-32] — Dan. 9:27; Zak. 14:1-3; Mt. 24:15-35; Mk. 13:14-31. \x*
\v 21 Xenni ittxeṣṣa ad arewřen inni iǧan di Yahudiyya ɣar idurar, ejj inni iǧan di řwesṭ nnes ad zzayes ffɣen, ad arewřen, d yinni iǧan di dcurat, war tt ttidfen,
\v 22 minzi ina d ussan n nneqmet ḥima ad ittwakemmeř marra min yurin. \f ◼ \fr 21:22 \fk ussan n nneqmet\ft - niɣ ‘ussan n weɛmud’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 21:22 \xt Dan. 9:26, 27; Mt. 24:15; Mk. 13:14. \x*
\v 23 Uct x temɣarin nni s ddeyset d tinni issuṭṭuḍen deg wussan nni, minzi ad din tiři řmeḥnet d tameqqrant x temmurt d weɣḍab x řgens-a.
\v 24 Nitni ad wḍan s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, ad ttwaḥebbsen am ttwanedhen jar marra řegnus, uca Urcalim ad xas ɛefsen řegnus ař ɣa kemmřent zzmanat n řegnus.” \x ◘ \xo 21:24 \xt Rum. 11:25. \x*
\b
\s1 Řeɛřamat deg ujenna i x temmurt
\m 
\v 25 “Ad din iřint řeɛřamat di tfuct, di tziri u deg itran, uca x temmurt \add ad din tiři\add* řmeḥnet di řegnus, ař d asen iweddar min ɣa ggen zeg unexřiɛ n zzhir ameqqran n řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 21:25 \xt Ica. 13:10; Ḥiz. 32:7; Yuw. 3:4; 3:15; Mt. 24:29; Mk. 13:24; Asa. 6:12. \x*
\v 26 u \add zeg\add* wenhezzi n temmurt d ameqqran ad issnexřiɛ řeɛmar n iwdan zi tiggʷudi zi min i dd ɣa yasen x temmurt, u ṣṣulaṭat n ijenwan ad ttwanhezzent.
\v 27 Řexdenni ad ẓaren Mmis n bnadem, xmi dd ɣa yas deg iseynuten, s jjehd d uɛuǧi aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 21:27 \xt Dan. 7:10; Mt. 16:27; 24:30; 25:31; 26:64; Mk. 13:26; 14:62; Řex. 1:11; 2 Ts. 1:10; Asa. 1:7. \x*
\v 28 Xmi ɣa bdant tmesřayin-a, ggem taryast, sgeɛɛdem izeǧifen nwem minzi asenjem nwem aqa yiweḍ-dd.” \x ◘ \xo 21:28 \xt Rum. 8:23. \x*
\b
\s1 Ḥḍam, ẓaǧem!
\m 
\v 29 Iɛawed asen ijj n umedya: “Xzarem ɣar wartu n tazart u ɣar marra ticejjura. \x ◘ \xo 21:29 \xt Mt. 24:32; Mk. 13:28. \x*
\v 30 Xmi ɣa ssneḍyent, ad tessnem s man aya aqa anebdu yiweḍ-dd.
\v 31 Ammu \add ittxeṣṣa\add* ɛawed kenniw, xmi ɣa tᵉttwařam timesřayin-a ttemsarant, snem \add xenni\add* belli Tageldit n AREBBI tudes-dd.
\v 32 S tidett ad awem iniɣ, aqa war iɛeddu jjiř-a ař ɣa yiři uya kuřci.
\v 33 Ajenna d temmurt ad ɛeddun, \add maca\add* awařen inu war ɛeddun ɛemmarṣ. \x ◘ \xo 21:33 \xt Izhd. 102:27; Ica. 51:6; Mt. 24:35; Ɛbr. 1:11. \x*
\m 
\v 34 Ḥḍam ixef nwem ḥima war tteḍqiřen wuřawen nwem zeg ufucceḥ d wescar d imunas n ddunect-a, u war xawem dd-iwḍi wass nni deɣya. \x ◘ \xo 21:34 \xt Rum. 13:13; 1 Ts. 5:6; 1 Bṭ. 4:7. \x*
\v 35 Minzi ad dd-yas \add ass nni\add* am řfex x marra inni iqqimen x uɣembub n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 21:35 \xt 1 Ts. 5:2; 2 Bṭ. 3:10; Asa. 3:3; 16:15. \x*
\v 36 Ḥḍam xenni řebda, ẓaǧem ḥima ad tiřim tesdaheǧem maḥend ad tnejmem zi marra min ɣa imsaren, uca ad tbeddem zzat i Mmis n bnadem.” \x ◘ \xo 21:36 \xt Mt. 24:42; 25:13; Mk. 13:33; Lk. 12:40; 1 Ts. 5:6. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 37 S uziř tuɣa isseřmad di Zzawect Tameqqrant, \add maca\add* s ǧiřet tuɣa itteffeɣ, ittɣima ittnusa x wedrar umi qqaren: ‘Taddart n Zzitun’. \x ◘ \xo 21:37 \xt Yḥ. 8:2. \x*
\v 38 Di ṣṣbeḥ zic tuɣa marra iwdan ttasen-dd ɣares di Zzawect Tameqqrant ḥima ad sřen Awař nnes.
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Řɣedran n Yahuda Isxariyuṭi
\m 
\v 1 Iqarreb-dd Řɛid n \add Weɣrum\add* břa Antun umi qqaren \add Řɛid n\add* \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 22:1 \xt [Mt. 26:1-5; 14-16; Mk. 14:1-2; 10-11; Yḥ. 11:45-53] — Uf. 12:15; Irm. 16:7 Mt. 26:2; Mk. 14:1. \x*
\v 2 Tuɣa imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen arezzun ict n tewwart, ḥima ad t nɣen, maca nitni ggʷeden zeg iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 22:2 \xt Izhd. 2:2; Yḥ. 11:47; Řex. 4:27. \x*
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* yudef cciṭan di Yahuda wenni umi qqaren Isxariyuṭi. Netta tuɣa d ijjen zi tenɛac \add n imeḥḍaren\add*. \x ◘ \xo 22:3 \xt Mt. 26:14; Mk. 14:10; Yḥ. 13:27. \x*
\v 4 Iruḥ, issiweř ak-d imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen d imgewwaden n iɛessasen n Zzawect Tameqqrant mammec t i ɣa isellem i nitni.
\v 5 Farḥen uca ttafqen ad as wcen \add tinɛacin n\add* nnuqart.
\v 6 Netta iwca asen awař uca yarzu ict n tewwart, ḥima ad asen t isellem barra i řɣaci.
\b
\s1 Asewjed n Umensi n Useɛdu
\m 
\v 7 Yiweḍ-dd wass n \add Weɣrum\add* břa Antun i di tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwaɣarṣ i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 22:7 \xt [Mt. 26:17-25; Mk. 14:12-21; Yḥ. 13:21-30] — Mt. 26:17; Mk. 14:12, 13. \x*
\v 8 Yasuɛ issekk-dd Buṭrus d Yuḥanna, inna \add asen\add*: “Ruḥem, tesswejdem aneɣ i \add umensi n\add* Useɛdu ḥima ad necc.”
\v 9 Nnan as: “Mani texsed ad nessewjed?”
\v 10 Inna asen: “Xzar, xmi ɣa tadfem ɣar tendint ad kenniw iřqa ijj n weryaz, yarbu ict n teqbuct n waman. Ḍfarem t!
\v 11 Inim i bab n taddart: ‘Amseřmad nneɣ isseqsa: Mani iǧa wexxam n inewjiwen i di i ɣa cceɣ \add umensi n\add* Useɛdu ak-d imeḥḍaren inu?’
\v 12 Netta ad awem isscen ict n tɣurfet tmiriwt sennej, yessu \add s ipayasen\add*. Swejdem din \add kuřci\add*!”
\v 13 Nitni ruḥen, ufin \add marra\add* am mammec tuɣa d asen inna uca sswejden i \add umensi n\add* Useɛdu.
\b
\s1 Amensi n Siditneɣ
\m 
\v 14 Umi dd-tiweḍ tsaɛɛet, yusa-dd Yasuɛ, iqqim \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* d tenɛac n rrusul akides. \x ◘ \xo 22:14 \xt [Mt. 26:26-30; Mk. 14:22-26; 1 Im. 11:23-25] — Mt. 26:20; Mk. 14:17. \x*
\v 15 Inna asen: “Necc tuɣa weḥḥceɣ aṭṭas ad cceɣ \add amensi-ya n\add* Useɛdu akidwem qbeř i ɣa weddbeɣ.
\v 16 Minzi ad awem iniɣ, aqa war zzayes ttᵉtteɣ \add ɛad\add* ař ɣa tᵉttwakemmeř di Tgeldit n AREBBI.”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef ijj n řkas uca iqada, inna: “Ksim wa, bḍam t jar awem!
\v 18 Minzi Necc ad awem iniɣ, war sesseɣ ca zi řɣiǧet n tzayart ař dd tusa Tgeldit n AREBBI.”
\v 19 Iksi aɣrum, iqada, yarẓa \add i-t\add* uca iwca asen t, inna: “Ta d Arrimet inu tenni xawem immewcen. Ggem aya i řidaret inu.” \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt Mt. 26:26; Mk. 14:22; 1 Kur. 11:24. \x*
\v 20 Ammu \add i inna\add* ɛawed x řkas awarni i umensi: “Řkas-a d Řɛahd n Jdid s Idammen inu inni i xawem i ɣa ittwassizzřen. \x ◘ \xo 22:20 \xt Irm. 31:31; Mt. 26:28, Mk. 14:24, Lk. 22:20, 1 Kur. 11:25, 2 Kur. 3:6, Ɛbr. 8:6, 8, 13; 9:15; 12:24\x*
\m 
\v 21 Maca aqa da, afus n wenni d ayi ɣa iɣdaren aqa-t akidi ɣar ṭṭabřa. \x ◘ \xo 22:21 \xt Mt. 26:23; Mk. 14:18; Yḥ. 13:21. \x*
\v 22 Mmis n bnadem ad iraḥ am mammec xas ittwakkes, maca uct x bnadem nni i t ɣa iɣdaren!” \x ◘ \xo 22:22 \xt Izhd. 41:10; Yḥ. 13:18; Řex. 1:6. \x*
\m 
\v 23 Bdan ttemsseqsan jar asen, man wen zzaysen i ɣa yegg man aya.
\m 
\v 24 Tuɣa jar asen ɛawed amcubbec x man wen zzaysen iǧan d ameqqran qaɛ.
\v 25 Xenni inna asen Yasuɛ: “Ijeǧiden n řegnus ṣellṭen xasen, u inni xasen iṣellṭen ttwařaɣan ‘tarwa n rejwad!’ \f ◼ \fr 22:25 \fk tarwa n řejwad\ft - niɣ ‘řmuḥsinin’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 22:25 \xt Mt. 20:25; Mk. 10:42. \x*
\v 26 Kenniw maca war tteggem ammu, maca ameqqran daywem ad yiři am umaẓuẓ, u amezwar \add ad yiři\add* am umsexxar. \x ◘ \xo 22:26 \xt Lk. 9:48; 1 Bṭ. 5:3. \x*
\v 27 Minzi man wen iǧan d ameqqran? Ma d wenni iqqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* niɣ d wenni ittsexxaren? Maca Necc di řwesṭ nwem am wenni ittsexxaren. \x ◘ \xo 22:27 \xt Mt. 20:28; Yḥ. 13:14; Fil. 2:7. \x*
\m 
\v 28 Aqa kenniw d inni akidi iqqimen deg ijarriben inu.
\v 29 Necc ad awem weɛdeɣ ict n Tageldit am mammec i d ayi tt iwaɛd Baba, \x ◘ \xo 22:29 \xt Lk. 12:32. \x*
\v 30 ḥima ad teccem ad teswem x ṭṭabřa inu di Tgeldit inu uca ad teqqimem x řekrasi n tgeldit, ad tḥekmem x tenɛac n tqebbař n ayt n Israil.” \x ◘ \xo 22:30 \xt Mt. 19:28; Asa. 3:21. \x*
\b
\s1 Qqimem tcebbarem di l’iman
\m 
\v 31 Inna Yasuɛ i Cimɛun: “Cimɛun, Cimɛun, aqa cciṭan tuɣa yarezzu ad kenniw izzuzar am yirden. \x ◘ \xo 22:31 \xt [Mt. 26:31-35; Mk. 14:27-31; Yḥ. 13:36-38] — 1 Bṭ. 5:8. \x*
\v 32 \add Maca\add* Necc ẓuǧeɣ xak ḥima war ifenni l’iman nnec. Uřa d cek, tub di řweqt ittwaggen, stebbet aytmac.”
\v 33 Inna as Cimɛun: “\add A\add* Sidi, necc aqa wejdeɣ ḥima ad kik raḥeɣ uřa ɣar řeḥbes d řmewt.”
\v 34 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna as: “Necc ad ac iniɣ, \add a\add* Cimɛun, war issququɛ uyaẓiḍ ass-a qbeř ma ad ayi tenkared třata n twařawin belli aqa tessned ayi.” \x ◘ \xo 22:34 \xt Mt. 26:34; Mk. 14:30; Yḥ. 13:38. \x*
\m 
\v 35 Inna asen: “Řami kenniw ssekkeɣ břa tacyart, břa ttesṭim niɣ sandaliyat, ma tuɣa ittxeṣṣa awem ca?” Nnan as: “Walu!” \x ◘ \xo 22:35 \xt Mt. 10:9; Mk. 6:8; Lk. 9:3. \x*
\v 36 \add Xas uca\add* inna asen: “Maca řexxu wenni ɣar iǧa tecyart, ad tt iksi, ammu uřa d ttesṭim, uca wenni war ɣar iǧi ssif, ad izzenz arruḍ nnes uca ad \add zzayes\add* iseɣ ssif i yixef nnes.
\v 37 Minzi Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa ittxeṣṣa ad ttwakemmřent tira-ya dayi: ‘Aqa ittwaḥseb ak-d inni war iseggden!’, minzi marra min xafi yuran, ad ittwakemmeř.” \x ◘ \xo 22:37 \xt Ica. 53:12; Mk. 15:28. \x*
\v 38 Nnan asen: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, aqa da tnayen n řesyuf!” Inna asen: “Ikfa!”
\b
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Yasuɛ x wedrar n Taddart n Zzitun
\m 
\v 39 Iffeɣ, iruḥ ɣar wedrar ‘Taddart n Zzitun’ am mammec tuɣa innum, uca ḍfaren t ɛawed imeḥḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:39 \xt [Mt. 26:36-46; Mk. 14:32-42] — Mt. 26:36; Mk. 14:32; Yḥ. 8:1; 18:1. \x*
\v 40 Umi ixecc ɣar wemcan nni, inna asen: “Ẓaǧem ḥima war dd-tᵉttidfem deg ujarreb.”
\v 41 Ifekk Ixef nnes zzaysen ɛřaḥař ticti n ijj n uḥejjar n weẓru, yuḍar x ifadden nnes, iẓẓuǧ,
\v 42 inna: “\add A\add* Baba, mařa texsed, ejj řkas-a ad xafi iɛdu. Maca war ittiři min xseɣ Necc maca min texsed Cek.” \x ◘ \xo 22:42 \xt Mt. 26:39; Mk. 14:35\x*
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* iḍhar as-dd ijj n lmalak zeg ujenna, iwca as jjehd.
\v 44 Tuɣa Netta iggwed aṭṭas, ittẓaǧa aṭṭas uca tidi nnes tuɣa tᵉttegg am tneqqiḍin n idammen weṭṭant ɣar temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 22:44 \xt Yḥ. 12:27; Ɛbr. 5:7. \x*
\v 45 \add Xenni\add* ikkar zi tẓaǧit, yusa-dd ɣar imeḥḍaren nnes uca yufa i-ten ṭṭṣen s wecḍan.
\v 46 Inna asen: “Mayemmi tᵉṭṭṣem? Kkarem, teẓẓaǧem ḥima war tᵉttidfem deg ujarreb.”
\b
\s1 Uḍuf n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 47 Am tuɣa ɛad issawař, xzar, aqa yusa-dd ijj n řɣaci ak-d wenni i d as qqaren Yahuda, wenni d ijjen zi tenɛac, uca netta tuɣa izwar asen, iqarreb-dd ɣar Yasuɛ, issudem i-t, maɣar aqa iwca asen ijj n wescan: “Wenni i ɣa ssudmeɣ, d wenni Netta!” \x ◘ \xo 22:47 \xt [Mt. 26:47-56; Mk. 14:43-50; Yḥ. 18:3-11] — Mt. 26:47; Mk. 14:43; Yḥ. 18:3. \x*
\v 48 Inna as Yasuɛ: “\add A\add* Yahuda, ma s usudem ad teɣdared Mmis n bnadem?”
\v 49 Umi ẓrin inni d as dd-innḍen min imsaren, nnan as: “A Siditneɣ, ma ad t newwet s řesyuf?”
\v 50 Ijjen zzaysen tuɣa iwta amsexxar n arrays n ikehhanen, iqess as amezzuɣ afusi. \x ◘ \xo 22:50 \xt Mt. 26:51; Mk. 14:47. \x*
\v 51 Iṭṭef Yasuɛ deg wawař, inna: “Ṣafi, baraka!” Xenni iḥada as amezzuɣ uca issgenfa i-t.
\m 
\v 52 Inna Yasuɛ i imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imgewwaden n iɛessasen n Zzawect Tameqqrant, inni tuɣa ɣares dd-yusin: “Ma teffɣem-dd ɣari axmi dd-teffɣem ɣar ijj n uxewwan, s řesyuf d iɛumad, maḥend ad ayi tᵉttfem? \x ◘ \xo 22:52 \xt Mt. 26:55; Mk. 14:48. \x*
\v 53 Ass x wass tuɣa ayi akidwem di Zzawect Tameqqrant, kenniw war ɣari tesswiẓẓḍem s ifassen, maca ta d tasaɛɛet nwem d ṣṣulṭa n taǧest.”
\b
\s1 Ankar n Buṭrus
\m 
\v 54 Ṭṭfen t, nedhen t uca ssidfen t di taddart n arrays n ikehhanen. Uca iḍfar i-t Cimɛun zi řaggʷaj. \x ◘ \xo 22:54 \xt [Mt. 26:57-58; 69-75; Mk. 14:53-54; 66-72; Yḥ. 18:12-18; 25-27] — Mt. 26:57; Mk. 14:53; Yḥ. 18:12, 24. \x*
\v 55 Nitni ssarɣen timessi di řwesṭ n řemraḥ, xenni qqimen deg wenneḍ nnes. Uca Cimɛun iqqim jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 22:55 \xt Mt. 26:69; Mk. 14:54, 66; Yḥ. 18:16, 25. \x*
\v 56 Teẓra i-t ict n tayya am iqqim ɣar tmessi uca texzar dayes mliḥ, tenna: “Uřa d wa tuɣa-t akides.”
\v 57 Maca netta inkar t, inna: “\add A\add* tamɣart, necc war t ssineɣ!”
\v 58 War din min iɛdun iẓra i-t wenneɣni, inna: “Uřa d cek d ijjen zzaysen.” Maca Buṭrus inna: “War iǧi bu d necc!”
\v 59 Umi teɛdu ɛřaḥař ict n tsaɛɛet, ibda wenneɣni ad iqaceḥ, inna: “S tidett, uřa d wa tuɣa-t akides, minzi uřa d netta d Ajalili.”
\v 60 Inna Buṭrus: “\add A\add* bnadem, necc war ssineɣ min xef tessawařed!” Řexdenni, am tuɣa ɛad issawař, issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ.
\v 61 Inneqřeb Yasuɛ uca ixzar ɣar Buṭrus. Uca iɛqeř Cimɛun x wawař i d as inna Siditneɣ: “Qbeř i ɣa issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ, ad ayi tenkared třata n twařawin!” \x ◘ \xo 22:61 \xt Mt. 26:34,75; Mk. 14:72; Yḥ. 13:38; 18:27. \x*
\v 62 Uca iffeɣ-dd Cimɛun barra, iru imeṭṭawen imerzagen.
\b
\s1 Aseḥqar n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 63 Iryazen nni iṭṭfen Yasuɛ, tuɣa sthezzan zzayes, \x ◘ \xo 22:63 \xt [Mt. 26:67-68; Mk. 14:65] — Ayub 16:10; Ica. 50:6; Mt. 26:67; Mk. 14:6; Yḥ. 19:3. \x*
\v 64 dřin \add tiṭṭawin nnes\add*, \add xenni\add* wtin t ɣar uɣembub, nnan: “Nabb, man wen i Cek iwtin?”
\v 65 S waṭṭas n tmesřayin nneɣni tuɣa ttceqqafen dayes, ssawařen ḍidd nnes.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ zzat i Jmaɛet Tameqqrant n Wudayen
\m 
\v 66 Umi dd-yiweḍ uziř, munen imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen uca nedhen t ɣar wexxam n Jmaɛet nsen. \x ◘ \xo 22:66 \xt [Mt. 26:59-66; Mk. 14:55-64; Yḥ. 18:19-24] — Izhd. 2:2; Mt. 27:1; Mk. 15:1; Yḥ. 18:28. \x*
\v 67 Nnan as: “Mařa Cek d Lmasiḥ, \add xenni\add* ini aneɣ t.” Inna asen: “Mařa nniɣ awem t, war dayi tᵉttimnem,
\v 68 u mařa sseqsiɣ kenniw, war xafi dd-tarrim niɣ war d ayi tarexxum.
\v 69 Zi řexxu d tsawent ad iqqim Mmis n bnadem x ufus afusi n jjehd n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 22:69 \xt Dan. 7:9; Mt. 16:27; 24:30; 25:31; 26:64; Mk. 14:62; Řex. 1:11; 1 Ts. 1:10; Asa. 1:7. \x*
\v 70 Nnan marra: “Ma Cek d Mmis n AREBBI?” Inna asen: “Kenniw \add s yixef nwem\add* teqqarem, aqa d Necc!”
\v 71 Nnan: “Umi neḥdaj ɛad řechud? Minzi aqa neccin \add s yixef nneɣ\add* nesřa t zeg uqemmum nnes.”
\b
\b
\c 23
\s1 Pilaṭus isseqsa Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 1 Marra tmesmunt nsen tekkar uca nitni nedhen t ɣar Pilaṭus. \x ◘ \xo 23:1 \xt [Mt. 27:1-2; 11-14; Mk. 15:1-5; Yḥ. 18:28-38] — Mt. 27:2; Mk. 15:1; Yḥ. 18:28. \x*
\v 2 Bdan ad t ḍeřmen, nnan: “Neccin nufa aqa Wa issefsed řgens nneɣ am imenneɛ ad wcen ḍḍariba i kuř azeǧif i qayṣar, iqqar belli Netta d Ajeǧid, Lmasiḥ!” \x ◘ \xo 23:2 \xt Mt. 17:25; 22:21; Mk. 12:17; Lk. 20:25; Řex. 17:7; Rum. 13:7. \x*
\v 3 Isseqsa t Pilaṭus, inna: “Ma Cek d Ajeǧid n Wudayen?” Yarra-dd, inna: “Cek i t iqqaren!” \x ◘ \xo 23:3 \xt Mt. 27:11; Mk. 15:2; Yḥ. 18:33. \x*
\m 
\v 4 Inna Pilaṭus i řɣaci u i imeqqranen n ikehhanen: “Aqa war ufiɣ bu uřa d ijj n řɛib di Bnadem-a!”
\v 5 \add Maca\add* sɣuyen nitni, nnan: “Netta issɣewwaɣ řgens, isseřmad di marra Yahudiyya, ibda zi Ljalil ař da.”
\v 6 Umi isřa Pilaṭus ‘Ljalil’, isseqsa: “Ma aryaz-a d Ajalili?”
\v 7 Umi ifhem belli Netta tuɣa sadu ufus n Hirudus, issekk i-t ɣar Hirudus, minzi wanita tuɣa-t di Urcalim deg wussan nni. \x ◘ \xo 23:7 \xt Lk. 3:1. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ zzat i Hirudus
\m 
\v 8 Ařami iẓra Hirudus Yasuɛ, ifarḥ aṭṭas, minzi aṭṭas zeg wami tuɣa ixs ad t iẓar, minzi isřa xas aṭṭas n tmesřayin, u tuɣa issitim ad zzayes iẓar ca n řeɛřamet. \x ◘ \xo 23:8 \xt Lk. 9:7. \x*
\v 9 Isseqsa t x waṭṭas n tmesřayin, maca Yasuɛ war xas dd-yarri s ca.
\v 10 Imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen kkaren, ḍeřmen t s řḥarret.
\v 11 Hirudus ak-d řɛeskar nnes sseḥqaren t, u awarni řami istehza zzayes, yarḍ as ijj n useřham adehmani, uca issekk i-t ɣar Pilaṭus.
\v 12 Dewřen Pilaṭus d Hirudus d imeddukkař deg wass nni, minzi qbeř tuɣa din řeɛdawet jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 23:12 \xt Řex. 4:27. \x*
\b
\s1 Řḥukm x Yasuɛ s řmewt
\m 
\v 13 \add Xas uca\add* iřaɣa Pilaṭus x imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imeqqranen n řgens, inna asen: \x ◘ \xo 23:13 \xt [Mt. 27:15-26; Mk. 15:6-15; Yḥ. 18:39-40; 19:1-16] — Mt. 27:23; Mk. 15:14; Yḥ. 18:38; 19:4. \x*
\v 14 “Kenniw tiwyem ayi-dd bnadem-a am yijjen wenni issɛiǧen řgens nwem. Xzar, necc sseqsiɣ t zzatwem, war ufiɣ uřa d ijj n řɛib deg weryaz-a zi jjihet marra i zzayes tᵉttcetcam xas kenniw.
\v 15 Uřa d Hirudus \add war dayes yufi ca\add*, minzi necc ssekkeɣ t ɣares. U xzar, war din uřa d ict n řḥajjet i igga tesdaheǧ řmewt.
\v 16 Necc ad t hettkeɣ s urekkuḍ uca ad as arxuɣ.”
\v 17 Maɣar tuɣa din ict n tnamit maḥend ad asen yarxu i yijjen di Řɛid. \x ◘ \xo 23:17 \xt Mt. 27:15; Mk. 15:6; Yḥ. 18:39. \x*
\v 18 Maca marra řɣaci isɣuy deg ijj n umur, inna: “Kksem Wa, arxu aneɣ-dd i Bar-Abbas!” \x ◘ \xo 23:18 \xt Řex. 3:14. \x*
\v 19 Wa tuɣa ittwammenḍar di řeḥbes x ssibbet n ijj n uɣuwweɣ i imsaren di tendint u \add x ssibbet n\add* wenɣay.
\v 20 Issiweř Pilaṭus ɛawed akidsen, minzi tuɣa ixs ad yarxu i Yasuɛ.
\v 21 Maca sɣuyen nitni, nnan: “Ṣellb i-t! Ṣellb i-t!”
\v 22 Inna asen i twařa wiss třata: “Man tuɛeffna igga Wa \add xenni\add*? Necc war dayes ufiɣ bu uxeṭṭu i \add isdaheǧen\add* řmewt? S uyenni awarni řami t hettkeɣ s urekkuḍ, ad as arxuɣ!”
\v 23 Maca nitni ziyyaren xas s tmijjawin jjehdent, ttaren \add maḥend\add* ad t ṣellben. Timijjawin nsen d tenni n imeqqranen n ikehhanen tuɣa arennyent di jjehd.
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* iḥkem Pilaṭus ad asen iqḍa cɣeř nsen. \x ◘ \xo 23:24 \xt Mt. 27:26; Mk. 15:15; Yḥ. 19:16. \x*
\v 25 Iḍřeq asen i wenni immenḍaren di řeḥbes zi ssibbet n uɣuwweɣ d wenɣay, d wenni ttaren nitni, maca isellem Yasuɛ \add i nitni\add* x řeḥsab řxaḍar nsen.
\b
\s1 Abrid ɣar ṣṣalib
\m 
\v 26 Umi t gewwden ssenni, ṭṭfen Cimɛun zi Qayrawan, tuɣa yusa-dd zi řkampu, uca ssarsen xas ṣṣalib ḥima ad \add t\add* yarbu awarni Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 23:26 \xt [Mt. 27:32-44; Mk. 15:21-32; Yḥ. 19:17-19]\x*
\v 27 Iḍfar i-t-i-dd ijj n řɣaci n iwdan d temɣarin nni tuɣa iwtin agejdur, ttrunt xas.
\v 28 Inneqřeb-dd ɣarsent Yasuɛ, inna: “\add A\add* yessis n Urcalim, war ttrunt ca xafi, maca runt x ixef nkent d tarwa nkent.
\v 29 Minzi ad dd-asen wussan i di i ɣa inin: ‘Sseɛd n temɣarin i war izemmaren ad urwent u \add sseɛd n\add* iɛeddisen nni war yurwen, d tibbac tinni war issuṭṭuḍen!’
\v 30 Xenni ad inin i idurar: ‘Wḍam-dd xaneɣ!’, u i tiwririn: ‘Dřent aneɣ!’ \x ◘ \xo 23:30 \xt Ica. 2:19; Ḥuc. 10:8; Asa. 6:16; 9:6. \x*
\v 31 Minzi mařa ggin aya s ukeccuḍ aziza, min ɣa imsaren xenni i \add ukeccuḍ\add* yuẓɣen?” \x ◘ \xo 23:31 \xt Irm. 25:29; 1 Bṭ. 4:17. \x*
\v 32 Nedhen akides ɛawed tnayen nneɣni inni tuɣa iqeṭṭɛen abrid, ḥima ad ten nɣen \add akides\add*. \x ◘ \xo 23:32 \xt Yḥ. 19:18. \x*
\m 
\v 33 Řami iwḍen ɣar wemcan umi qqaren ‘Taceqquft’, ṣellben t din ak-d yinni tuɣa iqeṭṭɛen abrid, ijjen x yefus nnes u wenneɣni x uzeřmaḍ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 23:33 \xt Mt. 27:33,38; Mk. 15:22; Yḥ. 19:18. \x*
\v 34 Maca Yasuɛ inna: “\add A\add* Baba, ɣfar asen, minzi nitni war ssinen min tteggen!” Uca bḍan arruḍ nnes, nḍaren xas akeccuḍ. \x ◘ \xo 23:34 \xt Izhd. 22:19; Mt. 27:35; Mk. 15:24; Yḥ. 19:23; Řex. 7:60; 1 Kur. 4:12. \x*
\v 35 Tuɣa iwdan bedden din, xezzaren. Uřa d imeqqranen \add n řgens\add* sthezzan zzayes, nnan: “Tuɣa issenjem inneɣni, řexxu ejj i-t ad issenjem Ixef nnes mařa Netta d Lmasiḥ, d Wenni ittwafarzen zi AREBBI?”
\v 36 Uřa d iɛeskariyyen stehzan zzayes am ɣares dd-qarrben uca wcin as řxeǧ.
\v 37 Nnan as: “Mařa Cek d Ajeǧid n Wudayen, \add xenni\add* senjem Ixef nnec!”
\v 38 Tuɣa din ɛawed ict n tira sennej nnes, urin tt \add s lḥuruf\add* n Tyunanit d Tlatinit d Tɛibranit: ‘Wa d Ajeǧid n Wudayen.’ \x ◘ \xo 23:38 \xt Mt. 27:37; Mk. 15:26; Yḥ. 19:19. \x*
\m 
\v 39 Ijjen zeg iqṭaṭɛiyyen i yuyřen akides, tuɣa ittceqqaf dayes, iqqar: “Mařa Cek d Lmasiḥ, senjem Ixef nnec uřa d neccin!”
\v 40 Maca wenneɣni iwebbex i-t, inna: “Ma cek war teggʷided ca ɛad zi AREBBI umi cek iřqef ccreɛ d ijjen?
\v 41 Neccin s řḥeqq minzi neṭṭef axeǧeṣ n min negga. Maca Wa war iggi min war iḥřin!”
\v 42 \add Xas uca\add* inna i Yasuɛ: “Ɛqeř xafi, \add a\add* Sidi inu, xmi dd ɣa tased di Tgeldit nnec.”
\v 43 Inna as Yasuɛ: “S tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ, aqa ass-a ad tiřid akidi di jjennet.”
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 44 Tuɣa tasaɛɛet ɛřaḥař d setta, \add aqa-tt d ḍḍhur\add*, xenni tewḍa-dd taǧest x temmurt marra ařami d tesɛa, \add aqa-tt d třata n uɛecci\add*. \f ◼ \fr 23:44 \fk setta\ft - ixs ad yini ‘tuɣa d azyen n wass’. \fk tesɛa\ft - ixs ad yini ‘tasaɛɛet tuɣa-tt d třata n wezyen n wass’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 23:44 \xt [Mt. 27:45-56; Mk. 15:33-41; Yḥ. 19:28-30] — Mt. 27:45; Mk. 15:33. \x*
\v 45 \add Xenni\add* tebbarcen tfuct uca ařeḥḥaf n wadaf ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant ittwacarreg deg wezyen. \x ◘ \xo 23:45 \xt Mt. 27:51; Mk. 15:38. \x*
\v 46 Yasuɛ iřaɣa s jjehd, inna: “\add A\add* Baba, deg ifassen nnec ad ssarseɣ Arruḥ inu.” Umi inna aya, isellem Ixef nnes \add ɣares\add*. \x ◘ \xo 23:46 \xt Izhd. 31:6; Mt. 27:50; Mk. 15:37; Yḥ. 19:30; Řex. 7:59. \x*
\v 47 Umi iẓra řqebṭan x mya min tuɣa imsaren, ibda issemɣara di AREBBI, inna: “S tidett tuɣa Bnadem-a d amseggad!” \x ◘ \xo 23:47 \xt Mt. 27:54; Mk. 15:39. \x*
\m 
\v 48 Umi marra řɣaci i d imunen ḥima ad ẓaren afurrej-a, ẓrin min imsaren, ɛeqben am wtin deg idmaren nsen.
\v 49 Marra inni issnen Yasuɛ d temɣarin i kides dd-yusin zi Ljalil, bedden ɣar řaggʷaj, ẓrin \add marra\add* aya.
\b
\s1 Anḍeř n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 50 Ijj n weryaz, qqaren as Yusuf, tuɣa-t d amcawar di Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*. Netta zi Ramta, ict n tendint di Yahuda, aqa-t d ijj n weryaz d aṣebḥan d amseggad. \f ◼ \fr 23:50 \fq ’Jmaɛet \bdit Tameqqrant\bdit*\ft - niɣ: ‘Jmaɛet n řḥukkam imeqqranen n Wudayen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 23:50 \xt [Mt. 27:57-61; Mk. 15:42-47; Yḥ. 19:38-42] — Mt. 27:57; Mk. 15:43; Yḥ. 19:38. \x*
\v 51 Netta war yarḍi ca x ccwar nsen u x min ggin, u netta tuɣa ittraja Tageldit n AREBBI.
\v 52 Wanita yuyur ɣar Pilaṭus uca ittar \add as\add* arrimet n Yasuɛ.
\v 53 Issehwa tt-i-dd \add zi ṣṣalib\add*, inneḍ i-tt deg ict n txeyyaḍt n řeqṭen \add azdad\add* uca issars i-tt deg wenḍeř i iɣza di sseǧaḥ mani war inḍiř ḥed ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 23:53 \xt Mt. 12:40; 26:12; 27:59; Mk. 15:46. \x*
\v 54 Tuɣa d ass n Usewjed, aqa ssebt tqarreb-dd.
\m 
\v 55 Timɣarin i kides dd-yusin zi Ljalil, qarrbent-i-dd, ẓrint anḍeř d mammec ssarsen arrimet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 23:55 \xt Lk. 8:2. \x*
\v 56 \add Xas uca\add* ɛeqbent, ssewjdent řeɛṭur d zzect ittfuḥen, \add maca\add* di ssebt areyyḥent am mammec teǧa di tewṣeyyet. \x ◘ \xo 23:56 \xt Mk. 15:47\x*
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Tanukra
\m 
\v 1 Deg \add wass\add* amezwar \add n ssimana\add* ɣar ṣṣbeḥ, řami tuɣa ɛad d taǧest, ruḥent ɣar wenḍeř, ksint řeɛṭur i tuɣa ssewjdent, u tuɣa din \add ɛad\add* timɣarin nneɣni akidsent. \x ◘ \xo 24:1 \xt [Mt. 28:1-10; Mk. 16:1-8; Yḥ. 20:1-10] — Mt. 28:1; Mk. 16:1; Yḥ. 20:1. \x*
\v 2 Aqa ufint, taṣḍart i tuɣa x wenḍeř, tᵉttwasseqnuni zzayes.
\v 3 Udfent, \add maca\add* war ufint ca arrimet n Yasuɛ.
\m 
\v 4 Am tbehtent di man aya, xzar, aqa din tnayen n yeryazen deg warruḍ ittissiqen, bedden sennej nsent.
\v 5 Nitenti ggʷedent aṭṭas uca qbařent azeǧif nsent ɣar temmurt. Nitni \add maca\add* nnan asent: “Mayemmi tarezzunt x Wenni iddaren jar imettinen?
\v 6 Aqa war da iǧi, minzi aqa ikkar! Ɛeqřent x min d akent inna umi t tuɣa ɛad di Ljalil, \x ◘ \xo 24:6 \xt Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:18; Mk. 8:31; 9:31; 10:33; Lk. 9:22; 18:31. \x*
\v 7 inna: ‘Aqa tura belli Mmis n bnadem ad immewc deg ifassen n imednab, ad ittwaṣelleb uca deg wass wiss třata ad dd-ikkar.’”
\m 
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ɛeqřent x wawařen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt Yḥ. 2:22. \x*
\v 9 Ɛeqbent-i-dd zeg wenḍeř uca xebbarent marra man aya i ḥiṭac u i inneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 24:9 \xt Mt. 28:8; Mk. 16:10. \x*
\v 10 Ina tuɣa d Maryam n Majdala d Yuḥanna d Maryam, yemmas n Yaɛqub, d min tuɣa iqqimen \add n temɣarin\add* i iǧan akidsent, ḥajant nitenti man aya i rrusul.
\v 11 Nitni ḥesben awařen-a d aṭemmes uca war tent ttiqqen.
\m 
\v 12 Maca Cimɛun ikkar-dd, yuzzeř deɣya ɣar wenḍeř, ixezzar daxeř, iẓra taxeyyaḍt n řeqṭen \add azdad\add* tᵉttwamars ɣar uɣezdis. \add Xenni\add* iruḥ, ittebhet deg yixef nnes s min imsaren. \x ◘ \xo 24:12 \xt Yḥ. 20:3, 6. \x*
\b
\s1 Deg webrid ɣar Ɛimwas
\m 
\v 13 U xzar, deg wass nni tuɣa tnayen zzaysen deg webrid ɣar ijj n dcar qqaren as Ɛimwas, iggʷej settin ‘istadiyyen’ x Urcalim, \add ɛřaḥař ḥiṭac kilumitr\add*. \x ◘ \xo 24:13 \xt [Mk. 16:12-13] — Mk. 16:12. \x*
\v 14 Tuɣa ssawařen ak-d wayawya x marra min tuɣa imsaren.
\m 
\v 15 Am ssawařen nitni, ttemsawaḍen, iqarreb-dd ɣarsen Yasuɛ, yuyur akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 24:15 \xt Mt. 18:20; Lk. 24:36. \x*
\v 16 Ttwacebbarent tiṭṭawin nsen ařami war t ɛqiřen.
\v 17 Inna asen: “Man awařen-a i xef tessawařem ak-d wayawya deg webrid, am teggurem u ttbanent řxeẓrat nwem ceḍnent?”
\v 18 Ijjen zzaysen umi qqaren Kliyupas, inna as: “Ma Cek d ayenni n ubarrani di Urcalim i war issinen min din imsaren deg wussan-a?”
\v 19 Inna asen: “Min imsaren?” Nnan as: “Min imsaren i Yasuɛ zi Nnaṣira, tuɣa-t d anabi, tuɣa ɣares jjehd di min ittegg u di min issawař qibač i AREBBI d marra řgens. \x ◘ \xo 24:19 \xt Lk. 7:16; Yḥ. 4:19; 6:14. \x*
\v 20 Sellmen t imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* i řḥukm s řmewt uca ṣellben t.
\v 21 Neccin tuɣa nessitim, aqa d Netta i ɣa isellken Israil, maca xzar, ass-a \add ɛdun ɛad\add* třata n wussan zeg wami imsar man aya marra. \x ◘ \xo 24:21 \xt Řex. 1:6. \x*
\v 22 Maca ca n temɣarin zzayneɣ ssḥeyyarent aneɣ ɛawed, maɣar nitenti ruḥent zic ɣar wenḍeř. \x ◘ \xo 24:22 \xt Mt. 28:8; Mk. 16:10; Yḥ. 20:18. \x*
\v 23 Řami war din ufint arrimet nnes, usint-i-dd, nnant: “Aqa neẓra din lmalakat, u \add lmalakat\add* nnant xas: ‘Aqa iddar!’”
\v 24 Ca zeg inni akidneɣ iǧan, ruḥen ɣar wenḍeř, ufin timesřayin am mammec xas nnant ɛawed temɣarin, maca Netta war t ẓrin ca.”
\m 
\v 25 Inna asen: “Mecḥař d ifɣař d ineḍqař n wuř i teǧam maḥend ad tamnem di marra min ssiwřen inabiyyen!
\v 26 Ma war ittxeṣṣi ad iweddeb Lmasiḥ ḥima ad yadef ɣar uɛuǧi nnes?” \x ◘ \xo 24:26 \xt Ica. 50:6; 53:5; Fil. 2:7; Ɛbr. 12:2; 1 Bṭ. 1:11. \x*
\v 27 Xenni ibda zi Musa u zi marra inabiyyen, ittfessar asen x Yixef nnes zi marra Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 24:27 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:15; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 7:14; 9:5; 40:10; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:25; Dan. 9:24; Mixa 7:20. \x*
\m 
\v 28 \add Umi\add* dd-qarrben ɣar dcar i ɣar tuɣa gguren, igga Netta axmi tuɣa ixs ad yarni deg webrid ɣar ijj n wemcan iggʷejen.
\v 29 \add Maca\add* nitni ggin xas bezzez, nnan: “Qqim akidneɣ, minzi tameddit ad tewḍa, aqa imeyyeř uziř.” Uca yudef, iqqim akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 24:29 \xt Amz. 19:3; Řex. 16:15; Ɛbr. 13:2. \x*
\v 30 Imsar ařami tuɣa akidsen iqqim \add ɣar umensi\add* iksi aɣrum, ibarek \add i-t\add*, yarẓa \add i-t\add*, xenni iwca asen \add t\add*.
\v 31 Deɣya nnurzment tiṭṭawin nsen, ɛeqřen t. \add Xas uca\add* ittwammeksi zzaysen.
\m 
\v 32 Nnan ijjen i wenneɣni: “Ma war tuɣi ideqqeř wuř nneɣ ařami tuɣa akidneɣ issawař deg webrid, issefham aneɣ Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*?”
\v 33 Di tsaɛɛet nni kkaren nitni, ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim, uca ufin ḥiṭac \add n rrusul\add* munen, nitni d yinni akidsen.
\v 34 Uca nitni nnan: “D tidett, aqa ikkar-dd Siditneɣ, iban-dd i Cimɛun.”
\v 35 Uřa d nitni xebbaren ɛawed s min imsaren deg webrid u mammec t ɛeqřen ařami yarẓa aɣrum.
\b
\s1 Aḍhar n Yasuɛ i imeḥḍaren nnes
\m 
\v 36 Am tuɣa ssawařen nitni x man aya, ibedd Yasuɛ simant nnes di řwesṭ nsen, inna asen: “Sřam xawem, aqa d NECC, war tteggʷedem ca!” \x ◘ \xo 24:36 \xt [Mt. 28:16-20; Mk. 16:14-18; Yḥ. 20:19-23; Uf. 1:6-8] — Mk. 16:14; Yḥ. 20:19; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*
\v 37 \add Maca\add* nitni nnxeřɛen uca ggʷeden aṭṭas, ittɣiř asen belli ttwařan ijj n řexyař.
\v 38 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Mayemmi tᵉttnexřiɛem, mayemmi tᵉtteggem ixarriṣen deg wuřawen nwem?
\v 39 Xzarem ifassen d iḍaren inu, aqa d \bd Necc Necc\bd*. Ḥadam ayi, u snem belli ijj n řexyař war ɣares bu weysum uřa d iɣsan am mammec d ayi tᵉttwařam.”
\v 40 Umi inna aya, isscen asen ifassen nnes d iḍaren nnes.
\v 41 War uminen ɛad zi ssibbet n řefraḥet, qqimen ttbehten. Inna asen: “Ma ɣarwem da ca n macca?” \x ◘ \xo 24:41 \xt Yḥ. 21:10. \x*
\v 42 Wcin as ict n tecwiḥt n wesřem icennfen d ca n tezřeft n tamment.
\v 43 Iksi tt uca icca i-tt qibač nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 44 Inna asen: “Ina d awařen i zi kidwem ssiwřeɣ umi d ayi tuɣa ɛad akidwem, aqa ittxeṣṣa ad ittwakemmeř marra min xafi yuran di Ccariɛa n Musa, deg Inabiyyen u deg Izehhiden.” \x ◘ \xo 24:44 \xt Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:18; Mk. 8:31; 9:31; 10:33; Lk. 9:22; 18:31; 24:6. \x*
\v 45 Xenni yarzem asen řeɛqeř nsen, ḥima ad fehmen i Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*.
\v 46 Inna asen: “Ammu i tura u ammu i tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad imarret Lmasiḥ u ad dd-ikkar zi taddart n imettinen deg wass wiss třata, \x ◘ \xo 24:46 \xt Izhd. 22:7; Řex. 17:3. \x*
\v 47 \add ḥima\add* ad ittwabarreḥ s ttubet i weɣfar n ddnub i marra řegnus s Yisem nnes, d amezwaru di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 24:47 \xt Řex. 13:38; 1 Yḥ. 2:12. \x*
\v 48 Kenniw d řechud x man aya. \x ◘ \xo 24:48 \xt Lk. 9:15; 21:13\x*
\v 49 Aqa Necc ad awem dd-ssekkeɣ lwaɛd n Baba. Qqimem \add maca\add* di tendint n Urcalim ař ɣa tᵉttwassyarḍem s jjehd zi řuɛřa!” \x ◘ \xo 24:49 \xt Yḥ. 14:26; 15:26; 16:7; Řex. 1:4. \x*
\b
\s1 Tameksit n Yasuɛ ɣar ujenna
\m 
\v 50 Xenni indeh i-ten ɣar \add tendint n\add* Bayt-Ɛanya, issgeɛɛed ifassen nnes uca ibark i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 24:50 \xt [Mk. 16:19-20; Řex.1:9-11] — Řex. 1:12. \x*
\v 51 Awarni řami ten tuɣa ittbarak, imsar, aqa immsebḍa xasen uca iggeɛɛed ɣar ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 24:51 \xt Mk. 16:19 Řex. 1:9. \x*
\v 52 Sejden as uca ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim s řefraḥet temɣar.
\v 53 Tuɣa-ten řebda di Zzawect Tameqqrant, ssemɣaran u ttbaraken AREBBI. Amin.
\b
\m Aneggar n L’Injil Iqeddsen am mammec t ibarreḥ Luka. 
